001695,000227:    6165           00003                           OCT      3                             	# 2 IN DP, AND 3 IN TP.
001696,000228:    6166           00006                           OCT      6                             	#
001697,000229: 
001699,000231:                                                                                          	#          TEST THE SECOND PREFIX BIT TO SEE IF THIS IS A MISCELLANEOUS OR A UNARY/SHORT SHIFT OPERATION.
001700,000232: 
001701,000233:    6167           10020        OPJUMP2            CCS      CYR                           	# TEST SECOND PREFIX BIT.
001702,000234:    6170           16217                           TCF      OPJUMP3                       	# TEST THIRD BIT TO SEE IF UNARY OR SHIFT
001703,000235: 
001704,000236:    6171           77722        -ENDVAC            DEC      -45        B-14               	#
001705,000237: 
001706,000238:                                                                                          	#          THE FOLLOWING ROUTINE PROCESSES ADDRESSES OF SUFFIX CLASS 10. THEY ARE BASICALLY WORK AREA ADDRESSES
001707,000239:                                                                                          	# IN THE RANGE 0 - 52, ERASABLE ADRES CONSTANTS FROM 100 - 1777, AND FCADRS ABOVE THAT. ALL 15 BITS ARE AVAILABLE
001708,000240:                                                                                          	# IN CONTRAST TO SUFFIX 1, IN WHICH ONLY THE LOW ORDER 14 ARE AVAILABLE.
001709,000241: 
001710,000242:    6172           24150        15BITADR           INCR     LOC                           	# (ENTRY HERE FROM STCALL).
001711,000243:    6173           50150                           INDEX    LOC                           	# PICK UP ADDRESS WORD.
001712,000244:    6174           30000                           CA       0                             	#
001713,000245:    6175           54103                           TS       POLISH                        	# THE ABSOLUTE ADDRESS WILL BE LEFT IN
001714,000246:    6176           54102                           TS       ADDRWD                        	# POLISH WITH AN EERASABLE SUBADDRESS IN
001715,000247:                                                                                          	# ADDRWD
001716,000248:    6177           76231                           MASK     HIGH9                         	# SEE IF RELATIVE TO WORK AREA
001717,000249:    6200           10000                           CCS      A                             	#
001718,000250:    6201           16203                           TCF      +2                            	#
001719,000251:    6202           16210                           TCF      RELWORK                       	# ONLY IF ZERO
001720,000252: 
001721,000253:    6203           36230                           CAF      LOW7+2K                       	# THESE INSTRUCTIONS ARE IN BANK 1.
001722,000254:    6204           54004                           TS       FBANK                         	#
001723,000255:    6205           70020                           MASK     CYR                           	#
001724,000256:    6206           50000                           INDEX    A                             	#
001725,000257:    6207           16275                           TCF      MISCJUMP                      	#
001726,000258: 
001727,000259:    6210           30104        RELWORK            CA       FIXLOC                        	# MAKE ADDRWD RELATIVE TO FIXLOC, LEAVING
001728,000260:    6211           26102                           ADS      ADDRWD                        	# POLISH ABSOLUTE IN CASE THIS WAS AN
001729,000261:    6212           36230                           CAF      LOW7+2K                       	# AXT, ETC.
001730,000262:    6213           54004                           TS       FBANK                         	#
001731,000263:    6214           70020                           MASK     CYR                           	#
001732,000264:    6215           50000                           INDEX    A                             	#
001733,000265:    6216           16275                           TCF      MISCJUMP                      	#
001734,000266: 
001736,000268:                                                                                          	#          COMPLETE THE DISPATCHING OF UNARY AND SHORT SHIFT OPERATIONS.
001737,000269: 
001738,000270:    6217           54004        OPJUMP3            TS       FBANK                         	# CALL IN BANK 0 (BITS 11-15 OF A ARE 0.)
001739,000271:    6220           10020                           CCS      CYR                           	# TEST THIRD PREFIX BIT.
001740,000272:    6221           50000                           INDEX    A                             	# THE DECREMENTED UNARY CODE IS IN BITS
001741,000273:    6222           16315                           TCF      UNAJUMP                       	# 1-4 OF A (ZERO, EXIT, HAS BEEN DETECTED)
001742,000274: 
001743,000275:    6223           10147                           CCS      MODE                          	# ITS A SHORT SHIFT CODE. SEE IF PRESENT
001744,000276:    6224           12000                           TCF      SHORTT                        	# SCALAR OR VECTOR.
001745,000277:    6225           12000                           TCF      SHORTT                        	#
001746,000278:    6226           12102                           TCF      SHORTV                        	# CALLS THE APPROPRIATE ROUTINE.
001747,000279: 
001748,000280: 
001749,000281:    6227           00023        OCT23              OCT      23                            	# MASK USED BY PUSH-UP ROUTINE.
001750,000282:    6230           02177        LOW7+2K            OCT      2177                          	# OP CODE MASK + BANK 1 FBANK SETTING.
001751,000283:    6231           77700        HIGH9              OCT      77700                         	#
001752,000284:    6232           76000        BANKMASK           OCT      76000                         	# FBANK MASK.
001753,000285:    6233     6232               FBANKMSK           EQUALS   BANKMASK                      	#
001754,000286:    6233           36000        B11T14             OCT      36000                         	# USED IN PROCESSING STORE CODES.
001755,000287:    6234           76056        -ENDERAS           DEC      -977       B-14               	#
001756,000288: 
001758,000290:                                                                                          	#          THE FOLLOWING IS THE JUMP TABLE FOR OP CODES WHICH MAY HAVE INDEXABLE ADDRESSES OR MAY PUSH UP.
001759,000291: 
001760,000292:    6235           16511        INDJUMP            TCF      VLOAD                         	# 00 - LOAD MPAC WITH A VECTOR.
001761,000293:    6236           17050                           TCF      TAD                           	# 01 - TRIPLE PRECISION ADD TO MPAC.
001762,000294:    6237           17603                           TCF      SIGN                          	# 02 - COMPLEMENT MPAC (V OR SC) IF X NEG.
001763,000295:    6240           17354                           TCF      VXSC                          	# 03 - VECTOR TIMES SCALAR.
001764,000296:    6241           16672                           TCF      CGOTO                         	# 04 - COMPUTED GO TO.
001765,000297:    6242           16474                           TCF      TLOAD                         	# 05 - LOAD MPAC WITH TRIPLE PRECISION.
001766,000298:    6243           16465                           TCF      DLOAD                         	# 06 - LOAD MPAC WITH A DP SCALAR.
001767,000299:    6244           17552                           TCF      V/SC                          	# 07 - VECTOR DIVIDED BY A SCALAR.
001768,000300: 
001769,000301:    6245           16505                           TCF      SLOAD                         	# 10 - LOAD MPAC IN SINGLE PRECISION.
001770,000302:    6246           16624                           TCF      SSP                           	# 11 - SET SINGLE PRECISION INTO X.
001771,000303:    6247           16527                           TCF      PDDL                          	# 12 - PUSH DOWN MPAC AND RE-LOAD IN DP.
001772,000304:    6250           17307                           TCF      MXV                           	# 13 - MATRIX POST-MULTIPLIED BY VECTOR.
001773,000305:    6251           16563                           TCF      PDVL                          	# 14 - PUSH DOWN AND VECTOR LOAD.
001774,000306:    6252           16632                           TCF      CCALL                         	# 15 - COMPUTED CALL.
001775,000307:    6253           17312                           TCF      VXM                           	# 16 - MATRIX PRE-MULTIPLIED BY VECTOR.
001776,000308:    6254           17544                           TCF      TSLC                          	# 17 - NORMALIZE MPAC (SCALAR ONLY).
001777,000309: 
001778,000310:    6255           17522                           TCF      DMPR                          	# 20 - DP MULTIPLY AND ROUND.
001779,000311:    6256           17525                           TCF      DDV                           	# 21 - DP DIVIDE BY.
001780,000312:    6257           17531                           TCF      BDDV                          	# 22 - DP DIVIDE INTO.
001781,000313:    6260           17547                           TCF      GSHIFT                        	# 23 - GENERAL SHIFT INSTRUCTION
001782,000314:    6261           16733                           TCF      VAD                           	# 24 - VECTOR ADD.
001783,000315:    6262           16761                           TCF      VSU                           	# 25 - VECTOR SUBTRACT.
001784,000316:    6263           17011                           TCF      BVSU                          	# 26 - VECTOR SUBTRACT FROM.
001785,000317:    6264           17304                           TCF      DOT                           	# 27 - VECTOR DOT PRODUCT.
001786,000318: 
001787,000319:    6265           17434                           TCF      VXV                           	# 30 - VECTOR CROSS PRODUCT.
001788,000320:    6266           17400                           TCF      VPROJ                         	# 31 - VECTOR PROJECTION.
001789,000321:    6267           16777                           TCF      DSU                           	# 32 - DP SUBTRACT.
001790,000322:    6270           17035                           TCF      BDSU                          	# 33 - DP SUBTRACT FROM.
001791,000323:    6271           16751                           TCF      DAD                           	# 34 - DP ADD.
001792,000324:    6272           16272                           TCF      +0                            	# 35 - AVAILABLE
001793,000325:    6273           17520                           TCF      DMP1                          	# 36 - DP MULTIPLY.
001794,000326:    6274           17541                           TCF      SETPD                         	# 37 - SET PUSH DOWN POINTER (DIRECT ONLY)
001795,000327: 
001796,000328:                                                                                          	# CODES 10 AND 14 MUST NOT PUSH UP. CODE 04 MAY BE USED FOR VECTOR DECLARE BEFORE PUSHUP IF DESIRED.
001797,000329: 
001799,000331:                                                                                          	#          THE FOLLOWING JUMP TABLE APPLIES TO INDEX, BRANCH, AND MISCELLANEOUS INSTRUCTIONS.
001800,000332: 
001801,000333:    6275           12000        MISCJUMP           TCF      AXT                           	# 00 - ADDRESS TO INDEX TRUE.
001802,000334:    6276           12005                           TCF      AXC                           	# 01 - ADDRESS TO INDEX COMPLEMENTED.
001803,000335:    6277           12010                           TCF      LXA                           	# 02 - LOAD INDEX FROM ERASABLE.
001804,000336:    6300           12014                           TCF      LXC                           	# 03 - LOAD INDEX FROM COMPLEMENT OF ERAS.
001805,000337:    6301           12020                           TCF      SXA                           	# 04 - STORE INDEX IN ERASABLE.
001806,000338:    6302           12024                           TCF      XCHX                          	# 05 - EXCHANGE INDEX WITH ERASABLE.
001807,000339:    6303           12040                           TCF      INCR                          	# 06 - INCREMENT INDEX REGISTER.
001808,000340:    6304           12047                           TCF      TIX                           	# 07 - TRANSFER ON INDEX.
001809,000341: 
001810,000342:    6305           12032                           TCF      XAD                           	# 10 - INDEX REGISTER ADD FROM ERASABLE.
001811,000343:    6306           12043                           TCF      XSU                           	# 11 - INDEX SUBTRACT FROM ERASABLE.
001812,000344:    6307           12107                           TCF      BZE/GOTO                      	# 12 - BRANCH ZERO AND GOTO
001813,000345:    6310           12114                           TCF      BPL/BMN                       	# 13 - BRANCH PLUS AND BRANCH MINUS.
001814,000346:    6311           12127                           TCF      CALL/ITA                      	# 14 - CALL AND STORE QPRET.
001815,000347:    6312           12067                           TCF      RTB/BHIZ                      	# 15 - RETURN TO BASIC AND BRANCH HI ZERO.
001816,000348:    6313           12135                           TCF      SW/                           	# 16 - SWITCH INSTRUCTIONS AND AVAILABLE.
001817,000349:    6314           12077                           TCF      BOV(B)                        	# 17 - BRANCH ON OVERFLOW TO BASIC OR INT.
001818,000350: 
001820,000352:                                                                                          	#          THE FOLLOWING JUMP TABLE APPLIES TO UNARY INSTRUCTIONS.
001821,000353: 
001822,000354:                                                                                          	# 00 - EXIT -- DETECTED EARLIER.
001823,000355:    6315           13135        UNAJUMP            TCF      SQRT                          	# 01 - SQUARE ROOT.
001824,000356:    6316           13456                           TCF      SINE                          	# 02 - SIN.
001825,000357:    6317           13445                           TCF      COSINE                        	# 03 - COS.
001826,000358:    6320           13536                           TCF      ARCSIN                        	# 04 - ARC SIN.
001827,000359:    6321           13540                           TCF      ARCCOS                        	# 05 - ARC COS.
001828,000360:    6322           13122                           TCF      DSQ                           	# 06 - DP SQUARE.
001829,000361:    6323           12077                           TCF      ROUND                         	# 07 - ROUND TO DP.
001830,000362: 
001831,000363:    6324           17616                           TCF      COMP                          	# 10 - COMPLEMENT VECTOR OR SCALAR
001832,000364:    6325           13160                           TCF      VDEF                          	# 11 - VECTOR DEFINE.
001833,000365:    6326           12750                           TCF      UNIT                          	# 12 - UNIT VECTOR.
001834,000366:    6327           13124                           TCF      ABVALABS                      	# 13 - LENGTH OF VECTOR OR MAG OF SCALAR.
001835,000367:    6330           13174                           TCF      VSQ                           	# 14 - SQUARE OF LENGTH OF VECTOR.
001836,000368:    6331           16334                           TCF      STADR                         	# 15 - PUSH UP ON STORE CODE.
001837,000369:    6332           13224                           TCF      RVQ                           	# 16 - RETURN VIA QPRET.
001838,000370:    6333           13177                           TCF      PUSH                          	# 17 - PUSH MPAC DOWN.
001839,000371: 
001841,000373:                                                                                          	# SECTION 2  LOAD AND STORE PACKAGE.
001842,000374: 
001843,000375:                                                                                          	#          A SET OF SIXTEEN STORE CODES ARE PROVIDED AS THE PRIMARY METHOD OF STORING THE MULTI-PURPOSE
001844,000376:                                                                                          	# ACCUMULATOR (MPAC). IF IN THE DANZIG SECTION LOC REFERS TO AN ALGEBRAICALLY POSITIVE WORD, IT IS TAKEN AS A
001845,000377:                                                                                          	# STORE CODE WITH A CORRESPONDING ERASABLE ADDRESS. MOST OF THESE CODES ARE TWO ADDRESS, SPECIFYING THAT THE WORD
001846,000378:                                                                                          	# FOLLOWING THE STORE CODE IS TO BE USED AS AN ADDRESS FROM WHICH TO RE-LOAD MPAC. FOUR OPTIONS ARE AVAILABLE:
001847,000379: 
001848,000380:                                                                                          	#          1. STORE               STORE MPAC. THE E ADDRESS MAY BE INDEXED.
001849,000381:                                                                                          	#          2. STODL               STORE MPAC AND RE-LOAD IT IN DP WITH THE NEXT ADDRESS (THE LOAD MAY BE INDEXED).
001850,000382:                                                                                          	#          3. STOVL               STORE MPAC AND RE-LOAD A VECTOR (AS ABOVE).
001851,000383:                                                                                          	#          4. STCALL              STORE AND DO A CALL (BOTH ADDRESSES MUST BE DIRECT HERE).
001852,000384: 
001853,000385:                                                                                          	#          STODL AND STOVL WILL TAKE FROM THE PUSH-DOWN LIST IF NO LOAD ADDRESS IS GIVEN.
001854,000386: 
001855,000387: 
001856,000388: 
001857,000389:    6334           30151        STADR              CA       BANKSET                       	# THE STADR CODE (PUSHUP UP ON STORE
001858,000390:    6335           54004                           TS       FBANK                         	# ADDRESS) ENTERS HERE.
001859,000391:    6336           24150                           INCR     LOC                           	#
001860,000392:    6337           50150                           INDEX    LOC                           	# THE STORE CODE WAS STORE COMPLEMENTED TO
001861,000393:    6340           40000                           CS       0                             	# MAKE IT LOOK LIKE AN OPCODE PAIR.
001862,000394:    6341           67667                           AD       NEGONE                        	# (YUL CANT REMOVE 1 BECAUSE OF EARLY CCS)
001863,000395: 
001864,000396:    6342           54102        DOSTORE            TS       ADDRWD                        	#
001865,000397:    6343           76426                           MASK     LOW10                         	# ENTRY FROM DISPATCHER. SAVE THE ERASABLE
001866,000398:    6344           56102                           XCH      ADDRWD                        	# ADDRESS AND JUMP ON THE STORE CODE NO.
001867,000399:    6345           76233                           MASK     B11T14                        	#
001868,000400:    6346           00006                           EXTEND                                 	#
001869,000401:    6347           77652                           MP       BIT6                          	# EACH TRANSFER VECTOR ENTRY IS TWO WORDS.
001870,000402:    6350           50000                           INDEX    A                             	#
001871,000403:    6351           16352                           TCF      STORJUMP                      	#
001872,000404: 
001874,000406:                                                                                          	#          STORE CODE JUMP TABLE. CALLS THE APPROPRIATE STORING ROUTINE AND EXITS TO DANZIG OR TO ADDRESS WITH
001875,000407:                                                                                          	# A SUPPLIED OPERATION CODE.
001876,000408: 
001877,000409:    6352           06422        STORJUMP           TC       STORE                         	# STORE.
001878,000410:    6353           16022                           TCF      NEWOPS     -1                 	# PICK UP NEW OP CODE(S).
001879,000411:    6354           06414                           TC       STORE,1                       	#
001880,000412:    6355           16022                           TCF      NEWOPS     -1                 	#
001881,000413:    6356           06417                           TC       STORE,2                       	#
001882,000414:    6357           16022                           TCF      NEWOPS     -1                 	#
001883,000415: 
001884,000416:    6360           06422                           TC       STORE                         	# STODL.
001885,000417:    6361           16455                           TCF      DODLOAD                       	#
001886,000418:    6362           06414                           TC       STORE,1                       	#
001887,000419:    6363           16455                           TCF      DODLOAD                       	#
001888,000420:    6364           06417                           TC       STORE,2                       	#
001889,000421:    6365           16455                           TCF      DODLOAD                       	#
001890,000422: 
001891,000423:    6366           06422                           TC       STORE                         	# STODL WITH INDEXED LOAD ADDRESS.
001892,000424:    6367           16071                           TCF      DODLOAD*                      	#
001893,000425:    6370           06414                           TC       STORE,1                       	#
001894,000426:    6371           16071                           TCF      DODLOAD*                      	#
001895,000427:    6372           06417                           TC       STORE,2                       	#
001896,000428:    6373           16071                           TCF      DODLOAD*                      	#
001897,000429: 
001898,000430:    6374           06422                           TC       STORE                         	# STOVL.
001899,000431:    6375           16460                           TCF      DOVLOAD                       	#
001900,000432:    6376           06414                           TC       STORE,1                       	#
001901,000433:    6377           16460                           TCF      DOVLOAD                       	#
001902,000434:    6400           06417                           TC       STORE,2                       	#
001903,000435:    6401           16460                           TCF      DOVLOAD                       	#
001904,000436: 
001905,000437:    6402           06422                           TC       STORE                         	# STOVL WITH INDEXED LOAD ADDRESS.
001906,000438:    6403           16463                           TCF      DOVLOAD*                      	#
001907,000439:    6404           06414                           TC       STORE,1                       	#
001908,000440:    6405           16463                           TCF      DOVLOAD*                      	#
001909,000441:    6406           06417                           TC       STORE,2                       	#
001910,000442:    6407           16463                           TCF      DOVLOAD*                      	#
001911,000443: 
001912,000444:    6410           06422                           TC       STORE                         	# STOTC.
001913,000445:    6411           37674                           CAF      CALLCODE                      	#
001914,000446:    6412           54020                           TS       CYR                           	#
001915,000447:    6413           16172                           TCF      15BITADR                      	# GET A 15 BIT ADDRESS.
001916,000448: 
001918,000450:                                                                                          	#          STORE CODE ADDRESS PROCESSOR.
001919,000451: 
001920,000452:    6414           50104        STORE,1            INDEX    FIXLOC                        	#
001921,000453:    6415           40046                           CS       X1                            	#
001922,000454:    6416           16421                           TCF      PRESTORE                      	#
001923,000455: 
001924,000456:    6417           50104        STORE,2            INDEX    FIXLOC                        	#
001925,000457:    6420           40047                           CS       X2                            	#
001926,000458:    6421           26102        PRESTORE           ADS      ADDRWD                        	# RESULTANT ADDRESS IS IN ERASABLE.
001927,000459: 
001928,000460:    6422           30102        STORE              CA       ADDRWD                        	# SEE IF ADDRESS REALTIVE TO WORK AREA.
001929,000461:    6423           66171                           AD       -ENDVAC                       	#
001930,000462:    6424           10000                           CCS      A                             	#
001931,000463:    6425           16431                           TCF      STARTSTO                      	# ADDRESS OK AS IS.
001932,000464: 
001933,000465:    6426           01777        LOW10              OCT      1777                          	#
001934,000466: 
001935,000467:    6427           30104                           CA       FIXLOC                        	# GIVEN ADDRESS IS RELATIVE TO WORK AREA.
001936,000468:    6430           26102                           ADS      ADDRWD                        	#
001937,000469: 
001939,000471:                                                                                          	#          STORING ROUTINES. STORE DP, TP, OR VECTOR AS INDICATED BY MODE.
001940,000472: 
001941,000473:    6431           00006        STARTSTO           EXTEND                                 	# MPAC,+1 MUST BE STORED IN ANY EVENT.
001942,000474:    6432           30141                           DCA      MPAC                          	#
001943,000475:    6433           50102                           INDEX    ADDRWD                        	#
001944,000476:    6434           52001                           DXCH     0                             	#
001945,000477: 
001946,000478:    6435           10147                           CCS      MODE                          	#
001947,000479:    6436           16451                           TCF      TSTORE                        	#
001948,000480:    6437           00002                           TC       Q                             	#
001949,000481: 
001950,000482:    6440           00006        VSTORE             EXTEND                                 	#
001951,000483:    6441           30144                           DCA      MPAC       +3                 	#
001952,000484:    6442           50102                           INDEX    ADDRWD                        	#
001953,000485:    6443           52003                           DXCH     2                             	#
001954,000486: 
001955,000487:    6444           00006                           EXTEND                                 	#
001956,000488:    6445           30146                           DCA      MPAC       +5                 	#
001957,000489:    6446           50102                           INDEX    ADDRWD                        	#
001958,000490:    6447           52005                           DXCH     4                             	#
001959,000491:    6450           00002                           TC       Q                             	#
001960,000492: 
001961,000493:    6451           30142        TSTORE             CA       MPAC       +2                 	#
001962,000494:    6452           50102                           INDEX    ADDRWD                        	#
001963,000495:    6453           54002                           TS       2                             	#
001964,000496:    6454           00002                           TC       Q                             	#
001965,000497: 
001967,000499:                                                                                          	#          ROUTINES TO BEGIN PROCESSING OF THE SECOND ADDRES ASSOCIATED WITH ALL STORE-TYPE CODES EXCEPT STORE
001968,000500:                                                                                          	# ITSELF.
001969,000501: 
001970,000502:    6455           37675        DODLOAD            CAF      DLOADCOD                      	#
001971,000503:    6456           54020                           TS       CYR                           	#
001972,000504:    6457           16041                           TCF      DIRADRES                      	# GO GET A DIRECT ADDRESS.
001973,000505: 
001974,000506:    6460           37641        DOVLOAD            CAF      VLOADCOD                      	#
001975,000507:    6461           54020                           TS       CYR                           	#
001976,000508:    6462           16041                           TCF      DIRADRES                      	#
001977,000509: 
001978,000510:    6463           36042        DOVLOAD*           CAF      VLOAD*                        	#
001979,000511:    6464           16072                           TCF      DODLOAD*   +1                 	# PROLOGUE TO INDEX ROUTINE.
001980,000512: 
001982,000514:                                                                                          	#          THE FOLLOWING LOAD INSTRUCTIONS ARE PROVIDED FOR LOADING THE MULTI-PURPOSE ACCUMULATOR MPAC.
001983,000515: 
001984,000516:    6465           00006        DLOAD              EXTEND                                 	#
001985,000517:    6466           50102                           INDEX    ADDRWD                        	#
001986,000518:    6467           30001                           DCA      0                             	# PICK UP DP ARGUMENT AND LEAVE IT IN
001987,000519:    6470           52141        SLOAD2             DXCH     MPAC                          	# MPAC,+1, SETTING MPAC +2 TO ZERO. THE
001988,000520:    6471           37665                           CAF      ZERO                          	# CONTENTS OF THE OTHER FOUR REGISTERS OF
001989,000521:    6472           54142                           TS       MPAC       +2                 	# MPAC ARE IRRELEVANT
001990,000522:    6473           16013                           TCF      NEWMODE                       	# DECLARE DOUBLE PRECISION MODE.
001991,000523: 
001992,000524:    6474           50102        TLOAD              INDEX    ADDRWD                        	#
001993,000525:    6475           30002                           CA       2                             	# LOAD A TRIPLE PRECISION ARGUMENT INTO
001994,000526:    6476           54142                           TS       MPAC       +2                 	# THE FIRST THREE MPAC REGISTERS, WITH THE
001995,000527:    6477           00006                           EXTEND                                 	# CONTENTS OF THE OTHER FOUR IRRELEVANT.
001996,000528:    6500           50102                           INDEX    ADDRWD                        	#
001997,000529:    6501           30001                           DCA      0                             	#
001998,000530:    6502           52141                           DXCH     MPAC                          	#
001999,000531:    6503           37657                           CAF      ONE                           	#
002000,000532:    6504           16013                           TCF      NEWMODE                       	# DECLARE TRIPLE PRECISION MODE.
002001,000533: 
002002,000534:    6505           22007        SLOAD              ZL                                     	# LOAD A SINGLE PRECISION NUMBER INTO
002003,000535:    6506           50102                           INDEX    ADDRWD                        	# MPAC, SETTING MPAC+1,2 TO ZERO. THE
002004,000536:    6507           30000                           CA       0                             	# CONTENTS OF THE REMAINING MPAC REGISTERS
002005,000537:    6510           16470                           TCF      SLOAD2                        	# ARE IRRELEVANT.
002006,000538: 
002007,000539:    6511           00006        VLOAD              EXTEND                                 	# LOAD A DOUBLE PRECISION VECTOR INTO
002008,000540:    6512           50102                           INDEX    ADDRWD                        	# MPAC,+1, MPAC+3,4, AND MPAC+5,6. THE
002009,000541:    6513           30001                           DCA      0                             	# CONTENTS OF MPAC +2 ARE IRRELEVANT.
002010,000542:    6514           52141                           DXCH     MPAC                          	#
002011,000543: 
002012,000544:    6515           00006        ENDVLOAD           EXTEND                                 	# PDVL COMES HERE TO FINISH UP FOR DP, TP.
002013,000545:    6516           50102                           INDEX    ADDRWD                        	#
002014,000546:    6517           30003                           DCA      2                             	#
002015,000547:    6520           52144                           DXCH     MPAC       +3                 	#
002016,000548: 
002017,000549:    6521           00006                 +4        EXTEND                                 	# TPDVL FINISHES HERE.
002018,000550:    6522           50102                           INDEX    ADDRWD                        	#
002019,000551:    6523           30005                           DCA      4                             	#
002020,000552:    6524           52146                           DXCH     MPAC       +5                 	#
002021,000553: 
002022,000554:    6525           47657                           CS       ONE                           	# DECLARE VECTOR MODE.
002023,000555:    6526           16013                           TCF      NEWMODE                       	#
002024,000556: 
002026,000558:                                                                                          	#          THE FOLLOWING INSTRUCTIONS ARE PROVIDED FOR STORING OPERANDS IN THE PUSHDOWN LIST:
002027,000559: 
002028,000560:                                                                                          	#          1.  PUSH               PUSHDOWN AND NO LOAD.
002029,000561:                                                                                          	#          2.  PDDL               PUSHDOWN AND DOUBLE PRECISION LOAD.
002030,000562:                                                                                          	#          3.  PDVL               PUSHDOWN AND VECTOR LOAD.
002031,000563: 
002032,000564:    6527           00006        PDDL               EXTEND                                 	#
002033,000565:    6530           50102                           INDEX    ADDRWD                        	# LOAD MPAC,+1, PUSHING THE FORMER
002034,000566:    6531           30001                           DCA      0                             	# CONTENTS DOWN.
002035,000567:    6532           52141                           DXCH     MPAC                          	#
002036,000568:    6533           50152                           INDEX    PUSHLOC                       	#
002037,000569:    6534           52001                           DXCH     0                             	#
002038,000570: 
002039,000571:    6535           50147                           INDEX    MODE                          	# ADVANCE THE PUSHDOWN POINTER APPRO-
002040,000572:    6536           36164                           CAF      NO.WDS                        	# PRIATELY.
002041,000573:    6537           26152                           ADS      PUSHLOC                       	#
002042,000574: 
002043,000575:    6540           10147                           CCS      MODE                          	#
002044,000576:    6541           16556                           TCF      ENDTPUSH                      	#
002045,000577:    6542           16554                           TCF      ENDDPUSH                      	#
002046,000578: 
002047,000579:    6543           54147                           TS       MODE                          	# NOW DP.
002048,000580:    6544           54142        ENDVPUSH           TS       MPAC       +2                 	#
002049,000581:    6545           52144                           DXCH     MPAC       +3                 	# PUSH DOWN THE REST OF THE VECTOR HERE.
002050,000582:    6546           50152                           INDEX    PUSHLOC                       	#
002051,000583:    6547           51775                           DXCH     0          -4                 	#
002052,000584: 
002053,000585:    6550           52146                           DXCH     MPAC       +5                 	#
002054,000586:    6551           50152                           INDEX    PUSHLOC                       	#
002055,000587:    6552           51777                           DXCH     0          -2                 	#
002056,000588: 
002057,000589:    6553           16014                           TCF      DANZIG                        	#
002058,000590: 
002059,000591:    6554           54142        ENDDPUSH           TS       MPAC       +2                 	# SET MPAC +2 TO ZERO AND EXIT ON DP.
002060,000592:    6555           16014                           TCF      DANZIG                        	#
002061,000593: 
002062,000594:    6556           54147        ENDTPUSH           TS       MODE                          	#
002063,000595:    6557           56142                           XCH      MPAC       +2                 	# ON TRIPLE, SET MPAC +2 TO ZERO, PUSHING
002064,000596:    6560           50152                 +2        INDEX    PUSHLOC                       	# DOWN THE OLD CONTENTS
002065,000597:    6561           53777                           TS       0          -1                 	#
002066,000598:    6562           16014                           TCF      DANZIG                        	#
002067,000599: 
002069,000601:                                                                                          	#          PDVL - PUSHDOWN AND VECTOR LOAD.
002070,000602: 
002071,000603:    6563           00006        PDVL               EXTEND                                 	# RELOAD MPAC AND PUSH DOWN ITS CONTENTS.
002072,000604:    6564           50102                           INDEX    ADDRWD                        	#
002073,000605:    6565           30001                           DCA      0                             	#
002074,000606:    6566           52141                           DXCH     MPAC                          	#
002075,000607:    6567           50152                           INDEX    PUSHLOC                       	#
002076,000608:    6570           52001                           DXCH     0                             	#
002077,000609: 
002078,000610:    6571           50147                           INDEX    MODE                          	# ADVANCE THE PUSHDOWN POINTER.
002079,000611:    6572           36164                           CAF      NO.WDS                        	#
002080,000612:    6573           26152                           ADS      PUSHLOC                       	#
002081,000613: 
002082,000614:    6574           10147                           CCS      MODE                          	# TEST PAST MODE.
002083,000615:    6575           16614                           TCF      TPDVL                         	#
002084,000616:    6576           16515                           TCF      ENDVLOAD                      	# JUST LOAD LAST FOUR REGISTERS ON DP.
002085,000617: 
002086,000618:    6577           00006        VPDVL              EXTEND                                 	# PUSHDOWN AND RE-LOAD LAST TWO COMPONENTS
002087,000619:    6600           50102                           INDEX    ADDRWD                        	#
002088,000620:    6601           30003                           DCA      2                             	#
002089,000621:    6602           52144                           DXCH     MPAC       +3                 	#
002090,000622:    6603           50152                           INDEX    PUSHLOC                       	#
002091,000623:    6604           51775                           DXCH     0          -4                 	#
002092,000624: 
002093,000625:    6605           00006                           EXTEND                                 	#
002094,000626:    6606           50102                           INDEX    ADDRWD                        	#
002095,000627:    6607           30005                           DCA      4                             	#
002096,000628:    6610           52146                           DXCH     MPAC       +5                 	#
002097,000629:    6611           50152                           INDEX    PUSHLOC                       	#
002098,000630:    6612           51777                           DXCH     0          -2                 	#
002099,000631: 
002100,000632:    6613           16014                           TCF      DANZIG                        	#
002101,000633: 
002102,000634:    6614           00006        TPDVL              EXTEND                                 	# ON TP, WE MUST LOAD THE Y COMPONENT
002103,000635:    6615           50102                           INDEX    ADDRWD                        	# BEFORE STORING MPAC +2 IN CASE THIS IS A
002104,000636:    6616           30003                           DCA      2                             	# PUSHUP.
002105,000637:    6617           52144                           DXCH     MPAC       +3                 	#
002106,000638: 
002107,000639:    6620           30142                           CA       MPAC       +2                 	#
002108,000640:    6621           50152                           INDEX    PUSHLOC                       	# IN DP.
002109,000641:    6622           53777                           TS       0          -1                 	#
002110,000642:    6623           16521                           TCF      ENDVLOAD   +4                 	#
002111,000643: 
002112,000644:                                                                                          	#          SSP (STORE SINGLE PRECISION) IS EXECUTED HERE.
002113,000645: 
002114,000646:    6624           24150        SSP                INCR     LOC                           	# PICK UP THE WORD FOLLOWING THE GIVEN
002115,000647:    6625           50150                           INDEX    LOC                           	# ADDRESS AND STORE IT AT X.
002116,000648:    6626           30000                           CA       0                             	#
002117,000649:    6627           50102        STORE1             INDEX    ADDRWD                        	# SOME INDEX AND MISCELLANEOUS OPS END
002118,000650:    6630           54000                           TS       0                             	# HERE.
002119,000651: 
002121,000653:    6631           16014                           TCF      DANZIG                        	#
002122,000654: 
002124,000656:                                                                                          	# SEQUENCE CHANGING AND SUBROUTINE CALLING OPTIONS.
002125,000657: 
002126,000658:                                                                                          	#          THE FOLLOWING OPERATIONS ARE AVAILABLE FOR SEQUENCING CHANGING, BRANCHING, AND CALLING SUBROUTINES:
002127,000659: 
002128,000660:                                                                                          	#          1. GOTO                GO TO.
002129,000661:                                                                                          	#          2. CALL                CALL SUBROUTINE SETTING QPRET.
002130,000662:                                                                                          	#          3. CGOTO               COMPUTED GO TO.
002131,000663:                                                                                          	#          4. CCALL               COMPUTED CALL.
002132,000664:                                                                                          	#          7. BPL                 BRANCH IF MPAC POSITIVE OR ZERO.
002133,000665:                                                                                          	#          8. BZE                 BRANCH IF MPAC ZERO.
002134,000666:                                                                                          	#          9. BMN                 BRANCH IF MPAC NEGATIVE NON-ZERO.
002135,000667: 
002136,000668:    6632           24150        CCALL              INCR     LOC                           	# MAINTAIN LOC FOR QPRET COMPUTATION
002137,000669:    6633           50150                           INDEX    LOC                           	#
002138,000670:    6634           30000                           CAF      0                             	# GET BASE ADDRESS OF CADR LIST.
002139,000671:    6635           50102                           INDEX    ADDRWD                        	#
002140,000672:    6636           60000                           AD       0                             	# ADD INCREMENT.
002141,000673:    6637           54004                           TS       FBANK                         	# SELECT DESIRED CADR.
002142,000674:    6640           76426                           MASK     LOW10                         	#
002143,000675:    6641           50000                           INDEX    A                             	#
002144,000676:    6642           32000                           CAF      10000                         	#
002145,000677:    6643           54103                 -1        TS       POLISH                        	#
002146,000678: 
002147,000679:    6644           46426        CALL               CS       LOW10                         	# FOR ANY OF THE CALL OPTIONS, MAKE UP THE
002148,000680:    6645           60150                           AD       LOC                           	# ADDRESS OF THE NEXT OP-CODE PAIR/STORE
002149,000681:    6646           60151                           AD       BANKSET                       	# CODE AND LEAVE IT IN QPRET. NOTE THAT
002150,000682:    6647           50104                           INDEX    FIXLOC                        	# LOW10 = 2000 - 1.
002151,000683:    6650           54052                           TS       QPRET                         	#
002152,000684: 
002153,000685:    6651           30103        GOTO               CA       POLISH                        	# BASIC BRANCHING SEQUENCE.
002154,000686:    6652           54004                           TS       FBANK                         	#
002155,000687:    6653           76426                           MASK     LOW10                         	# MAKE UP 12 BIT SUB-ADDRESS AND FALL INTO
002156,000688:    6654           67645                           AD       2K                            	# FALL INTO THE INTPRET ENTRY UNLESS THE
002157,000689:    6655           54150                           TS       LOC                           	# GIVEN ADDRESS WAS IN ERASABLE, IN WHICH
002158,000690:    6656           10004                           CCS      FBANK                         	# CASE IT IS USED AS THE ADDRESS OF THE
002159,000691:    6657           16002                           TCF      INTPRET    +2                 	# BRANCH ADDRESS.
002160,000692:    6660           16662                           TCF      +2                            	#
002161,000693:    6661           16002                           TCF      INTPRET    +2                 	#
002162,000694: 
002164,000696:    6662           40150                           CS       LOC                           	# THE GIVEN ADDRESS IS IN ERASABLE - SEE
002165,000697:    6663           66710                           AD       EVAC+2K                       	# IF RELATIVE TO THE WORK AREA.
002166,000698:    6664           10000                           CCS      A                             	#
002167,000699:    6665           30104                           CA       FIXLOC                        	# ADD FIXLOC IF SO.
002168,000700:    6666           26150                           ADS      LOC                           	#
002169,000701: 
002170,000702:    6667           50150                           INDEX    LOC                           	#
002171,000703:    6670           26000                           CA       0          -2000              	# (ADDRESS HAD BEEN AUGMENTED BY 2000.)
002172,000704:    6671           16652                           TCF      GOTO       +1                 	# ALLOWS ARBITRARY INDICRECTNESS.
002173,000705: 
002174,000706:    6672           50150        CGOTO              INDEX    LOC                           	# COMPUTED GO TO. PICK UP ADDRESS OF CADR
002175,000707:    6673           30001                           CA       1                             	# LIST.
002176,000708:    6674           50102                           INDEX    ADDRWD                        	# ADD MODIFIER.
002177,000709:    6675           60000                           AD       0                             	#
002178,000710:    6676           54004                           TS       FBANK                         	# SELECT GOTO ADDRESS.
002179,000711:    6677           76426                           MASK     LOW10                         	#
002180,000712:    6700           50000                           INDEX    A                             	#
002181,000713:    6701           32000                           CA       10000                         	#
002182,000714:    6702           16652                           TCF      GOTO       +1                 	# WITH ADDRESS IN A.
002183,000715: 
002184,000716:    6703           30151        SWBRANCH           CA       BANKSET                       	# SWITCH INSTRUCTIONS WHICH ELECT TO
002185,000717:    6704           54004                           TS       FBANK                         	# BRANCH COME HERE TO DO SO.
002186,000718:    6705           50150                           INDEX    LOC                           	#
002187,000719:    6706           30001                           CA       1                             	#
002188,000720:    6707           16652                           TCF      GOTO       +1                 	#
002189,000721: 
002190,000722:    6710           02055        EVAC+2K            DEC      1069       B-14               	# =1024+45
002191,000723: 
002193,000725:                                                                                          	#          TRIPLE PRECISION BRANCHING ROUTINE. IF CALLING TC IS AT L, RETURN IS AS FOLLOWS:
002194,000726:                                                                                          	#          L+1  IF MPAC IS GREATER THAN ZERO.
002195,000727:                                                                                          	#          L+2  IF MPAC IS EQUAL TO +0 OR -0.
002196,000728:                                                                                          	#          L+3  IF MPAC IS LESS THAN ZERO.
002197,000729: 
002198,000730: 
002199,000731: 
002200,000732:    6711           10140        BRANCH             CCS      MPAC                          	#
002201,000733:    6712           00002                           TC       Q                             	#
002202,000734:    6713           16715                           TCF      +2                            	# ON ZERO.
002203,000735:    6714           16727                           TCF      NEG                           	#
002204,000736: 
002205,000737:    6715           10141                           CCS      MPAC       +1                 	#
002206,000738:    6716           00002                           TC       Q                             	#
002207,000739:    6717           16721                           TCF      +2                            	#
002208,000740:    6720           16727                           TCF      NEG                           	#
002209,000741: 
002210,000742:    6721           10142                           CCS      MPAC       +2                 	#
002211,000743:    6722           00002                           TC       Q                             	#
002212,000744:    6723           16725                           TCF      +2                            	#
002213,000745:    6724           16727                           TCF      NEG                           	#
002214,000746: 
002215,000747:    6725           50002                           INDEX    Q                             	# IF ALL THREE REGISTERS WHERE +-0.
002216,000748:    6726           00001                           TC       1                             	#
002217,000749: 
002218,000750:    6727           50002        NEG                INDEX    Q                             	# IF FIRST NON-ZERO REGISTER WAS NEGATIVE.
002219,000751:    6730           00002                           TC       2                             	#
002220,000752: 
002221,000753: 
002222,000754: 
002223,000755:    6731           50150        EXIT               INDEX    LOC                           	# LEAVE INTERPRETIVE MODE.
002224,000756:    6732           10001                           TCF      1                             	#
002225,000757: 
002227,000759:                                                                                          	# SECTION 3 - ADD/SUBTRACT PACKAGE.
002228,000760: 
002229,000761:                                                                                          	#          THE FOLLOWING OPERATIONS ARE PROVIDED FOR ADDING TO AND SUBTRACTING FROM THE MULTI-PURPOSE ACCUMULATOR
002230,000762:                                                                                          	# MPAC:
002231,000763: 
002232,000764:                                                                                          	#          1. DAD                 DOUBLE PRECISION ADD.
002233,000765:                                                                                          	#          2. DSU                 DOUBLE PRECISION SUBTRACT.
002234,000766:                                                                                          	#          3. BDSU                DOUBLE PRECISION SUBTRACT FROM.
002235,000767: 
002236,000768:                                                                                          	#          4. TAD                 TRIPLE PRECISION ADD.
002237,000769: 
002238,000770:                                                                                          	#          5. VAD                 VECTOR ADD.
002239,000771:                                                                                          	#          6. VSU                 VECTOR SUBTRACT.
002240,000772:                                                                                          	#          7. BVSU                VECTOR SUBTRACT FROM.
002241,000773: 
002242,000774:                                                                                          	# THE INTERPRETIVE OVERFLOW INDICATOR OVFIND IS SET NON-ZERO IF OVERFLOW OCCURS IN ANY OF THE ABOVE.
002243,000775: 
002244,000776: 
002245,000777: 
002246,000778:    6733           00006        VAD                EXTEND                                 	#
002247,000779:    6734           50102                           INDEX    ADDRWD                        	#
002248,000780:    6735           30003                           DCA      2                             	#
002249,000781:    6736           20144                           DAS      MPAC       +3                 	#
002250,000782:    6737           00006                           EXTEND                                 	# CHECK OVERFLOW.
002251,000783:    6740           16742                           BZF      +2                            	#
002252,000784:    6741           07007                           TC       OVERFLOW                      	#
002253,000785: 
002254,000786:    6742           00006                           EXTEND                                 	#
002255,000787:    6743           50102                           INDEX    ADDRWD                        	#
002256,000788:    6744           30005                           DCA      4                             	#
002257,000789:    6745           20146                           DAS      MPAC       +5                 	#
002258,000790:    6746           00006                           EXTEND                                 	#
002259,000791:    6747           16751                           BZF      +2                            	#
002260,000792:    6750           07007                           TC       OVERFLOW                      	#
002261,000793: 
002262,000794:    6751           00006        DAD                EXTEND                                 	#
002263,000795:    6752           50102                           INDEX    ADDRWD                        	#
002264,000796:    6753           30001                           DCA      0                             	#
002265,000797:    6754           20141        ENDVXV             DAS      MPAC                          	# VXV FINISHES HERE.
002266,000798:    6755           00006                           EXTEND                                 	#
002267,000799:    6756           16014                           BZF      DANZIG                        	#
002268,000800:    6757           07007                           TC       OVERFLOW                      	#
002269,000801:    6760           16014                           TCF      DANZIG                        	#
002270,000802: 
002272,000804:    6761           00006        VSU                EXTEND                                 	#
002273,000805:    6762           50102                           INDEX    ADDRWD                        	#
002274,000806:    6763           40003                           DCS      2                             	#
002275,000807:    6764           20144                           DAS      MPAC       +3                 	#
002276,000808:    6765           00006                           EXTEND                                 	#
002277,000809:    6766           16770                           BZF      +2                            	#
002278,000810:    6767           07007                           TC       OVERFLOW                      	#
002279,000811: 
002280,000812:    6770           00006                           EXTEND                                 	#
002281,000813:    6771           50102                           INDEX    ADDRWD                        	#
002282,000814:    6772           40005                           DCS      4                             	#
002283,000815:    6773           20146                           DAS      MPAC       +5                 	#
002284,000816:    6774           00006                           EXTEND                                 	#
002285,000817:    6775           16777                           BZF      +2                            	#
002286,000818:    6776           07007                           TC       OVERFLOW                      	#
002287,000819: 
002288,000820:    6777           00006        DSU                EXTEND                                 	#
002289,000821:    7000           50102                           INDEX    ADDRWD                        	#
002290,000822:    7001           40001                           DCS      0                             	#
002291,000823:    7002           20141                           DAS      MPAC                          	#
002292,000824:    7003           00006                           EXTEND                                 	#
002293,000825:    7004           16014                           BZF      DANZIG                        	#
002294,000826:    7005           07007                           TC       OVERFLOW                      	#
002295,000827:    7006           16014                           TCF      DANZIG                        	#
002296,000828: 
002297,000829:    7007           37657        OVERFLOW           CAF      ONE                           	# SUBROUTINE TO TURN OVFIND ON.
002298,000830:    7010           17132                           TCF      SETOVF2                       	#
002299,000831: 
002301,000833:    7011           00006        BVSU               EXTEND                                 	#
002302,000834:    7012           50102                           INDEX    ADDRWD                        	#
002303,000835:    7013           30003                           DCA      2                             	#
002304,000836:    7014           52144                           DXCH     MPAC       +3                 	#
002305,000837:    7015           00006                           EXTEND                                 	#
002306,000838:    7016           40001                           DCOM                                   	#
002307,000839:    7017           20144                           DAS      MPAC       +3                 	#
002308,000840:    7020           00006                           EXTEND                                 	#
002309,000841:    7021           17023                           BZF      +2                            	#
002310,000842:    7022           07007                           TC       OVERFLOW                      	#
002311,000843: 
002312,000844:    7023           00006                           EXTEND                                 	#
002313,000845:    7024           50102                           INDEX    ADDRWD                        	#
002314,000846:    7025           30005                           DCA      4                             	#
002315,000847:    7026           52146                           DXCH     MPAC       +5                 	#
002316,000848:    7027           00006                           EXTEND                                 	#
002317,000849:    7030           40001                           DCOM                                   	#
002318,000850:    7031           20146                           DAS      MPAC       +5                 	#
002319,000851:    7032           00006                           EXTEND                                 	#
002320,000852:    7033           17035                           BZF      +2                            	#
002321,000853:    7034           07007                           TC       OVERFLOW                      	#
002322,000854: 
002323,000855:    7035           00006        BDSU               EXTEND                                 	#
002324,000856:    7036           50102                           INDEX    ADDRWD                        	#
002325,000857:    7037           30001                           DCA      0                             	#
002326,000858:    7040           52141                           DXCH     MPAC                          	#
002327,000859:    7041           00006                           EXTEND                                 	#
002328,000860:    7042           40001                           DCOM                                   	#
002329,000861:    7043           20141                           DAS      MPAC                          	#
002330,000862:    7044           00006                           EXTEND                                 	#
002331,000863:    7045           16014                           BZF      DANZIG                        	#
002332,000864:    7046           07007                           TC       OVERFLOW                      	#
002333,000865:    7047           16014                           TCF      DANZIG                        	#
002334,000866: 
002336,000868:                                                                                          	#          TRIPLE PRECISION ADD ROUTINE.
002337,000869: 
002338,000870:    7050           00006        TAD                EXTEND                                 	#
002339,000871:    7051           50102                           INDEX    ADDRWD                        	#
002340,000872:    7052           30002                           DCA      1                             	# ADD MINOR PARTS FIRST.
002341,000873:    7053           20142                           DAS      MPAC       +1                 	#
002342,000874:    7054           50102                           INDEX    ADDRWD                        	#
002343,000875:    7055           60000                           AD       0                             	#
002344,000876:    7056           60140                           AD       MPAC                          	#
002345,000877:    7057           54140                           TS       MPAC                          	#
002346,000878:    7060           16014                           TCF      DANZIG                        	#
002347,000879: 
002348,000880:    7061           54105        SETOVF             TS       OVFIND                        	# SET OVFIND IF SUCH OCCURS.
002349,000881:    7062           16014                           TCF      DANZIG                        	#
002350,000882: 
002352,000884:                                                                                          	# ARITHMETIC SUBROUTINES REQUIRED IN FIXED-FIXED.
002353,000885: 
002354,000886:                                                                                          	#          1.  DMPSUB     DOUBLE PRECISION MULTIPLY, MULTIPLY THE CONTENTS OF MPAC,+1 BY THE DP WORD WHOSE ADDRESS
002355,000887:                                                                                          	#                         IS IN ADDRWD AND LEAVE A TRIPLE PRECISION RESULT IN MPAC.
002356,000888:                                                                                          	#          2.  ROUNDSUB   ROUND THE TRIPLE PRECISON CONTENTS OF MPAC TO DOUBLE PRECISION.
002357,000889:                                                                                          	#          3.  DOTSUB     TAKE THE DOT PRODUCT OF THE VECTOR IN MPAC AND THE VECTOR WHOSE ADDRESS IS IN ADDRWD
002358,000890:                                                                                          	#                         AND LEAVE THE TRIPLE PRECISION RESULT IN MPAC.
002359,000891:                                                                                          	#          4.  POLY       USING THE CONTENTS OF MPAC AS A DP ARGUMENT, EVALUATE THE POLYNOMIAL WHOSE DEGREE AND
002360,000892:                                                                                          	#                         COEFFICIENTS IMMEDIATELY FOLLOW THE TC POLY INSTRUCTION (SEE ROUTINE FOR DETAILS).
002361,000893: 
002362,000894: 
002363,000895: 
002364,000896:    7063           50002        DMP                INDEX    Q                             	# BASIC SUBROUTINE FOR USE BY PINBALL, ETC
002365,000897:    7064           30000                           CAF      0                             	# ADRES OF ARGUMENT FOLLOWS  TC DMP  .
002366,000898:    7065           24002                           INCR     Q                             	#
002367,000899:    7066           54102                 -1        TS       ADDRWD                        	# (PROLOGUE FOR SETTING ADDRWD.)
002368,000900: 
002369,000901:    7067           50102        DMPSUB             INDEX    ADDRWD                        	# GET MINOR PART OF OPERAND AT C(ADDRWD).
002370,000902:    7070           30001                           CA       1                             	#
002371,000903:    7071           54142                           TS       MPAC       +2                 	# THIS WORKS FOR SQUARING MPAC AS WELL.
002372,000904:    7072           37665                           CAF      ZERO                          	# SET MPAC +1 TO ZERO SO WE CAN ACCUMULATE
002373,000905:    7073           56141                           XCH      MPAC       +1                 	# THE PARTIAL PRODUCTS WITH DAS
002374,000906:    7074           54121                           TS       MPTEMP                        	# INSTRUCTIONS.
002375,000907:    7075           00006                           EXTEND                                 	#
002376,000908:    7076           70142                           MP       MPAC       +2                 	# MINOR OF MPAC X MINOR OF C(ADDRWD).
002377,000909: 
002378,000910:    7077           56142                           XCH      MPAC       +2                 	# DISCARD MINOR PART OF ABOVE RESULT AND
002379,000911:    7100           00006                           EXTEND                                 	# FORM MAJOR OF MPAC X MINOR OF C(ADDRWD).
002380,000912:    7101           70140                           MP       MPAC                          	#
002381,000913:    7102           20142                           DAS      MPAC       +1                 	# GUARANTEED NO OVERFLOW.
002382,000914: 
002383,000915:    7103           50102                           INDEX    ADDRWD                        	# GET MAJOR PART OF ARGUMENT AT C(ADDRWD).
002384,000916:    7104           30000                           CA       0                             	#
002385,000917:    7105           56121                           XCH      MPTEMP                        	# SAVE AND BRING OUT MINOR OF MPAC.
002386,000918:    7106           00006                           EXTEND                                 	#
002387,000919:    7107           70121                           MP       MPTEMP                        	# MAJOR OF C(ADDRWD) X MINOR OF MPAC.
002388,000920:    7110           20142                           DAS      MPAC       +1                 	# ACCUMULATE, SETTING A TO NET OVERFLOW.
002389,000921: 
002390,000922:    7111           56140                           XCH      MPAC                          	# SETTING MPAC TO 0 OR +-1.
002391,000923:    7112           00006                           EXTEND                                 	#
002392,000924:    7113           70121                           MP       MPTEMP                        	# MAJOR OF MPAC X MAJOR OF C(ADDRWD).
002393,000925:    7114           20141                           DAS      MPAC                          	# GUARANTEED NO OVERFLOW.
002394,000926:    7115           00002                           TC       Q                             	# 49 MCT = .573 MS. INCLUDING RETURN.
002395,000927: 
002397,000929:                                                                                          	#          ROUND MPAC TO DOUBLE PRECISION, SETTING OVFIND ON THE RARE EVENT OF OVERFLOW.
002398,000930: 
002399,000931:    7116           37665        ROUNDSUB           CAF      ZERO                          	# SET MPAC +2 = 0 FOR SCALARS AND CHANGE
002400,000932:    7117           54147                 +1        TS       MODE                          	# MODE TO DP.
002401,000933: 
002402,000934:    7120           56142        VROUND             XCH      MPAC       +2                 	# BUT WE NEEDNT TAKE THE TIME FOR VECTORS.
002403,000935:    7121           60000                           DOUBLE                                 	#
002404,000936:    7122           54001                           TS       L                             	#
002405,000937:    7123           00002                           TC       Q                             	#
002406,000938: 
002407,000939:    7124           60141                           AD       MPAC       +1                 	# ADD ROUNDING BIT IF MPAC +2 WAS GREATER
002408,000940:    7125           54141                           TS       MPAC       +1                 	# THAN .5 IN MAGNITUDE.
002409,000941:    7126           00002                           TC       Q                             	#
002410,000942: 
002411,000943:    7127           60140                           AD       MPAC                          	# PROPAGATE INTERFLOW.
002412,000944:    7130           54140                           TS       MPAC                          	#
002413,000945:    7131           00002                           TC       Q                             	#
002414,000946: 
002415,000947:    7132           54105        SETOVF2            TS       OVFIND                        	# (RARE).
002416,000948:    7133           00002                           TC       Q                             	#
002417,000949: 
002419,000951:                                                                                          	#          THE DOT PRODUCT SUBROUTINE USUALLY FORMS THE DOT PRODUCT OF THE VECTOR IN MPAC WITH A STANDARD SIX
002420,000952:                                                                                          	# REGISTER VECTOR WHOSE ADDRESS IS IN ADDRWD. IN THIS CASE C(DOTINC) ARE SET TO 2. VXM, HOWEVER, SETS C(DOTINC) TO
002421,000953:                                                                                          	# 6 SO THAT DOTSUB DOTS MPAC WITH A COLUMN VECTOR OF THE MATRIX IN QUESTION IN THIS CASE.
002422,000954: 
002423,000955: 
002424,000956: 
002425,000957:    7134           37656        PREDOT             CAF      TWO                           	# PROLOGUE TO SET DOTINC TO 2.
002426,000958:    7135           54122                           TS       DOTINC                        	#
002427,000959: 
002428,000960:    7136           00006        DOTSUB             EXTEND                                 	#
002429,000961:    7137           22123                           QXCH     DOTRET                        	# SAVE RETURN.
002430,000962:    7140           07067                           TC       DMPSUB                        	# DOT X COMPONENTS.
002431,000963:    7141           52144                           DXCH     MPAC       +3                 	# POSITION Y COMPONENT OF MPAC FOR
002432,000964:    7142           52141                           DXCH     MPAC                          	# MULTIPLICATION WHILE SAVING RESULT IN
002433,000965:    7143           52115                           DXCH     BUF                           	# THREE WORD BUFFER, BUF.
002434,000966:    7144           30142                           CA       MPAC       +2                 	#
002435,000967:    7145           54116                           TS       BUF        +2                 	#
002436,000968: 
002437,000969:    7146           30122                           CA       DOTINC                        	# ADVANCE ADDRWD TO Y COMPONENT OF
002438,000970:    7147           26102                           ADS      ADDRWD                        	# OTHER ARGUMENT.
002439,000971:    7150           07067                           TC       DMPSUB                        	#
002440,000972:    7151           52142                           DXCH     MPAC       +1                 	# ACCUMULATE PARTIAL PRODUCTS.
002441,000973:    7152           20116                           DAS      BUF        +1                 	#
002442,000974:    7153           60140                           AD       MPAC                          	#
002443,000975:    7154           60114                           AD       BUF                           	#
002444,000976:    7155           54114                           TS       BUF                           	#
002445,000977:    7156           17160                           TCF      +2                            	#
002446,000978:    7157           54105                           TS       OVFIND                        	# IF OVERFLOW OCCURS.
002447,000979: 
002448,000980:    7160           52146                           DXCH     MPAC       +5                 	# MULTIPLY Z COMPONENTS.
002449,000981:    7161           52141                           DXCH     MPAC                          	#
002450,000982:    7162           30122                           CA       DOTINC                        	#
002451,000983:    7163           26102                           ADS      ADDRWD                        	#
002452,000984:    7164           07067                           TC       DMPSUB                        	#
002453,000985:    7165           52116        ENDDOT             DXCH     BUF        +1                 	# LEAVE FINAL ACCUMULATION IN MPAC.
002454,000986:    7166           20142                           DAS      MPAC       +1                 	#
002455,000987:    7167           60140                           AD       MPAC                          	#
002456,000988:    7170           60114                           AD       BUF                           	#
002457,000989:    7171           54140                           TS       MPAC                          	#
002458,000990:    7172           00123                           TC       DOTRET                        	#
002459,000991: 
002460,000992:    7173           54105                           TS       OVFIND                        	# ON OVERFLOW HERE.
002461,000993:    7174           00123                           TC       DOTRET                        	#
002462,000994: 
002464,000996:                                                                                          	# DOUBLE PRECISION POLYNOMIAL EVALUATOR
002465,000997: 
002466,000998:                                                                                          	#                                    N        N-1
002467,000999:                                                                                          	#          THIS ROUTINE EVALUATES A X  + A   X    + ... + A  X + A  LEAVING THE DP RESULT IN MPAC ON EXIT.
002468,001000:                                                                                          	#                                  N      N-1              1      0
002469,001001: 
002470,001002:                                                                                          	# THE ROUTINE HAS TWO ENTRIES
002471,001003: 
002472,001004:                                                                                          	#          1. ENTRY THRU POWRSERS. THE COEFFICIENTS MAY BE EITHER IN FIXED OR ERASABLE, THE CALL IS BY
002473,001005:                                                                                          	#             TC POWRSERS, AND THE RETURN IS TO LOC(TC POWRSERS)+1. THE ENTERING DATA MUST BE AS FOLLOWS
002474,001006: 
002475,001007:                                                                                          	#                                         A        SP     LOC-3           ADDRESS FOR REFERENCING COEF TABLE
002476,001008:                                                                                          	#                                         L        SP     N-1             N IS THE DEGREE OF THE POWER SERIES
002477,001009:                                                                                          	#                                         MPAC     DP     X               ARGUMENT
002478,001010: 
002479,001011:                                                                                          	#                                         LOC-2N   DP     A(0)
002480,001012:                                                                                          	#                                                  ...
002481,001013:                                                                                          	#                                         LOC      DP     A(N)
002482,001014:
