002483,001015:                                                                                          	#          2. ENTRY THRU POLY. THE CALL TO POLY AND THE ENTERING DATA MUST BE AS FOLLOWS
002484,001016: 
002485,001017:                                                                                          	#                                         MPAC     DP     X               ARGUMENT
002486,001018: 
002487,001019:                                                                                          	#                                         LOC      TC     POLY
002488,001020:                                                                                          	#                                         LOC+1    SP     N-1
002489,001021:                                                                                          	#                                         LOC+2    DP     A(0)
002490,001022:                                                                                          	#                                                  ...
002491,001023:                                                                                          	#                                         LOC+2N+2 DP     A(N)            RETURN IS TO LOC+2N+4
002492,001024: 
002493,001025:    7175           00006        POWRSERS           EXTEND                                 	#
002494,001026:    7176           22125                           QXCH     POLYRET                       	# RETURN ADDRESS
002495,001027:    7177           54103                           TS       POLISH                        	# POWER SERIES ADDRESS
002496,001028:    7200           22124                           LXCH     POLYCNT                       	# N-1 TO COUNTER
002497,001029:    7201           17212                           TCF      POLYCOM                       	# SKIP SET UP BY POLY
002498,001030: 
002499,001031:    7202           50002        POLY               INDEX    Q                             	#
002500,001032:    7203           30000                           CAF      0                             	#
002501,001033:    7204           54124                           TS       POLYCNT                       	# N-1 TO COUNTER
002502,001034:    7205           60000                           DOUBLE                                 	#
002503,001035:    7206           60002                           AD       Q                             	#
002504,001036:    7207           54103                           TS       POLISH                        	# L(A(N))-3 TO POLISH
002505,001037:    7210           67664                           AD       FIVE                          	#
002506,001038:    7211           54125                           TS       POLYRET                       	# STORE RETURN ADDRESS
002507,001039: 
002508,001040:    7212           37677        POLYCOM            CAF      LVBUF                         	# INCOMING X WILL BE MOVED TO VBUF, SO
002509,001041:    7213           54102                           TS       ADDRWD                        	# SET ADDRWD SO DMPSUB WILL MPY BY VBUF.
002510,001042: 
002511,001043:    7214           00006                           EXTEND                                 	#
002512,001044:    7215           50103                           INDEX    POLISH                        	#
002513,001045:    7216           30004                           DCA      3                             	#
002514,001046: 
002516,001048:    7217           52141                           DXCH     MPAC                          	# LOAD A(N) INTO MPAC.
002517,001049:    7220           52107                           DXCH     VBUF                          	# SAVING X IN VBUF
002518,001050:    7221           17225                           TCF      POLY2                         	#
002519,001051: 
002520,001052:    7222           54124        POLYLOOP           TS       POLYCNT                       	# SAVE DECREMENTED LOOP COUNTER
002521,001053:    7223           47656                           CS       TWO                           	#
002522,001054:    7224           26103                           ADS      POLISH                        	# REGRESS COEFFICIENT POINTER
002523,001055: 
002524,001056:    7225           07067        POLY2              TC       DMPSUB                        	# MULTIPLY BY X
002525,001057:    7226           00006                           EXTEND                                 	#
002526,001058:    7227           50103                           INDEX    POLISH                        	#
002527,001059:    7230           30002                           DCA      1                             	# ADD IN NEXT COEFFICIENT
002528,001060:    7231           20141                           DAS      MPAC                          	# USER'S RESPONSIBILITY TO ASSURE NO OVFLOW
002529,001061: 
002530,001062:    7232           10124                           CCS      POLYCNT                       	#
002531,001063:    7233           17222                           TCF      POLYLOOP                      	#
002532,001064:    7234           00125                           TC       POLYRET                       	# RETURN CALLER
002533,001065: 
002535,001067:                                                                                          	#          MISCELLANEOUS MULTI-PRECISION ROUTINES REQUIRED IN FIXED-FIXED BUT NOT USED BY THE INTERPRETER.
002536,001068: 
002537,001069:    7235           00006        TPAGREE            EXTEND                                 	# FORCE SIGN AGREEMENT AMONG THE TRIPLE-
002538,001070:    7236           22114                           QXCH     BUF                           	# PRECISION CONTENTS OF MPAC, RETURNING
002539,001071:    7237           06711                           TC       BRANCH                        	# WITH SIGNUM OF THE INPUT IN A.
002540,001072:    7240           17244                           TCF      ARG+                          	#
002541,001073:    7241           17264                           TCF      ARGZERO                       	#
002542,001074: 
002543,001075:    7242           47637                           CS       POSMAX                        	# IF NEGATIVE.
002544,001076:    7243           17245                           TCF      +2                            	#
002545,001077: 
002546,001078:    7244           37637        ARG+               CAF      POSMAX                        	#
002547,001079:    7245           54115                 +2        TS       BUF        +1                 	#
002548,001080:    7246           00006                           EXTEND                                 	#
002549,001081:    7247           24000                           AUG      A                             	# FORMS +-1.0.
002550,001082:    7250           60142                           AD       MPAC       +2                 	#
002551,001083:    7251           54142                           TS       MPAC       +2                 	#
002552,001084:    7252           37665                           CAF      ZERO                          	#
002553,001085:    7253           60115                           AD       BUF        +1                 	#
002554,001086:    7254           60141                           AD       MPAC       +1                 	#
002555,001087:    7255           54141                           TS       MPAC       +1                 	#
002556,001088:    7256           37665                           CAF      ZERO                          	#
002557,001089:    7257           60115                           AD       BUF        +1                 	#
002558,001090:    7260           60140                           AD       MPAC                          	#
002559,001091:    7261           54140        ARGZERO2           TS       MPAC                          	# ALWAYS SKIPPING UNLESS ARGZERO.
002560,001092:    7262           54141                           TS       MPAC       +1                 	#
002561,001093:    7263           00114                           TC       BUF                           	# RETURN.
002562,001094: 
002563,001095:    7264           54142        ARGZERO            TS       MPAC       +2                 	# SET ALL THREE MPAC REGISTERS TO ZERO.
002564,001096:    7265           17261                           TCF      ARGZERO2                      	#
002565,001097: 
002566,001098:                                                                                          	#          SHORTMP MULTIPLIES THE TP CONTENTS OF MPAC BY THE SINGLE PRECISION NUMBER ARRIVING IN A.
002567,001099: 
002568,001100:    7266           54121        SHORTMP            TS       MPTEMP                        	#
002569,001101:    7267           00006                           EXTEND                                 	#
002570,001102:    7270           70142                           MP       MPAC       +2                 	#
002571,001103:    7271           54142                           TS       MPAC       +2                 	#
002572,001104:    7272           37665                           CAF      ZERO                          	# SO SUBSEQUENT DAS WILL WORK.
002573,001105:    7273           56141                           XCH      MPAC       +1                 	#
002574,001106:    7274           00006                           EXTEND                                 	#
002575,001107:    7275           70121                           MP       MPTEMP                        	#
002576,001108:    7276           20142                           DAS      MPAC       +1                 	#
002577,001109:    7277           56140                           XCH      MPAC                          	# SETTING MAPC TO 0.
002578,001110:    7300           00006                           EXTEND                                 	#
002579,001111:    7301           70121                           MP       MPTEMP                        	#
002580,001112:    7302           20141                           DAS      MPAC                          	#
002581,001113:    7303           00002                           TC       Q                             	#
002582,001114: 
002584,001116:                                                                                          	# MISCELLANEOUS VECTOR OPERATIONS. INCLUDED HERE ARE THE FOLLOWING.
002585,001117: 
002586,001118:                                                                                          	#          1.  DOT                DP VECTOR DOT PRODUCT.
002587,001119:                                                                                          	#          2.  VXV                DP VECTOR CROSS PRODUCT.
002588,001120:                                                                                          	#          3.  VXSC               DP VECTOR TIMES SCALAR.
002589,001121:                                                                                          	#          4.  V/SC               DP VECTOR DIVIDED BY SCALAR.
002590,001122:                                                                                          	#          5.  VPROJ              DP VECTOR PROJECTION. ( (MPAC.X)MPAC ).
002591,001123:                                                                                          	#          6.  VXM                DP VECTOR POST-MULTIPLIED BY MATRIX.
002592,001124:                                                                                          	#          7.  MXV                DP VECTOR PRE-MULTIPLIED BY MATRIX.
002593,001125: 
002594,001126:    7304           07134        DOT                TC       PREDOT                        	# DO THE DOT PRODUCT AND EXIT, CHANGING
002595,001127:    7305           37665                           CAF      ZERO                          	# THE MODE TO DP SCALAR.
002596,001128:    7306           16013                           TCF      NEWMODE                       	#
002597,001129: 
002598,001130: 
002599,001131: 
002600,001132:    7307           37656        MXV                CAF      TWO                           	# SET UP MATINC AND DOTINC FOR ROW
002601,001133:    7310           54124                           TS       MATINC                        	# VECTORS.
002602,001134:    7311           17315                           TCF      VXM/MXV                       	# GO TO COMMON PORTION.
002603,001135: 
002604,001136:    7312           47661        VXM                CS       TEN                           	# SET MATINC AND DOTINC TO REFER TO MATRIX
002605,001137:    7313           54124                           TS       MATINC                        	# AS THREE COLUMN VECTORS.
002606,001138:    7314           36162                           CAF      SIX                           	#
002607,001139: 
002609,001141:                                                                                          	#          COMMON PORTION OF MXV AND VXM.
002610,001142: 
002611,001143:    7315           54122        VXM/MXV            TS       DOTINC                        	#
002612,001144:    7316           07506                           TC       MPACVBUF                      	# SAVE VECTOR IN MPAC FOR FURTHER USE.
002613,001145: 
002614,001146:    7317           07136                           TC       DOTSUB                        	# GO DOT TO GET X COMPONENT OF ANSWER.
002615,001147:    7320           00006                           EXTEND                                 	#
002616,001148:    7321           30107                           DCA      VBUF                          	# MOVE MPAC VECTOR BACK INTO MPAC, SAVING
002617,001149:    7322           52141                           DXCH     MPAC                          	# NEW X COMPONENT IN BUF2.
002618,001150:    7323           52120                           DXCH     BUF2                          	#
002619,001151:    7324           00006                           EXTEND                                 	#
002620,001152:    7325           30111                           DCA      VBUF       +2                 	#
002621,001153:    7326           52144                           DXCH     MPAC       +3                 	#
002622,001154:    7327           00006                           EXTEND                                 	#
002623,001155:    7330           30113                           DCA      VBUF       +4                 	#
002624,001156:    7331           52146                           DXCH     MPAC       +5                 	#
002625,001157:    7332           30124                           CA       MATINC                        	# INITIALIZE ADDRWD FOR NEXT DOT PRODUCT.
002626,001158:    7333           26102                           ADS      ADDRWD                        	# FORMS BASE ADDRESS OF NEXT COLUMN(ROW).
002627,001159: 
002628,001160:    7334           07136                           TC       DOTSUB                        	#
002629,001161:    7335           52107                           DXCH     VBUF                          	# MORE GIVEN VECTOR BACK TO MPAC, SAVING Y
002630,001162:    7336           52141                           DXCH     MPAC                          	# COMPONENT OF ANSWER IN VBUF +2.
002631,001163:    7337           52111                           DXCH     VBUF       +2                 	#
002632,001164:    7340           52144                           DXCH     MPAC       +3                 	#
002633,001165:    7341           52113                           DXCH     VBUF       +4                 	#
002634,001166:    7342           52146                           DXCH     MPAC       +5                 	#
002635,001167:    7343           30124                           CA       MATINC                        	# FORM ADDRESS OF LAST COLUMN OR ROW.
002636,001168:    7344           26102                           ADS      ADDRWD                        	#
002637,001169: 
002638,001170:    7345           07136                           TC       DOTSUB                        	#
002639,001171:    7346           52120                           DXCH     BUF2                          	# ANSWER NOW COMPLETE. PUT COMPONENTS INTO
002640,001172:    7347           52141                           DXCH     MPAC                          	# PROPER MPAC REGISTERS.
002641,001173:    7350           52146                           DXCH     MPAC       +5                 	#
002642,001174:    7351           52111                           DXCH     VBUF       +2                 	#
002643,001175:    7352           52144                           DXCH     MPAC       +3                 	#
002644,001176:    7353           16014                           TCF      DANZIG                        	# EXIT.
002645,001177: 
002647,001179:                                                                                          	#          VXSC - VECTOR TIMES SCALAR.
002648,001180: 
002649,001181:    7354           10147        VXSC               CCS      MODE                          	# TEST PRESENT MODE.
002650,001182:    7355           17403                           TCF      DVXSC                         	# SEPARATE ROUTINE WHEN SCALAR IS IN MPAC.
002651,001183:    7356           17403                           TCF      DVXSC                         	#
002652,001184: 
002653,001185:    7357           07067        VVXSC              TC       DMPSUB                        	# COMPUTE X COMPONENT
002654,001186:    7360           07120                           TC       VROUND                        	# AND ROUND IT.
002655,001187:    7361           52144                           DXCH     MPAC       +3                 	# PUT Y COMPONENT INTO MPAC SAVING MPAC IN
002656,001188:    7362           52141                           DXCH     MPAC                          	# MPAC +3.
002657,001189:    7363           52144                           DXCH     MPAC       +3                 	#
002658,001190: 
002659,001191:    7364           07067                           TC       DMPSUB                        	# DO SAME FOR Y AND Z COMPONENTS.
002660,001192:    7365           07120                           TC       VROUND                        	#
002661,001193:    7366           52146                           DXCH     MPAC       +5                 	#
002662,001194:    7367           52141                           DXCH     MPAC                          	#
002663,001195:    7370           52146                           DXCH     MPAC       +5                 	#
002664,001196: 
002665,001197:    7371           07067                           TC       DMPSUB                        	#
002666,001198:    7372           07120                           TC       VROUND                        	#
002667,001199:    7373           52141        VROTATEX           DXCH     MPAC                          	# EXIT USED TO RESTORE MPAC AFTER THIS
002668,001200:    7374           52146                           DXCH     MPAC       +5                 	# TYPE OF ROTATION. CALLED BY VECTOR SHIFT
002669,001201:    7375           52144                           DXCH     MPAC       +3                 	# RIGHT, V/SC, ETC.
002670,001202:    7376           52141                           DXCH     MPAC                          	#
002671,001203:    7377           16014                           TCF      DANZIG                        	#
002672,001204: 
002674,001206:                                                                                          	#          DP VECTOR PROJECTION ROUTINE.
002675,001207: 
002676,001208: 
002677,001209: 
002678,001210:    7400           07134        VPROJ              TC       PREDOT                        	# (MPAC.X)MPAC IS COMPUTED AND LEFT IN
002679,001211:    7401           47655                           CS       FOUR                          	# MPAC. DO DOT AND FALL INTO DVXSC.
002680,001212:    7402           26102                           ADS      ADDRWD                        	#
002681,001213: 
002682,001214:                                                                                          	#          VXSC WHEN SCALAR ARRIVES IN MPAC AND VECTOR IS AT X.
002683,001215: 
002684,001216:    7403           00006        DVXSC              EXTEND                                 	# SAVE SCALAR IN MPAC +3 AND GET X
002685,001217:    7404           30141                           DCA      MPAC                          	# COMPONENT OF ANSWER.
002686,001218:    7405           52144                           DXCH     MPAC       +3                 	#
002687,001219:    7406           07067                           TC       DMPSUB                        	#
002688,001220:    7407           07120                           TC       VROUND                        	#
002689,001221: 
002690,001222:    7410           37656                           CAF      TWO                           	# ADVANCE ADDRWD TO Y COMPONENT OF X.
002691,001223:    7411           26102                           ADS      ADDRWD                        	#
002692,001224:    7412           00006                           EXTEND                                 	#
002693,001225:    7413           30144                           DCA      MPAC       +3                 	# PUT SCALAR BACK INTO MPAC AND SAVE
002694,001226:    7414           52141                           DXCH     MPAC                          	# X RESULT IN MPAC +5.
002695,001227:    7415           52146                           DXCH     MPAC       +5                 	#
002696,001228:    7416           07067                           TC       DMPSUB                        	#
002697,001229:    7417           07120                           TC       VROUND                        	#
002698,001230: 
002699,001231:    7420           37656                           CAF      TWO                           	#
002700,001232:    7421           26102                           ADS      ADDRWD                        	# TO Z COMPONENT.
002701,001233:    7422           52144                           DXCH     MPAC       +3                 	# BRING SCALAR BACK, PUTTING Y RESULT IN
002702,001234:    7423           52141                           DXCH     MPAC                          	# THE PROPER PLACE.
002703,001235:    7424           52144                           DXCH     MPAC       +3                 	#
002704,001236:    7425           07067                           TC       DMPSUB                        	#
002705,001237:    7426           07120                           TC       VROUND                        	#
002706,001238: 
002707,001239:    7427           52141                           DXCH     MPAC                          	# PUT Z COMPONENT IN PROPER PLACE, ALSO
002708,001240:    7430           52146                           DXCH     MPAC       +5                 	# POSITIONING X.
002709,001241:    7431           52141                           DXCH     MPAC                          	#
002710,001242: 
002711,001243:    7432           47657                           CS       ONE                           	# MODE HAS CHANGED TO VECTOR.
002712,001244:    7433           16013                           TCF      NEWMODE                       	#
002713,001245: 
002715,001247:                                                                                          	#          VECTOR CROSS PRODUCT ROUTINE CALCULATES (X M -X M ,X M -X M ,X M -X M ) WHERE M IS THE VECTOR IN
002716,001248:                                                                                          	#                                                    3 2  2 3  1 3  3 1  2 1  1 2
002717,001249:                                                                                          	# MPAC AND X THE VECTOR AT THE GIVEN ADDRESS.
002718,001250: 
002719,001251: 
002720,001252: 
002721,001253:    7434           00006        VXV                EXTEND                                 	#
002722,001254:    7435           30146                           DCA      MPAC       +5                 	# FORM UP M3X1, LEAVING M1 IN VBUF.
002723,001255:    7436           52141                           DXCH     MPAC                          	#
002724,001256:    7437           52107                           DXCH     VBUF                          	#
002725,001257:    7440           07067                           TC       DMPSUB                        	# BY X1.
002726,001258: 
002727,001259:    7441           00006                           EXTEND                                 	#
002728,001260:    7442           40144                           DCS      MPAC       +3                 	# CALCULATE -X1M2, SAVING X1M3 IN VBUF +2.
002729,001261:    7443           52141                           DXCH     MPAC                          	#
002730,001262:    7444           52111                           DXCH     VBUF       +2                 	#
002731,001263:    7445           07067                           TC       DMPSUB                        	#
002732,001264: 
002733,001265:    7446           37656                           CAF      TWO                           	# ADVANCE ADDRWD TO X2.
002734,001266:    7447           26102                           ADS      ADDRWD                        	#
002735,001267:    7450           00006                           EXTEND                                 	#
002736,001268:    7451           40146                           DCS      MPAC       +5                 	# PREPARE TO GET -X2M3, SAVING -X1M2 IN
002737,001269:    7452           52141                           DXCH     MPAC                          	# MPAC +5.
002738,001270:    7453           52146                           DXCH     MPAC       +5                 	#
002739,001271:    7454           07067                           TC       DMPSUB                        	#
002740,001272: 
002741,001273:    7455           00006                           EXTEND                                 	#
002742,001274:    7456           30107                           DCA      VBUF                          	# GET X2M1, SAVING -X2M3 IN VBUF +4.
002743,001275:    7457           52141                           DXCH     MPAC                          	#
002744,001276:    7460           52113                           DXCH     VBUF       +4                 	#
002745,001277:    7461           07067                           TC       DMPSUB                        	#
002746,001278: 
002747,001279:    7462           37656                           CAF      TWO                           	# ADVANCE ADDRWD TO X3.
002748,001280:    7463           26102                           ADS      ADDRWD                        	#
002749,001281:    7464           00006                           EXTEND                                 	#
002750,001282:    7465           40107                           DCS      VBUF                          	# GET -X3M1, ADDING X2M1 TO MPAC +5 TO
002751,001283:    7466           52141                           DXCH     MPAC                          	# COMPLETE THE Z COMPONENT OF THE ANSWER.
002752,001284:    7467           20146                           DAS      MPAC       +5                 	#
002753,001285: 
002754,001286:    7470           00006                           EXTEND                                 	#
002755,001287:    7471           17473                           BZF      +2                            	#
002756,001288:    7472           07007                           TC       OVERFLOW                      	#
002757,001289: 
002759,001291:    7473           07067                           TC       DMPSUB                        	#
002760,001292:    7474           52111                           DXCH     VBUF       +2                 	# MOVE X1M3 TO MPAC +3 SETTING UP FOR X3M2
002761,001293:    7475           52144                           DXCH     MPAC       +3                 	# AND ADD -X3M1 TO MPAC +3 TO COMPLETE THE
002762,001294:    7476           52141                           DXCH     MPAC                          	# Y COMPONENT OF THE RESULT.
002763,001295:    7477           20144                           DAS      MPAC       +3                 	#
002764,001296: 
002765,001297:    7500           00006                           EXTEND                                 	#
002766,001298:    7501           17503                           BZF      +2                            	#
002767,001299:    7502           07007                           TC       OVERFLOW                      	#
002768,001300: 
002769,001301:    7503           07067                           TC       DMPSUB                        	#
002770,001302:    7504           52113                           DXCH     VBUF       +4                 	# GO ADD -X2M3 TO X3M2 TO COMPLETE THE X
002771,001303:    7505           16754                           TCF      ENDVXV                        	# COMPONENT (TAIL END OF DAD).
002772,001304: 
002773,001305:                                                                                          	#          THE MPACVBUF SUBROUTINE SAVES THE VECTOR IN MPAC IN VBUF WITHOUT CLOBBERING MPAC.
002774,001306: 
002775,001307:    7506           00006        MPACVBUF           EXTEND                                 	# CALLED BY MXV, VXM, AND UNIT.
002776,001308:    7507           30141                           DCA      MPAC                          	#
002777,001309:    7510           52107                           DXCH     VBUF                          	#
002778,001310:    7511           00006                           EXTEND                                 	#
002779,001311:    7512           30144                           DCA      MPAC       +3                 	#
002780,001312:    7513           52111                           DXCH     VBUF       +2                 	#
002781,001313:    7514           00006                           EXTEND                                 	#
002782,001314:    7515           30146                           DCA      MPAC       +5                 	#
002783,001315:    7516           52113                           DXCH     VBUF       +4                 	#
002784,001316:    7517           00002                           TC       Q                             	# RETURN TO CALLER.
002785,001317: 
002787,001319:                                                                                          	#          INTERPRETIVE INSTRUCTIONS WHOSE EXECUTION CONSISTS OF PRINCIPALLY CALLING SUBROUTINES.
002788,001320: 
002789,001321:    7520           07067        DMP1               TC       DMPSUB                        	# DMP INSTRUCTIONS
002790,001322:    7521           16014                           TCF      DANZIG                        	#
002791,001323: 
002792,001324:    7522           07067        DMPR               TC       DMPSUB                        	#
002793,001325:    7523           07117                           TC       ROUNDSUB   +1                 	# (C(A) = +0).
002794,001326:    7524           16014                           TCF      DANZIG                        	#
002795,001327: 
002796,001328:    7525           00006        DDV                EXTEND                                 	#
002797,001329:    7526           50102                           INDEX    ADDRWD                        	# MOVE DIVIDEND INTO BUF.
002798,001330:    7527           30001                           DCA      0                             	#
002799,001331:    7530           17535                           TCF      BDDV       +4                 	#
002800,001332: 
002801,001333:    7531           00006        BDDV               EXTEND                                 	# MOVE DIVISOR INTO MPAC SAVING MPAC, THE
002802,001334:    7532           50102                           INDEX    ADDRWD                        	# DIVIDEND, IN BUF.
002803,001335:    7533           30001                           DCA      0                             	#
002804,001336:    7534           52141                           DXCH     MPAC                          	#
002805,001337:    7535           52115                 +4        DXCH     BUF                           	#
002806,001338:    7536           37665                           CAF      ZERO                          	# DIVIDE ROUTINES IN BANK 0.
002807,001339:    7537           54004                           TS       FBANK                         	#
002808,001340:    7540           12332                           TCF      DDV/BDDV                      	#
002809,001341: 
002810,001342:    7541           30102        SETPD              CA       ADDRWD                        	# ANYWHERE IN ERASABLE IN GENERAL, BUT
002811,001343:    7542           54152                           TS       PUSHLOC                       	# ALMOST ALWAYS IN THE WORK AREA.
002812,001344:    7543           16016                           TCF      NOIBNKSW                      	# NO FBANK SWITCH REQUIRED.
002813,001345: 
002814,001346:    7544           37665        TSLC               CAF      ZERO                          	# SHIFTING ROUTINES LOCATED IN BANK 00.
002815,001347:    7545           54004                           TS       FBANK                         	#
002816,001348:    7546           12153                           TCF      TSLC2                         	#
002817,001349: 
002818,001350:    7547           36027        GSHIFT             CAF      LOW7                          	# USED AS MASK AT GENSHIFT. THIS PROCESSES
002819,001351:    7550           54004                           TS       FBANK                         	# ANY SHIFT INSTRUCTION (EXCEPT TSLC) WITH
002820,001352:    7551           12174                           TCF      GENSHIFT                      	# AN ADDRESS (ROUTINES IN BANK 0).
002821,001353: 
002823,001355:                                                                                          	#          THE FOLLOWING IS THE PROLOGUE TO V/SC. IF THE PRESENT MODE IS VECTOR, IT SAVES THE SCALAR AT X IN BUF
002824,001356:                                                                                          	# AND CALLS THE V/SC ROUTINE IN BANK 0. IF THE PRESENT MODE IS SCALAR, IT MOVES THE VECTOR AT X INTO MPAC, SAVING
002825,001357:                                                                                          	# THE SCALAR IN MPAC IN BUF BEFORE CALLING THE V/SC ROUTINE IN BANK 0.
002826,001358: 
002827,001359:    7552           10147        V/SC               CCS      MODE                          	#
002828,001360:    7553           17564                           TCF      DV/SC                         	# MOVE VECTOR INTO MPAC.
002829,001361:    7554           17564                           TCF      DV/SC                         	#
002830,001362: 
002831,001363:    7555           00006        VV/SC              EXTEND                                 	#
002832,001364:    7556           50102                           INDEX    ADDRWD                        	#
002833,001365:    7557           30001                           DCA      0                             	#
002834,001366:    7560           52115        V/SC1              DXCH     BUF                           	# IN BOTH CASES, VECTOR IS NOW IN MPAC AND
002835,001367:    7561           37665                           CAF      ZERO                          	# SCALAR IN BUF.
002836,001368:    7562           54004                           TS       FBANK                         	#
002837,001369:    7563           12576                           TCF      V/SC2                         	#
002838,001370: 
002839,001371:    7564           00006        DV/SC              EXTEND                                 	#
002840,001372:    7565           50102                           INDEX    ADDRWD                        	#
002841,001373:    7566           30003                           DCA      2                             	#
002842,001374:    7567           52144                           DXCH     MPAC       +3                 	#
002843,001375:    7570           00006                           EXTEND                                 	#
002844,001376:    7571           50102                           INDEX    ADDRWD                        	#
002845,001377:    7572           30005                           DCA      4                             	#
002846,001378:    7573           52146                           DXCH     MPAC       +5                 	#
002847,001379: 
002848,001380:    7574           47657                           CS       ONE                           	# CHANGE MODE TO VECTOR.
002849,001381:    7575           54147                           TS       MODE                          	#
002850,001382: 
002851,001383:    7576           00006                           EXTEND                                 	#
002852,001384:    7577           50102                           INDEX    ADDRWD                        	#
002853,001385:    7600           30001                           DCA      0                             	#
002854,001386:    7601           52141                           DXCH     MPAC                          	#
002855,001387:    7602           17560                           TCF      V/SC1                         	# FINISH PROLOGUE AT COMMON SECTION.
002856,001388: 
002858,001390:                                                                                          	#          SIGN AND COMPLEMENT INSTRUCTIONS.
002859,001391: 
002860,001392:    7603           50102        SIGN               INDEX    ADDRWD                        	# CALL COMP INSTRUCTION IF WORD AT X IS
002861,001393:    7604           10000                           CCS      0                             	# NEGATIVE NON-ZERO.
002862,001394:    7605           16016                           TCF      NOIBNKSW                      	#
002863,001395:    7606           17610                           TCF      +2                            	#
002864,001396:    7607           17616                           TCF      COMP                          	# DO THE COMPLEMENT.
002865,001397: 
002866,001398:    7610           50102                           INDEX    ADDRWD                        	#
002867,001399:    7611           10001                           CCS      1                             	#
002868,001400:    7612           16016                           TCF      NOIBNKSW                      	# NO FBANK SWITCH REQIURED.
002869,001401:    7613           16016                           TCF      NOIBNKSW                      	# NO FBANK SWITCH REQUIRED.
002870,001402:    7614           17616                           TCF      COMP                          	#
002871,001403:    7615           16016                           TCF      NOIBNKSW                      	# NO FBANK SWITCH REQUIRED.
002872,001404: 
002873,001405: 
002874,001406: 
002875,001407:    7616           00006        COMP               EXTEND                                 	# COMPLEMENT DP MPAC IN EVERY CASE.
002876,001408:    7617           40141                           DCS      MPAC                          	#
002877,001409:    7620           52141                           DXCH     MPAC                          	#
002878,001410: 
002879,001411:    7621           10147                           CCS      MODE                          	# EITHER COMPLEMENT MPAC +3 OR THE REST OF
002880,001412:    7622           17633                           TCF      DCOMP                         	# THE VECTOR ACCUMULATOR.
002881,001413:    7623           17633                           TCF      DCOMP                         	#
002882,001414: 
002883,001415:    7624           00006                           EXTEND                                 	# VECTOR COMPLEMENT.
002884,001416:    7625           40144                           DCS      MPAC       +3                 	#
002885,001417:    7626           52144                           DXCH     MPAC       +3                 	#
002886,001418:    7627           00006                           EXTEND                                 	#
002887,001419:    7630           40146                           DCS      MPAC       +5                 	#
002888,001420:    7631           52146                           DXCH     MPAC       +5                 	#
002889,001421:    7632           16014                           TCF      DANZIG                        	#
002890,001422: 
002891,001423:    7633           40142        DCOMP              CS       MPAC       +2                 	#
002892,001424:    7634           54142                           TS       MPAC       +2                 	#
002893,001425:    7635           16014                           TCF      DANZIG                        	#
002894,001426: 
002896,001428:                                                                                          	#          CONSTANTS REQUIRED IN FIXED-FIXED
002897,001429: 
002898,001430:    7636           37777        DPOSMAX            OCT      37777                         	#
002899,001431:    7637           37777        POSMAX             OCT      37777                         	#
002900,001432:    7640     7640               LIMITS             EQUALS   POSMAX     +1                 	#
002901,001433:    7640           57777        NEG1/2             OCT      -20000                        	# MUST BE TWO LOCATIONS AHEAD OF POS1/2.
002902,001434: 
002903,001435:    7641           40000        BIT15              OCT      40000                         	# BIT TABLE FOLLOWS.
002904,001436:    7642           20000        BIT14              OCT      20000                         	#
002905,001437:    7643           10000        BIT13              OCT      10000                         	#
002906,001438:    7644           04000        BIT12              OCT      04000                         	#
002907,001439:    7645           02000        BIT11              OCT      02000                         	#
002908,001440:    7646           01000        BIT10              OCT      01000                         	#
002909,001441:    7647           00400        BIT9               OCT      00400                         	#
002910,001442:    7650           00200        BIT8               OCT      00200                         	#
002911,001443:    7651           00100        BIT7               OCT      00100                         	#
002912,001444:    7652           00040        BIT6               OCT      00040                         	#
002913,001445:    7653           00020        BIT5               OCT      00020                         	#
002914,001446:    7654           00010        BIT4               OCT      00010                         	#
002915,001447:    7655           00004        BIT3               OCT      00004                         	#
002916,001448:    7656           00002        BIT2               OCT      00002                         	#
002917,001449:    7657           00001        BIT1               OCT      00001                         	#
002918,001450: 
002919,001451:    7660     7641               NEGMAX             EQUALS   BIT15                         	#
002920,001452:    7660     7642               HALF               EQUALS   BIT14                         	#
002921,001453:    7660     7642               POS1/2             EQUALS   HALF                          	#
002922,001454:    7660     7643               QUARTER            EQUALS   BIT13                         	#
002923,001455:    7660     7645               2K                 EQUALS   BIT11                         	#
002924,001456:    7660           00013        ELEVEN             DEC      11         B-14               	#
002925,001457:    7661     7660               NOUTCON            =        ELEVEN                        	#
002926,001458:    7661           00012        TEN                DEC      10         B-14               	#
002927,001459:    7662           00011        NINE               DEC      9          B-14               	#
002928,001460:    7663     7642               EIHGT              EQUALS   BIT14                         	#
002929,001461:    7663           00007        SEVEN              OCT      7                             	#
002930,001462:    7664     6162               SIX                EQUALS   REVCNT                        	#
002931,001463:    7664           00005        FIVE               OCT      5                             	#
002932,001464:    7665     7655               FOUR               EQUALS   BIT3                          	#
002933,001465:    7665     6165               THREE              EQUALS   NO.WDS     +1                 	#
002934,001466:    7665     7656               TWO                EQUALS   BIT2                          	#
002935,001467:    7665     7657               ONE                EQUALS   BIT1                          	#
002936,001468:    7665           00000        ZERO               OCT      0                             	#
002937,001469:    7666           77777        NEGO               OCT      77777                         	#
002938,001470:    7667           77776        NEGONE             DEC      -1         B-14               	#
002939,001471: 
002940,001472:    7670     7667               NEG1               =        NEGONE                        	#
002941,001473:    7670     7667               MINUS1             EQUALS   NEG1                          	#
002942,001474:    7670           77775        NEG2               OCT      77775                         	#
002943,001475:    7671           77774        NEG3               DEC      -3         B-14               	#
002944,001476:    7672           00777        LOW9               OCT      777                           	#
002945,001477:    7673           00017        LOW4               OCT      17                            	#
002946,001478: 
002948,001480:    7674     7663               LOW3               EQUALS   SEVEN                         	#
002949,001481:    7674     6165               LOW2               EQUALS   THREE                         	#
002950,001482: 
002951,001483:    7674           00030        CALLCODE           OCT      00030                         	#
002952,001484:    7675           40014        DLOADCOD           OCT      40014                         	#
002953,001485:    7676     7641               VLOADCOD           EQUALS   BIT15                         	#
002954,001486:    7676           40015        DLOAD*             OCT      40015                         	#
002955,001487:    7677     6042               VLOAD*             EQUALS   OCT40001                      	#
002956,001488:    7677           00106        LVBUF              ADRES    VBUF                          	#
002957,001489:    7700           30000        BIT13-14           OCTAL    30000                         	#
002958,001490:    7701                        ENDINTF            EQUALS                                 	#
002959,001491: 
002961,001493:                                                                                          	# SHIFTING AND ROUNDING PACKAGE.
002962,001494: 
002963,001495:                                                                                          	#          THE FOLLOWING SHORT SHIFT CODES REQUIRE NO ADDRESS WORD:
002964,001496: 
002965,001497:                                                                                          	#          1.  SR1 TO SR4         SCALAR SHIFT RIGHT.
002966,001498:                                                                                          	#          2.  SR1R TO SR4R       SCALAR SHIFT RIGHT AND ROUND.
002967,001499:                                                                                          	#          3.  SL1 TO SL4         SCALAR SHIFT LEFT.
002968,001500:                                                                                          	#          4.  SL1R TO SL4R       SCALAR SHIFT LEFT AND ROUND.
002969,001501: 
002970,001502:                                                                                          	#          5.  VSR1 TO VSR8       VECTOR SHIFT RIGHT (ALWAYS ROUNDS).
002971,001503:                                                                                          	#          6.  VSL1 TO VSL8       VECTOR SHIFT LEFT (NEVER ROUNDS).
002972,001504: 
002973,001505:                                                                                          	#          THE FOLLOWING CODES REQUIRE AND ADDRESS WHICH MAY BE INDEXED:*
002974,001506: 
002975,001507:                                                                                          	#          1.  SR                 SCALAR SHIFT RIGHT.
002976,001508:                                                                                          	#          2.  SRR                SCALAR SHIFT RIGHT AND ROUND.
002977,001509:                                                                                          	#          3.  SL                 SCALAR SHIFT LEFT.
002978,001510:                                                                                          	#          4.  SLR                SCALAR SHIFT LEFT AND ROUND.
002979,001511: 
002980,001512:                                                                                          	#          5.  VSR                VECTOR SHIFT RIGHT.
002981,001513:                                                                                          	#          6.  VSL                VECTOR SHIFT LEFT.
002982,001514: 
002983,001515:                                                                                          	# *  IF THE ADDRESS IS INDEXED, AND THE INDEX MODIFICATION RESULTS IN A NEGATIVE SHIFT COUNT, A SHIFT OF THE
002984,001516:                                                                                          	# ABSOLUTE VALUE OF THE COUNT IS DONE IN THE OPPOSITE DIRECTION.
002985,001517: 
002986,001518: 
002987,001519: 00,2000                                           SETLOC   10000                         	# BANK 0 PORTION FOLLOWS.
002988,001520: 
002989,001521: 00,2000           36162        SHORTT             CAF      SIX                           	# SCALAR SHORT SHIFTS COME HERE. THE SHIFT
002990,001522: 00,2001           70020                           MASK     CYR                           	# COUNT-1 IS NOW IN BITS 2-3 OF CYR. THE
002991,001523: 00,2002           54021                           TS       SR                            	# ROUNDING BIT IS IN BIT1 AT THIS POINT.
002992,001524: 
002993,001525: 00,2003           10020                           CCS      CYR                           	# SEE IF RIGHT OR LEFT SHIFT DESIRED.
002994,001526: 00,2004           12062                           TCF      TSSL                          	# SHIFT LEFT.
002995,001527: 
002996,001528: 00,2005           00024        SRDDV              DEC      20         B-14               	# MPTEMP SETTING FOR SR BEFORE DDV.
002997,001529: 
002998,001530: 00,2006           50021        TSSR               INDEX    SR                            	# GET SHIFTING BIT.
002999,001531: 00,2007           37642                           CAF      BIT14                         	#
003000,001532: 00,2010           54121                           TS       MPTEMP                        	#
003001,001533: 
003002,001534: 00,2011           10020                           CCS      CYR                           	# SEE IF A ROUND IS DESIRED.
003003,001535: 00,2012           02031        RIGHTR             TC       MPACSRND                      	# YES - SHIFT RIGHT AND ROUND.
003004,001536: 00,2013           16013                           TCF      NEWMODE                       	# SET MODE TO DP (C(A) = 0).
003005,001537: 00,2014           30121        MPACSHR            CA       MPTEMP                        	# DO A TRIPLE PRECISION SHIFT RIGHT.
003006,001538: 00,2015           00006                           EXTEND                                 	#
003007,001539: 00,2016           70142                           MP       MPAC       +2                 	#
003008,001540: 00,2017           54142                 +3        TS       MPAC       +2                 	# (EXIT FROM SQRT AND ABVAL).
003009,001541: 00,2020           30121                           CA       MPTEMP                        	#
003010,001542: 
003012,001544: 00,2021           00006                           EXTEND                                 	#
003013,001545: 00,2022           70140                           MP       MPAC                          	# SHIFT MAJOR PART INTO A,L AND PLACE IN
003014,001546: 00,2023           52141                           DXCH     MPAC                          	# MPAC,+1.
003015,001547: 00,2024           30121                           CA       MPTEMP                        	#
003016,001548: 00,2025           00006                           EXTEND                                 	#
003017,001549: 00,2026           70001                           MP       L                             	# ORIGINAL C(MPAC +1).
003018,001550: 00,2027           20142                           DAS      MPAC       +1                 	# GUARANTEED NO OVERFLOW.
003019,001551: 00,2030           16014                           TCF      DANZIG                        	#
003020,001552: 
003021,001553:                                                                                          	#          MPAC SHIFT RIGHT AND ROUND SUBROUTINES
003022,001554: 
003023,001555: 00,2031           30142        MPACSRND           CA       MPAC       +2                 	# WE HAVE TO DO ALL THREE MULTIPLIES SINCE
003024,001556: 00,2032           00006                           EXTEND                                 	# MPAC +1 AND MPAC +2 MIGHT HAVE SIGN
003025,001557: 00,2033           70121                           MP       MPTEMP                        	# DISAGREEMENT WITH A SHIFT RIGHT OF 1.
003026,001558: 00,2034           56141                           XCH      MPAC       +1                 	#
003027,001559: 00,2035           00006                           EXTEND                                 	#
003028,001560: 00,2036           70121                           MP       MPTEMP                        	#
003029,001561: 00,2037           56141                           XCH      MPAC       +1                 	# TRIAL MINOR PART.
003030,001562: 00,2040           60001                           AD       L                             	#
003031,001563: 
003032,001564: 00,2041           60000        VSHR2              DOUBLE                                 	# (FINISH VECTOR COMPONENT SHIFT RIGHT
003033,001565: 00,2042           54142                           TS       MPAC       +2                 	# AND ROUND.
003034,001566: 00,2043           12045                           TCF      +2                            	#
003035,001567: 00,2044           26141                           ADS      MPAC       +1                 	# GUARANTEED NO OVERFLOW.
003036,001568: 
003037,001569: 00,2045           37665                           CAF      ZERO                          	#
003038,001570: 00,2046           54142                           TS       MPAC       +2                 	#
003039,001571: 00,2047           56140                           XCH      MPAC                          	# SETTING TO ZERO SO FOLLOWING DAS WORKS.
003040,001572: 00,2050           00006                           EXTEND                                 	#
003041,001573: 00,2051           70121                           MP       MPTEMP                        	#
003042,001574: 00,2052           20141                           DAS      MPAC                          	# AGAIN NO OVERFLOW.
003043,001575: 00,2053           00002                           TC       Q                             	#
003044,001576: 
003045,001577: 00,2054           30121        VSHRRND            CA       MPTEMP                        	# ENTRY TO SHIFT RIGHT AND ROUND MPAC WHEN
003046,001578: 00,2055           00006                           EXTEND                                 	# MPAC CONTAINS A VECTOR COMPONENT.
003047,001579: 00,2056           70141                           MP       MPAC       +1                 	#
003048,001580: 00,2057           54141                           TS       MPAC       +1                 	#
003049,001581: 00,2060           56001                           XCH      L                             	#
003050,001582: 00,2061           12041                           TCF      VSHR2                         	# GO ADD ONE IF NECESSARY AND FINISH.
003051,001583: 
003053,001585:                                                                                          	#          ROUTINE FOR SHORT SCALAR SHIFT LEFT (AND MAYBE ROUND).
003054,001586: 
003055,001587: 00,2062           30021        TSSL               CA       SR                            	# GET SHIFT COUNT FOR SR.
003056,001588: 00,2063           54121                 +1        TS       MPTEMP                        	#
003057,001589: 
003058,001590: 00,2064           00006                 +2        EXTEND                                 	# ENTRY HERE FROM SL FOR SCALARS.
003059,001591: 00,2065           30142                           DCA      MPAC       +1                 	# SHIFTING LEFT ONE PLACE AT A TIME IS
003060,001592: 00,2066           20142                           DAS      MPAC       +1                 	# FASTER THAN DOING THE WHOLE SHIFT WITH
003061,001593: 00,2067           60140                           AD       MPAC                          	# MULTIPLIES ASSUMING THAT FREQUENCY OF
003062,001594: 00,2070           60140                           AD       MPAC                          	# SHIFT COUNTS GOES DOWN RAPIDLY AS A
003063,001595: 00,2071           54140                           TS       MPAC                          	# FUNCTION OF THEIR MAGNITUDE.
003064,001596: 00,2072           12074                           TCF      +2                            	#
003065,001597: 00,2073           54105                           TS       OVFIND                        	# OVERFLOW. (LEAVES OVERFLOW-CORRECTED
003066,001598:                                                                                          	# RESULT ANYWAY).
003067,001599: 00,2074           10121                           CCS      MPTEMP                        	# LOOP ON DECREMENTED SHIFT COUNT.
003068,001600: 00,2075           12063                           TCF      TSSL       +1                 	#
003069,001601: 
003070,001602: 00,2076           10020                           CCS      CYR                           	# SEE IF ROUND WANTED.
003071,001603: 00,2077           07116        ROUND              TC       ROUNDSUB                      	# YES - ROUND AND EXIT.
003072,001604: 00,2100           16014                           TCF      DANZIG                        	# SL LEAVES A ZERO IN CYR FOR NO ROUND.
003073,001605: 00,2101           16014                           TCF      DANZIG                        	# NO - EXIT IMMEDIATELY
003074,001606: 
003076,001608:                                                                                          	# VECTOR SHIFTING ROUTINES.
003077,001609: 
003078,001610: 00,2102           37663        SHORTV             CAF      LOW3                          	# SAVE 3 BIT SHIFT COUNT - 1 WITHOUT
003079,001611: 00,2103           70020                           MASK     CYR                           	# EDITING CYR.
003080,001612: 00,2104           54121                           TS       MPTEMP                        	#
003081,001613: 00,2105           10020                           CCS      CYR                           	# SEE IF LEFT OR RIGHT SHIFT.
003082,001614: 00,2106           12126                           TCF      VSSL                          	# VECTOR SHIFT LEFT.
003083,001615: 00,2107           00176        OCT176             OCT      176                           	# USED IN PROCESSED SHIFTS WITH - COUNT.
003084,001616: 
003085,001617: 00,2110           50121        VSSR               INDEX    MPTEMP                        	# (ENTRY FROM SR). PICK UP SHIFTING BIT.
003086,001618: 00,2111           37642                           CAF      BIT14                         	# MPTEMP CONTAINS THE SHIFT COUNT - 1.
003087,001619: 00,2112           54121                           TS       MPTEMP                        	#
003088,001620: 00,2113           02054                           TC       VSHRRND                       	# SHIFT X COMPONENT.
003089,001621: 
003090,001622: 00,2114           52141                           DXCH     MPAC                          	# SWAP X AND Y COMPONENTS.
003091,001623: 00,2115           52144                           DXCH     MPAC       +3                 	#
003092,001624: 00,2116           52141                           DXCH     MPAC                          	#
003093,001625: 00,2117           02054                           TC       VSHRRND                       	# SHIFT Y COMPONENT.
003094,001626: 
003095,001627: 00,2120           52141                           DXCH     MPAC                          	# SWAP Y AND Z COMPONENTS.
003096,001628: 00,2121           52146                           DXCH     MPAC       +5                 	#
003097,001629: 00,2122           52141                           DXCH     MPAC                          	#
003098,001630: 00,2123           02054                           TC       VSHRRND                       	# SHIFT Z COMPONENT.
003099,001631: 
003100,001632: 00,2124           17373                           TCF      VROTATEX                      	# RESTORE COMPONENTS TO PROPER PLACES.
003101,001633: 
003103,001635:                                                                                          	# VECTOR SHIFT LEFT - DONE ONE PLACE AT A TIME.
003104,001636: 
003105,001637: 00,2125           54121                 -1        TS       MPTEMP                        	# SHIFTING LOOP.
003106,001638: 
003107,001639: 00,2126           00006        VSSL               EXTEND                                 	#
003108,001640: 00,2127           30141                           DCA      MPAC                          	#
003109,001641: 00,2130           20141                           DAS      MPAC                          	#
003110,001642: 00,2131           00006                           EXTEND                                 	#
003111,001643: 00,2132           12134                           BZF      +2                            	#
003112,001644: 00,2133           07007                           TC       OVERFLOW                      	#
003113,001645: 
003114,001646: 00,2134           00006                           EXTEND                                 	#
003115,001647: 00,2135           30144                           DCA      MPAC       +3                 	#
003116,001648: 00,2136           20144                           DAS      MPAC       +3                 	#
003117,001649: 00,2137           00006                           EXTEND                                 	#
003118,001650: 00,2140           12142                           BZF      +2                            	#
003119,001651: 00,2141           07007                           TC       OVERFLOW                      	#
003120,001652: 
003121,001653: 00,2142           00006                           EXTEND                                 	#
003122,001654: 00,2143           30146                           DCA      MPAC       +5                 	#
003123,001655: 00,2144           20146                           DAS      MPAC       +5                 	#
003124,001656: 00,2145           00006                           EXTEND                                 	#
003125,001657: 00,2146           12150                           BZF      +2                            	#
003126,001658: 00,2147           07007                           TC       OVERFLOW                      	#
003127,001659: 
003128,001660: 00,2150           10121                           CCS      MPTEMP                        	# LOOP ON DECREMENTED SHIFT COUNTER.
003129,001661: 00,2151           12125                           TCF      VSSL       -1                 	#
003130,001662: 00,2152           16014                           TCF      DANZIG                        	# EXIT.
003131,001663: 
003133,001665:                                                                                          	#          TSLC - TRIPLE SHIFT LEFT AND COUNT. SHIFTS MPAC LEFT UNTIL GREATER THAN .5 IN MAGNITUDE, LEAVING
003134,001666:                                                                                          	# THE COMPLEMENT OF THE NUMBER OF SHIFTS REQUIRED IN X.
003135,001667: 
003136,001668: 00,2153           54121        TSLC2              TS       MPTEMP                        	# START BY ZEROING SHIFT COUNT (IN A NOW).
003137,001669: 00,2154           06711                           TC       BRANCH                        	# EXIT WITH NO SHIFTING IF ARGUMENT ZERO.
003138,001670: 00,2155           12157                           TCF      +2                            	#
003139,001671: 00,2156           12172                           TCF      ENDTSLC                       	# STORES ZERO SHIFT COUNT IN THIS CASE.
003140,001672: 
003141,001673: 00,2157           30140                           CA       MPAC                          	# BEGIN NORMALIZATION LOOP.
003142,001674: 00,2160           12167                           TCF      TSLCTEST                      	#
003143,001675: 
003144,001676: 00,2161           24121        TSLCLOOP           INCR     MPTEMP                        	# INCREMENT SHIFT COUNTER.
003145,001677: 00,2162           00006                           EXTEND                                 	#
003146,001678: 00,2163           30142                           DCA      MPAC       +1                 	#
003147,001679: 00,2164           20142                           DAS      MPAC       +1                 	#
003148,001680: 00,2165           60140                           AD       MPAC                          	#
003149,001681: 00,2166           26140                           ADS      MPAC                          	#
003150,001682: 00,2167           60000        TSLCTEST           DOUBLE                                 	# SEE IF (ANOTHER) SHIFT IS REQUIRED
003151,001683: 00,2170           54000                           OVSK                                   	#
003152,001684: 00,2171           12161                           TCF      TSLCLOOP                      	# YES - INCREMENT COUNT AND SHIFT AGAIN.
003153,001685: 
003154,001686: 00,2172           40121        ENDTSLC            CS       MPTEMP                        	#
003155,001687: 00,2173           16627                           TCF      STORE1                        	# STORE SHIFT COUNT AND RETURN TO DANZIG.
003156,001688: 
003158,001690:                                                                                          	#          THE FOLLOWING ROUTINES PROCESSES THE GENERAL SHIFT INSTRUCTIONS SR, SRR, SL, AND SLR.
003159,001691:                                                                                          	# THE GIVEN ADDRESS IS DECODED AS FOLLOWS:
003160,001692: 
003161,001693:                                                                                          	#          BITS 1-7        SHIFT COUNT (SUBADDRESS) LESS THAN 125 DECIMAL.
003162,001694:                                                                                          	#          BIT 8           PSEUDO SIGN BIT (DETECTS CHANGE IN SIGN IN INDEXED SHIFTS).
003163,001695:                                                                                          	#          BIT 9           0 FOR LEFT SHIFT, AND 1 FOR RIGHT SHIFT.
003164,001696:                                                                                          	#          BIT 10          1 FOR TERMINAL ROUND ON SCALAR SHIFTS, 0 OTHERWISE
003165,001697:                                                                                          	#          BITS 11-15      0.
003166,001698: 
003167,001699:                                                                                          	# THE ABOVE ENCODING IS DONE BY THE YUL SYSTEM.
003168,001700: 
003169,001701: 
003170,001702: 
003171,001703: 00,2174           70102        GENSHIFT           MASK     ADDRWD                        	# GET SHIFT COUNT, TESTING FOR ZERO.
003172,001704: 00,2175           10000                           CCS      A                             	# (ARRIVES WITH C(A) = LOW7).
003173,001705: 00,2176           12204                           TCF      GENSHFT2                      	# IF NON-ZERO, PROCEED WITH DECREMENTED CT
003174,001706: 
003175,001707: 00,2177           37646                           CAF      BIT10                         	# ZERO SHIFT COUNT. NO SHIFTS NEEDED BUT
003176,001708: 00,2200           70102                           MASK     ADDRWD                        	# WE MIGHT HAVE TO ROUND MPAC ON SLR AND
003177,001709: 00,2201           10000                           CCS      A                             	# SRR (SCALAR ONLY).
003178,001710: 00,2202           07116                           TC       ROUNDSUB                      	#
003179,001711: 00,2203           16014                           TCF      DANZIG                        	#
003180,001712: 
003181,001713: 00,2204           54121        GENSHFT2           TS       MPTEMP                        	# DECREMENTED SHIFT COUNT TO MPTEMP.
003182,001714: 00,2205           37650                           CAF      BIT8                          	# TEST MEANING OF LOW SEVEN BIT COUNT IN
003183,001715: 00,2206           00006                           EXTEND                                 	# MPTEMP NOW.
003184,001716: 00,2207           70102                           MP       ADDRWD                        	#
003185,001717: 00,2210           76165                           MASK     LOW2                          	# JUMPS ON SHIFT DIRECTION (BIT8) AND
003186,001718: 00,2211           50000                           INDEX    A                             	#
003187,001719: 00,2212           12213                           TCF      +1                            	# ORIGINAL SHIFT DIRECTION (BIT 9)
003188,001720: 00,2213           12312                           TCF      RIGHT-                        	# NEGATIVE SHIFT COUNT FOR SL OR SLR.
003189,001721: 00,2214           12321                           TCF      LEFT                          	# SL OR SLR.
003190,001722: 00,2215           12316                           TCF      LEFT-                         	# NEGATIVE SHIFT COUNT WITH SR OR SRR.
003191,001723: 
003193,001725:                                                                                          	#          GENERAL SHIFT RIGHT
003194,001726: 
003195,001727: 00,2216           10147        RIGHT              CCS      MODE                          	# SET IF VECTOR OR SCALAR.
003196,001728: 00,2217           12257                           TCF      GENSCR                        	#
003197,001729: 00,2220           12257                           TCF      GENSCR                        	#
003198,001730: 
003199,001731: 00,2221           30121                           CA       MPTEMP                        	# SEE IF SHIFT COUNT LESS THAN 13D.
003200,001732: 00,2222           62273        VRIGHT2            AD       NEG12                         	#
003201,001733: 00,2223           00006                           EXTEND                                 	#
003202,001734: 00,2224           62110                           BZMF     VSSR                          	# IF SO, BRANCH AND SHIFT IMMEDIATELY.
003203,001735: 
003204,001736: 00,2225           67667                           AD       NEGONE                        	# IF NOT, REDUCE MPTEMP BY A TOTAL OF 14.
003205,001737: 00,2226           54121                           TS       MPTEMP                        	# AND DO A SHIFT RIGHT AND ROUND BY 14.
003206,001738: 00,2227           37665                           CAF      ZERO                          	# THE ROUND AT THIS STAGE MAY INTRODUCE A
003207,001739: 00,2230           54001                           TS       L                             	# ONE BIT ERROR IN A SHIFT RIGHT 15D.
003208,001740: 00,2231           56140                           XCH      MPAC                          	#
003209,001741: 00,2232           56141                           XCH      MPAC       +1                 	#
003210,001742: 00,2233           02252                           TC       SETROUND                      	# X COMPONENT NOW SHIFTED, SO MAKE UP THE
003211,001743: 00,2234           20141                           DAS      MPAC                          	# ROUNDING QUANTITY (0 IN A AND 0 OR +-1
003212,001744:                                                                                          	# IN L).
003213,001745: 00,2235           56143                           XCH      MPAC       +3                 	# REPEAT THE ABOVE PROCESS FOR Y AND Z.
003214,001746: 00,2236           56144                           XCH      MPAC       +4                 	#
003215,001747: 00,2237           02252                           TC       SETROUND                      	#
003216,001748: 00,2240           20144                           DAS      MPAC       +3                 	# NO OVERFLOW ON THESE ADDS.
003217,001749: 
003218,001750: 00,2241           56145                           XCH      MPAC       +5                 	#
003219,001751: 00,2242           56146                           XCH      MPAC       +6                 	#
003220,001752: 00,2243           02252                           TC       SETROUND                      	#
003221,001753: 00,2244           20146                           DAS      MPAC       +5                 	#
003222,001754: 
003223,001755: 00,2245           10121                           CCS      MPTEMP                        	# SEE IF DONE, DOING FINAL DECREMENT.
003224,001756: 00,2246           12222                           TCF      VRIGHT2                       	#
003225,001757: 00,2247           13630        TCSUBTR            TCF      SUBTR                         	#
003226,001758: 00,2250           04604        BIASLO             DEC      .2974      B-1                	# SQRT CONSTANT
003227,001759: 
003228,001760: 00,2251           16014                           TCF      DANZIG                        	#
003229,001761: 
003230,001762: 
003231,001763: 
003232,001764: 00,2252           60000        SETROUND           DOUBLE                                 	# MAKES UP ROUNDING QUANTITY FROM ARRIVING
003233,001765: 00,2253           54142                           TS       MPAC       +2                 	# C(A). L IS ZERO INITIALLY.
003234,001766: 00,2254           37665                           CAF      ZERO                          	#
003235,001767: 00,2255           56001                           XCH      L                             	#
003236,001768: 00,2256           00002                           TC       Q                             	# RETURN AND DO THE DAS, RESETTING L TO 0.
003237,001769: 
003239,001771:                                                                                          	#          PROCESS SR AND SRR FOR SCALARS.
003240,001772: 
003241,001773: 00,2257           30121        GENSCR             CA       MPTEMP                        	# SEE IF THE ORIGINAL SHIFT COUNT WAS LESS
003242,001774: 00,2260           62273                 +1        AD       NEG12                         	# THAN 14D.
003243,001775: 00,2261           00006                           EXTEND                                 	#
003244,001776: 00,2262           62302                           BZMF     DOSSHFT                       	# DO THE SHIFT IMMEDIATELY IF SO.
003245,001777: 
003246,001778: 00,2263           67667                 +4        AD       NEGONE                        	# IF NOT, DECREMENT SHIFT COUNT BY 14D AND
003247,001779: 00,2264           54121                           TS       MPTEMP                        	# SHIFT MPAC RIGHT 14 PLACES.
003248,001780: 00,2265           37665                           CAF      ZERO                          	#
003249,001781: 00,2266           56140                           XCH      MPAC                          	#
003250,001782: 00,2267           56141                           XCH      MPAC       +1                 	#
003251,001783: 00,2270           54142                           TS       MPAC       +2                 	#
003252,001784: 00,2271           10121                           CCS      MPTEMP                        	# SEE IF FINISHED, DO FINAL DECREMENT.
003253,001785: 00,2272           02260                           TC       GENSCR     +1                 	#
003254,001786: 00,2273           77763        NEG12              DEC      -12        B-14               	#
003255,001787: 00,2274           22650        SLOPEHI            DEC      .5884                         	# SQRT CONSTANT.
003256,001788: 00,2275           37646                           CAF      BIT10                         	# FINISHED WITH SHIFT. SEE IF ROUND
003257,001789: 00,2276           70102                           MASK     ADDRWD                        	# WANTED.
003258,001790: 00,2277           10000                           CCS      A                             	#
003259,001791: 00,2300           07116                           TC       ROUNDSUB                      	#
003260,001792: 00,2301           16014                           TCF      DANZIG                        	# DO SO AND/OR EXIT.
003261,001793: 
003262,001794: 00,2302           50121        DOSSHFT            INDEX    MPTEMP                        	# PICK UP SHIFTING BIT.
003263,001795: 00,2303           37642                           CAF      BIT14                         	#
003264,001796: 00,2304           54121                           TS       MPTEMP                        	#
003265,001797: 00,2305           37646                           CAF      BIT10                         	# SEE IF TERMINAL ROUND DESIRED.
003266,001798: 00,2306           70102                           MASK     ADDRWD                        	#
003267,001799: 00,2307           10000                           CCS      A                             	#
003268,001800: 00,2310           12012                           TCF      RIGHTR                        	# YES.
003269,001801: 00,2311           12014                           TCF      MPACSHR                       	# JUST SHIFT RIGHT.
003270,001802: 
003272,001804:                                                                                          	#          PROCESS THE RIGHT- (SL(R) WITH A NEGATIVE COUNT), LEFT-, AND LEFT OPTIONS.
003273,001805: 
003274,001806: 00,2312           40121        RIGHT-             CS       MPTEMP                        	# GET ABSOLUTE VALUE - 1 OF SHIFT COUNT
003275,001807: 00,2313           62107                           AD       OCT176                        	# UNDERSTANDING THAT BIT8 (PSEUDO-SIGN)
003276,001808: 00,2314           54121                           TS       MPTEMP                        	# WAS 1 INITIALLY.
003277,001809: 00,2315           12216                           TCF      RIGHT                         	# DO NORMAL SHIFT RIGHT.
003278,001810: 
003279,001811: 00,2316           40121        LEFT-              CS       MPTEMP                        	# SAME PROLOGUE TO LEFT FOR INDEXED RIGHT
003280,001812: 00,2317           62107                           AD       OCT176                        	# SHIFTS WHOSE NET SHIFT COUNT IS NEGATIVE
003281,001813: 00,2320           54121                           TS       MPTEMP                        	#
003282,001814:
