017646,000618: 24,2732           02716 46066  JTLSTADR           2CADR    JTLST                         	#
017647,000619: 
017648,000620: 24,2734           02467        RTJETADR           GENADR   RTJETIME                      	#
017649,000621: 
017651,000623:                                                                                          	# Q,R-AXES ATTITUDE STEERING CALCULATIONS:
017652,000624: 
017653,000625:                                                                                          	# (EXECUTED WHEN LGC IS IN AUTOMATIC SCSMODE OR IF SCSMODE IS ATTITUDE HOLD AND THE ROTATIONAL HAND CONTROLLER IS
017654,000626:                                                                                          	# NEITHER OUT OF DETENT NOR IS THE RATE COMMAND BIT SET IN DAPBOOLS)
017655,000627: 
017656,000628:                                                                                          	# IMMEDIATELY AFTER CALCULATING THE ATTITUDE ERRORS, THE FOLLOWING TESTS ARE MADE TO DETERMINE WHETHER THE DESCENT
017657,000629:                                                                                          	# ENGINE TRIM GIMBAL SHOULD BE USED TO CONTROL THE LEM ATTITUDE RATHER THAN TEH RCS JETS:
017658,000630: 
017659,000631:                                                                                          	#          1) IS THE TRIM GIMBAL FUNCTIONALLY OPERATIVE?
017660,000632:                                                                                          	#          2) ARE THE Q,R-AXES RCS JETS OFF?
017661,000633:                                                                                          	#          3) ARE BOTH TRIM GIMBAL DRIVES OFF?
017662,000634:                                                                                          	#          4) IS THE LEM RATE LESS THAN .5 DEG/SEC ABOUT BOTH AXES?
017663,000635: 
017664,000636: 24,2735           32742        GOTOGTS            CAF      INITFILT                      	# ERRORS NOW CONTROLLABLE BY TRIM GIMBAL
017665,000637: 24,2736           54345                           TS       T5ADR                         	# SET T5RUPT TO GO TO FILTER INITIALIZING
017666,000638: 24,2737           14606                           TCF      RESUME                        	# PROGRAM
017667,000639: 
017668,000640: 24,2740           07400        BGIM24             OCTAL    07400                         	#
017669,000641: 24,2741           03644        DESCADR            GENADR   TJET-LAW                      	# RETURN ADDRESS FOR JET SELECT LOGIC
017670,000642: 24,2742           02000        INITFILT           GENADR   FILTINIT                      	# ADDRESS OF FILTER INITIALIZATION RUPT
017671,000643: 
017672,000644:                                                                                          	# "ATTSTEER" IS THE NOMINAL ENTRY POINT FOR REACTION CONTROL SYSTEM ATTITUDE STEERING:
017673,000645:                                                                                          	# BEGIN ATTSTEER BY CHECKING IF RATE HOLD MODE(CURRENTLY USED ONLY AT SIVB
017674,000646:                                                                                          	# -LEM SEPARATION-206 MISSION PHASE 6) IS REQUESTED(BIT 14 OF DAPBOOLS ON)
017675,000647:                                                                                          	# IF BIT 14 IS OFF, BRANCH TO QERRCALC DIRECTLY AND BEGIN AUTOMATIC
017676,000648:                                                                                          	# STEERING.  IF BIT 14 IS ON, TEST BIT 3 OF DAPBOOLS TO SEE IF THE DESIRED
017677,000649:                                                                                          	# RATE HAS BEEN SAVED YET.  IF IT IS ON, THIS IS NOT THE FIRST PASS AND
017678,000650:                                                                                          	# THE RATE HAS BEEN SAVED.  GO DIRECTLY TO QERRCALC FOR AUTOMATIC STEERING
017679,000651:                                                                                          	# IF THE BIT IS OFF, THE RATE MUST BE SAVED.  TRANSFER TO SAVERATE(BANK25)
017680,000652:                                                                                          	# AND RETURN AFTER FIRST PASS TO RESUME AND DAPIDLER.
017681,000653: 
017682,000654:                                                                                          	# IN ORDER TO USE RATE HOLD, THE MISSION PROGRAMMER MUST SET BIT 14 OF
017683,000655:                                                                                          	# DAPBOOLS ON AND SET BIT 3 OF DAPBOOLS TO ZERO.  UPON RETURNING FROM THE
017684,000656:                                                                                          	# FIRST PASS AT LEAST THROUGH RATE HOLD, THE MISSION PROGRAMMER MUST RESET
017685,000657:                                                                                          	# BIT 3 TO ITS PREVIOUS VALUE IF THIS IS NOT 1, BECASUE SAVERATE SETS BIT3
017686,000658:                                                                                          	# TO 1 FOR ALL PASSES AFTER THE FIRST IN ORDER NOT TO SAVE THE RATE AGAIN.
017687,000659: 
017688,000660:                                                                                          	# IN ADDITION TO NON-RATE HOLD MODE AND NON-FIRST PASS RATE HOLD MODE
017689,000661:                                                                                          	# EXITS TO QERRCALC, THE FIRST PASS EXITS TO RESUME, IE. OUT OF INTERRUPT
017690,000662:                                                                                          	# AND BACK TO DAPIDLER TO AWAIT THE NEXT CALL TO DAP.
017691,000663: 
017692,000664:                                                                                          	# RATE HOLD PRODUCES THE FOLLOWING OUTPUT IN ERASABLE --
017693,000665: 
017694,000666:                                                                                          	#    CDUD - SCALED AT +/-PI, DESIRED GIMBAL ANGLE
017695,000667: 
017696,000668:                                                                                          	#    DELCDU - SCALED AT +/-PI, INCREMENT TO CDUD EVERY 100 MS.
017697,000669: 
017698,000670:                                                                                          	#    OMEGAPD, QD, RD - SCALED AT +/-PI/4, BODY AXIS RATES
017699,000671: 
017700,000672:                                                                                          	# ALL THESE ARE USED BY AUTOMATIC STEERING MODE EQUATIONS.
017701,000673: 
017703,000675:                                                                                          	# RATE HOLD REQUIRES OMEGAP, Q, R EVERY .25 SEC, AND ALSO REQUIRES PILOT-
017704,000676:                                                                                          	# TO-GIMBAL AXIS MATRIX ELEMENTS, MR12, 22, 13, 23 TO BE LOCATED IN THAT
017705,000677:                                                                                          	# ORDER.
017706,000678: 
017707,000679:                                                                                          	# FINALLY, RATE HOLD LEAVES DEBRIS IN --
017708,000680: 
017709,000681:                                                                                          	#    DLCDUIDX - LOOP INDEX USED IN COMPUTING DELCDUS, = 1, 0
017710,000682: 
017711,000683:                                                                                          	#    ITEMP1 - STORES TEMPORARY PRODUCTS AND SUMS, LEFT WITH DELCDUY IN 1S.
017712,000684: 
017713,000685: 
017714,000686: 
017715,000687: 24,2743           40765        ATTSTEER           CS       DAPBOOLS                      	# DOES BIT14 OF DAPBOOLS REQUEST RATE HOLD
017716,000688: 24,2744           77642                           MASK     BIT14                         	# (SIVB-LEM SEPARATION)
017717,000689: 24,2745           10000                           CCS      A                             	#
017718,000690: 24,2746           13025                           TCF      QERRCALC                      	# NO, GO DIRECTLY TO AUTOMATIC STEERING
017719,000691: 
017720,000692:                                                                                          	# CHECK DAPBOOLS, BIT3, TO SEE IF DESIRED RATE HAS BEEN SAVED YET
017721,000693: 
017722,000694: 24,2747           30765                           CAE      DAPBOOLS                      	# DOES BIT3 SHOW THAT THE DESIRED RATE HAS
017723,000695: 24,2750           77655                           MASK     BIT3                          	# BEEN SAVED(NOT FIRST PASS).  IF NOT, GO
017724,000696: 24,2751           10000                           CCS      A                             	# SAVE DESIRED RATES IN OMEGADS
017725,000697: 24,2752           12771                           TCF      NEXDLCDU   -1                 	# YES, COMPUTE THE DELCDUS.
017726,000698: 
017727,000699:                                                                                          	# SAVERATE IS ENTERED ONLY DURING THE FIRST PASS THROUGH RATE HOLD.  IT
017728,000700:                                                                                          	# SAVES THE CURRENT CDUS FIRST IN CDUDS AND THEN SAVES THE BODY RATES,
017729,000701:                                                                                          	# OMEGAP, Q, R IN OMEGAPD, QD, RD.  NEXT, WE SET BIT 3 OF DAPBOOLS TO 1.
017730,000702: 
017731,000703: 24,2753           00006        SAVERATE           EXTEND                                 	# COME HERE FIRST TIME INTO RATE HOLD IN
017732,000704: 24,2754           30034                           DCA      CDUY                          	#
017733,000705: 24,2755           52776                           DXCH     CDUYD                         	# ORDER TO SET UP RATES, CDUS, AND DELCDUS
017734,000706: 24,2756           30032                           CAE      CDUX                          	#
017735,000707: 24,2757           54774                           TS       CDUXD                         	# FIRST, CDUDS = CDUS AT SIVB SEPARATION
017736,000708: 
017737,000709: 24,2760           00006                           EXTEND                                 	# NEXT, SAVE CURRENT SIVB SEPARATION RATES
017738,000710: 24,2761           31417                           DCA      OMEGAP                        	#
017739,000711: 24,2762           53427                           DXCH     OMEGAPD                       	# OMEGAP AND OMEGAR, IN OMEGAPD AND
017740,000712: 24,2763           31421                           CAE      OMEGAR                        	#
017741,000713: 24,2764           55430                           TS       OMEGARD                       	# OMEGARD.  LEM HELD TO RATES FOR 13 SECS.
017742,000714: 
017743,000715: 24,2765           37655                           CAF      BIT3                          	# RESET BIT 3 = 1 SO THAT RATES NOT SAVED
017744,000716: 24,2766           26765                           ADS      DAPBOOLS                      	# AGAIN IN RATE HOLD PASSES
017745,000717: 24,2767           14606                           TCF      RESUME                        	# RETURN TO IDLE AFTER SAVING RATE
017746,000718: 
017747,000719: 24,2770           00632        100MSCAL           DEC      .025                          	# 100 MS. SACLED AT 4 SEC.  RATE HOLD DELT
017748,000720: 
017749,000721:                                                                                          	# TO COMPUTE TEH DELCDUS, Y AND Z, WE SET UP A LOOP AND SOLVE THE EQUATION
017750,000722: 
017751,000723:                                                                                          	# C(DELCDUY+DLCDUIDX)=(OMEGAQD.C(MR12+DLCDUIDX)+OMEGARD.C(MR13+DLCDUIDX))
017752,000724:                                                                                          	#                       .(100MS) SCALED AT PI IN 2S COMPLEMENT(LIKE CDUS)
017753,000725: 
017755,000727:                                                                                          	# DURING THIS COMPUTATION, ITEMP1 IS USED TO STORE THE PARTIAL SUMS AND
017756,000728:                                                                                          	# PRODUCTS.  DELCDUY IS RESCALED TO 1 AS MR12 AND MR13 ARE SCALED AT 2.
017757,000729:                                                                                          	# AFTER CONVERTING TO TWOS COMPLEMENT, WE SET DELCDUX TO ZERO TO AVOID ANY
017758,000730:                                                                                          	# ROLL DURING RATE HOLD MODE.  NOTE THAT DELCDUS ARE COMPUTED IN THE NEGA-
017759,000731:                                                                                          	# TIVE TO ALLOW 2S COMP. MOD. SUBTRACT LATER ON (CDU-(-DELCDU))
017760,000732: 
017761,000733: 24,2771           37657                           CAF      ONE                           	# SET UP LOOP INDEX TO COMPUTE DELCDUS.
017762,000734: 24,2772           55672        NEXDLCDU           TS       DLCDUIDX                      	# DLCDUIDX = C(A)
017763,000735: 
017764,000736: 24,2773           41427                           CS       OMEGAQD                       	# DLCDUIDX = 1              DLCDUIDX = 0
017765,000737: 24,2774           00006                           EXTEND                                 	# ITEMP1=-OMEGAQD.MR22
017766,000738: 24,2775           51672                           INDEX    DLCDUIDX                      	#
017767,000739: 24,2776           71400                           MP       MR12                          	# MR22 SCALED AT 1       MR12 SCALED AT 2
017768,000740: 24,2777           54065                           TS       ITEMP1                        	#                     ITEMP1=-OMEGAQD.MR12
017769,000741: 
017770,000742: 24,3000           41430                           CS       OMEGARD                       	# C(A)=ITEMP1 -OMEGARD.MR23
017771,000743: 24,3001           00006                           EXTEND                                 	#
017772,000744: 24,3002           51672                           INDEX    DLCDUIDX                      	#                C(A)=ITEMP1 -OMEGARD.MR13
017773,000745: 24,3003           71402                           MP       MR13                          	# MR23 SCALED AT 1        MR13 SCALED AT 2
017774,000746: 24,3004           60065                           AD       ITEMP1                        	#
017775,000747: 24,3005           00006                           EXTEND                                 	# DELT = 100 MS. SCALED AT 4 SEC.
017776,000748: 24,3006           72770                           MP       100MSCAL                      	#
017777,000749: 24,3007           54065                           TS       ITEMP1                        	# ITEMP1 = C(A) . DELT
017778,000750: 
017779,000751: 24,3010           11672                           CCS      DLCDUIDX                      	# CHECK INDEX FOR RESCALING
017780,000752: 24,3011           13014                           TCF      +3                            	# DELCDUZ SCALED AT PI/4, RESCALE UNNEEDED
017781,000753: 24,3012           30065                           CAE      ITEMP1                        	# DELCDUY SCALED AT PI/2, RESCALE BY
017782,000754: 24,3013           26065                           ADS      ITEMP1                        	# ADDING TO ITSELF
017783,000755: 
017784,000756: 24,3014           10065                           CCS      ITEMP1                        	# CONVERT DELCDUS TO TWOS COMPLEMENT (SAME
017785,000757: 24,3015           67657                           AD       ONE                           	# AS CDUS).  ADD ONE TO RESTORE PRE-CCS A

017834,000806: 24,3064           13122                           TCF      STILLRCS                      	# BUT INSUFFICIENT REASON FOR GTS USE
017835,000807: 
017836,000808:                                                                                          	# TEST (3): ARE BOTH TRIM GIMBAL DRIVES OFF?
017837,000809: 
017838,000810: 24,3065           00006                           EXTEND                                 	# BITS 9-12 OF CHANNEL 12 ARE THE SIGNALS
017839,000811: 24,3066           00012                           READ     12                            	# WHICH DRIVE THE TRIM GIMBAL ENGINE:
017840,000812: 24,3067           72740                           MASK     BGIM24                        	# IF NONE OF THESE BITS ARE ON, THEN BOTH
017841,000813: 24,3070           10000                           CCS      A                             	# WAITLIST TASKS TO TURN OFF THE DRIVES
017842,000814: 24,3071           13122                           TCF      STILLRCS                      	# HAVE BEEN DONE AND GTS CONTROL CAN OCCUR
017843,000815: 
017844,000816:                                                                                          	# TEST (4): IS THE LEM RATE LESS THAN .5 DEG/SEC ABOUT BOTH AXES?
017845,000817:

019163,000033: 
019164,000034:                                                                                          	# THE FOLLOWING T5RUPT ENTRY BEGINS THE PROGRAM WHICH INITIALIZES THE KALMAN FILTERS AND SETS UP A P-AXIS RUPT TO
019165,000035:                                                                                          	# OCCUR 20 MS FROM ITS BEGINNING.
019166,000036: 
019167,000037: 26,2000                                           BANK     26                            	#
019168,000038: 
019169,000039: 26,2000           32372        FILTINIT           CAF      MS20F                         	# RESET TIMER IMMEDIATELY: DT = 20 MS
019170,000040: 26,2001           54030                           TS       TIME5                         	#
019171,000041: 
019172,000042: 26,2002           22016                           LXCH     BANKRUPT                      	# INTERRUPT LEAD IN (CONTINUED)
019173,000043: 26,2003           00006                           EXTEND                                 	#
019174,000044: 26,2004           22012                           QXCH     QRUPT                         	#
019175,000045: 
019176,000046: 26,2005           00006                           EXTEND                                 	# SET UP FOR P-AXIS RUPT
019177,000047: 26,2006           32071                           DCA      PAX/FILT                      	#
019178,000048: 26,2007           52346                           DXCH     T5ADR                         	#
019179,000049: 
019180,000050: 26,2010           32013                           CAF      FIRSTADR                      	# SET UP TO AVOID DT CALCULATION DURING
019181,000051: 26,2011           55553                           TS       STEERADR                      	# KALMAN FILTER INITIALIZATION PASS
019182,000052: 
019183,000053: 
KALMAN_FILTER_FOR_LEM_DAP.agc:54: Fatal Error: Symbol "FILSTART" undefined or offset bad
019184,000054: 26,2012           16000                           TCF      FILSTART                      	#
019185,000055: 
019186,000056: 26,2013           02315        FIRSTADR           GENADR   FILFIRST                      	#
019187,000057: 
019188,000058:                                                                                          	# THE FOLLOWING T5RUPT ENTRY BEGINS THE KALMAN FILTER PROGRAM.  THIS SECTION ALSO SETS UP A T5RUPT
019189,000059:                                                                                          	# FROM ITS BEGINNING AND SETS IT TO GO TO THE LOCATION AT THE TOP OF THE POST FILTER RUPT LIST.
019190,000060: 
019191,000061: 26,2014           02051        MOSTPASS           GENADR   DTCALC                        	# WORD IN FILTPASS FOR THESE PASSES
019192,000062: 
KALMAN_FILTER_FOR_LEM_DAP.agc:63: Fatal Error: Symbol "MS2OF" undefined or offset bad
019193,000063: 26,2015           30000        FILTER             CAF      MS2OF                         	# RESET TIMER IMMEDIATELY: DT = 20 MS
019194,000064: 26,2016           54030                           TS       TIME5                         	#
019195,000065: 
019196,000066: 26,2017           22016                           LXCH     BANKRUPT                      	# INTERRUPT LEAD IN (CONTINUED)
019197,000067: 26,2020           00006                           EXTEND                                 	#
019198,000068: 26,2021           22012                           QXCH     QRUPT                         	#
019199,000069: 
019200,000070: 26,2022           00006                           EXTEND                                 	# SET RUPT ADDRESS TO TOP OF
019201,000071: 26,2023           31604                           DCA      PFRPTLST                      	# POST FILTER RUPT LIST
019202,000072: 26,2024           52346                           DXCH     T5ADR                         	#
019203,000073: 
019204,000074: 26,2025           53604                           DXCH     PFRPTLST                      	# ROTATE 2CADR'S IN POST FILTER RUPT LIST
019205,000075: 26,2026           53612                           DXCH     PFRPTLST   +6                 	#
019206,000076: 26,2027           53610                           DXCH     PFRPTLST   +4                 	#
019207,000077: 26,2030           53606                           DXCH     PFRPTLST   +2                 	#
019208,000078: 26,2031           53604                           DXCH     PFRPTLST                      	#
019209,000079: 
019210,000080:                                                                                          	# BEGIN THE KALMAN FILTER BY READING CDU ANGLES AND TIME.
019211,000081: 
019212,000082: 26,2032           04177        FILTSTART           TC       T6JOBCHK                      	# CHECK T6 CLOCK FOR P-AXIS ACTIVITY
019213,000083: 
019215,000085: 26,2033           00006                           EXTEND                                 	#
019216,000086: 26,2034           30034                           DCA      CDUY                          	# STORE CDUY AND CDUZ AT PI AND IN 2.5 COM
019217,000087: 26,2035           53550                           DXCH     STORCDUY                      	#
019218,000088: 26,2036           00006                           EXTEND                                 	# BEGIN READING THE CLOCK TO GET TIME
019219,000089: 26,2037           00004                           READ     4                             	#   INCREMENT.
019220,000090: 26,2040           54001                           TS       L                             	#
019221,000091: 26,2041           00006                           EXTEND                                 	#
019222,000092: 26,2042           06004                           RXOR     4                             	# CHECK TO SEE IF CH 4 WAS IN TRANSITION
019223,000093: 26,2043           00006                           EXTEND                                 	#   WHEN IT WAS FIRST READ.
019224,000094: 26,2044           12050                           BZF      +4                            	# BRANCH IF TIME WAS THE SAME IN 2 READS.
019225,000095: 26,2045           00006                           EXTEND                                 	#
019226,000096: 26,2046           00004                           READ     4                             	#
019227,000097: 26,2047           54001                           TS       L                             	# THIS TIME READ ALWAYS GIVES GOOD NO.
019228,000098: 26,2050           01553                           TC       STEERADR                      	# SKIP DTCALC DURING INITIAL PASS
019229,000099: 
019230,000100: 26,2051           40001        DTCALC             CS       L                             	#
019231,000101: 26,2052           61552                           AD       DAPTIME                       	# A CONTAINS THE TIME DIFFERENCE (DT)
019232,000102: 26,2053           23552                           LXCH     DAPTIME                       	#   SINCE THE LAST FILTER.
019233,000103: 26,2054           00006                           EXTEND                                 	#
019234,000104: 26,2055           62060                           BZMF     +3                            	#
019235,000105: 26,2056           67640                           AD       NEG1/2                        	# THIS IS ADDING -1.0 TO -DT AND ACCOUNTS
019236,000106: 26,2057           67640                           AD       NEG1/2                        	# FOR AN OVERFLOW INTO CHANNEL 5
019237,000107: 
019238,000108:                                                                                          	#  SCALING OF DELTA T FOR KALMAN FILTER IS 1/8 SECOND.
019239,000109: 26,2060           00006                           EXTEND                                 	# TIME NOW SCALED AT 5.12 SECONDS
019240,000110: 26,2061           77651                           MP       BIT7                          	# FIRST RESCALE TO 5.12/64
019241,000111: 26,2062           42367                           CS       .64                           	#
019242,000112: 26,2063           00006                           EXTEND                                 	# THEN RESCALE TO 5/12/(64*.64) OR
019243,000113: 26,2064           70001                           MP       L                             	# 5.12/40.96 WHICH IS THE SAME AS
019244,000114: 26,2065           55551                           TS       DT                            	# DT SCALED AT 1/8
019245,000115: 
019246,000116:                                                                                          	# SET UP FILTER WEIGHTING VECTOR FOR THIS FILTER PASS.
019247,000117: 
019248,000118: 26,2066           11556                           CCS      WPOINTER                      	# TEST FOR WEIGHTING VECTOR STEADY-STATE
019249,000119: 26,2067           12073                           TCF      MOVEWGTS                      	# POINTER NOT YET ZERO (MULTIPLE OF THREE)
019250,000120: 26,2070           02055 46066  PAX/FILT           2CADR    PAXIS                         	# (ROOM FOR 2CADR IN CCS HOLES)
019251,000121: 
019252,000122: 26,2072           12104                           TCF      FLTZAXIS                      	# STEADY-STATE ALREADY, NO UPDATING AGAIN
019253,000123: 
019254,000124: 26,2073           46165        MOVEWGTS           CS       THREE                         	# SET UP POINTER FOR THIS PASS
019255,000125: 26,2074           27556                           ADS      WPOINTER                      	# (NEVER GETS BELOW ZERO HERE)
019256,000126: 
019257,000127: 26,2075           00006                           EXTEND                                 	# WPOINTER IS INDEX = 87 FIRST TIME HERE
019258,000128: 26,2076           51556                           INDEX    WPOINTER                      	# AND IS DECREASED BY 3 EVERY FILTER PASS
019259,000129: 26,2077           32404                           DCA      WVECTOR                       	# UNTIL THE STEADY-STATE IS REACHED.
019260,000130: 26,2100           53560                           DXCH     W0                            	# MOVE IN NEW W0,W1
019261,000131: 26,2101           51556                           INDEX    WPOINTER                      	#
019262,000132: 26,2102           32405                           CAF      WVECTOR    +2                 	#
019263,000133: 26,2103           55561                           TS       W2                            	# MOVE IN NEW W2
019264,000134: 
019266,000136: 
019267,000137: 26,2104           37656        FLTZAXIS           CAF      TWO                           	# SET UP INDEXER FOR D.P. PICKUP AND TO
019268,000138: 26,2105           54073                           TS       QRCNTR                        	# INDICATE Z-AXIS FILTER PASS
019269,000139: 
KALMAN_FILTER_FOR_LEM_DAP.agc:140: Fatal Error: Symbol "FLTAXIS" undefined or offset bad
019270,000140: 26,2106           16000                           TCF      FLTAXIS                       	#
019271,000141: 
019272,000142: 26,2107           37665        GOYFILTR           CAF      ZERO                          	# SET INDEXER FOR Y-AXIS
019273,000143: 26,2110           54073                           TS       QRCNTR                        	#
019274,000144: 
019275,000145: 26,2111           04177                           TC       T6JOBCHK                      	# CHECK T6 CLOCK FOR P-AXIS ACTIVITY
019276,000146: 
019277,000147: 26,2112           50073        FLTYAXIS           INDEX    QRCNTR                        	#
019278,000148: 26,2113           53563                           DXCH     CDUYFIL                       	# THETA IS D.P. SCALED AT 2 PI RADIANS
019279,000149: 26,2114           52077                           DXCH     CDU                           	#
019280,000150: 26,2115           50073                           INDEX    QRCNTR                        	#   .
019281,000151: 26,2116           53567                           DXCH     DCDUYFIL                      	# THETA IS D.P. SCALED AT PI/4 RAD/SEC
019282,000152: 26,2117           52066                           DXCH     CDUDOT                        	#
019283,000153: 26,2120           50073                           INDEX    QRCNTR                        	#  ..                                 2
019284,000154: 26,2121           53573                           DXCH     D2CDUYFL                      	# THETA IS D.P. SCALED AT PI/8 RAD/SEC
019285,000155: 26,2122           52071                           DXCH     CDU2DOT                       	#
019286,000156: 26,2123           50073                           INDEX    QRCNTR                        	#  ...                        7       3
019287,000157: 26,2124           31576                           CAE      Y3DOT                         	# THETA IS S.P. SCALED AT PI/2 RAD/SEC
019288,000158: 26,2125           57577                           XCH      CDU3DOT                       	#
019289,000159: 
019290,000160:                                                                                          	# NOTE THAT THE FILTERED VARIABLES ARE READ DESTRUCTIVELY FOR SPEED AND EFFICIENCY AND THAT Y3DOT IS NOT UPDATED.
019291,000161:                                                                                          	# SO IT MUST BE READ NON-DESTRUCTIVELY BUT NEED NOT BE RESTORED AFTER EACH KALMAN FILTER PASS.
019292,000162: 
019294,000164: 
019295,000165: 26,2126           30070        KLMNFLTR           CAE      CDU2DOT                       	# A SCALED AT PI/8 (USE S.P.)
019296,000166: 26,2127           00006                           EXTEND                                 	#
019297,000167: 26,2130           71551                           MP       DT                            	# ADT SCALED AT PI/64 OR .5ADT AT PI/128
019298,000168: 26,2131           00006                           EXTEND                                 	#
019299,000169: 26,2132           77646                           MP       BIT10                         	# RESCALE BY RIGHT SHIFT 5
019300,000170: 26,2133           60065                           AD       CDUDOT                        	# W + .5ADT SCALED AT PI/4
019301,000171: 26,2134           00006                           EXTEND                                 	#
019302,000172: 26,2135           71551                           MP       DT                            	# (W + .5ADT)DT SCALED AT PI/32
019303,000173: 26,2136           00006                           EXTEND                                 	#
019304,000174: 26,2137           77647                           MP       BIT9                          	# RESCALE BY RIGHT SHIFT 6 (KEEP D.P.)
019305,000175: 26,2140           20077                           DAS      CDU                           	# CDU = CDU + (W + .5ADT)DT SCALED AT 2PI
019306,000176: 
019307,000177: 26,2141           31577                           CAE      CDU3DOT                       	# ADOT SCALED AT PI/2(7)
019308,000178: 26,2142           00006                           EXTEND                                 	#
019309,000179: 26,2143           71551                           MP       DT                            	# .5ADOTDT SCALED AT PI/2(11)
019310,000180: 26,2144           54072                           TS       ITEMP5                        	# (SAVE FOR ALPHA INTEGRATION)
019311,000181: 26,2145           00006                           EXTEND                                 	#
019312,000182: 26,2146           77651                           MP       BIT7                          	# RESCALE BY RIGHT SHIFT 8
019313,000183: 26,2147           60070                           AD       CDU2DOT                       	# A + .5ADOTDT SCALED AT PI/64
019314,000184: 26,2150           00006                           EXTEND                                 	#
019315,000185: 26,2151           71551                           MP       DT                            	#
019316,000186: 26,2152           00006                           EXTEND                                 	#
019317,000187: 26,2153           77645                           MP       BIT11                         	# RESCALE BY RIGHT SHIFT 4 (KEEP D.P.)
019318,000188: 26,2154           20066                           DAS      CDUDOT                        	# W = W + (A + .5ADOTDT)DT SCALED AT PI/4
019319,000189: 
019320,000190: 26,2155           30072                           CAE      ITEMP5                        	# ADOTDT SCALED AT PI/2(10) (FROM ABOVE)
019321,000191: 26,2156           00006                           EXTEND                                 	#
019322,000192: 26,2157           77650                           MP       BIT8                          	# RESCALE BY RIGHT SHIFT 7 (KEEP D.P.)
019323,000193: 26,2160           20071                           DAS      CDU2DOT                       	# A = A + ADOTDT SCALED AT PI/8
019324,000194: 
019326,000196: 
019327,000197:                                                                                          	# WEIGHTING VECTOR ADJUSTMENT EQUATIONS:
019328,000198: 26,2161           00006                           EXTEND                                 	# CONVERT CDU INTEGRATED VALUE FROM DOUBLE
019329,000199: 26,2162           30077                           DCA      CDU                           	# PRECISION SCALED AT 2PI IN ONES COMPLE-
019330,000200: 26,2163           02302                           TC       ONETOTWO                      	# MENT TO SINGLE PRECISION SCALED AT PI
019331,000201: 26,2164           31550                           CAE      STORCDUZ                      	# IN TWOS COMPLEMENT, THEN DIFFERENCE WITH
019332,000202: 26,2165           00006                           EXTEND                                 	# STORED CDU REGISTER READING TO GET A
019333,000203: 26,2166           20072                           MSU      ITEMP5                        	# SINGLE PRECISION ONES COMPLEMENT RESULT
019334,000204: 26,2167           55554                           TS       DPDIFF                        	# SCALED AT PI RADIANS (UPPER HALF)
019335,000205: 
019336,000206: 26,2170           40077                           CS       CDU        +1                 	# CREATE LOW ORDER WORD OF D.P. DIFFERENCE
019337,000207: 26,2171           60000                           DOUBLE                                 	# ONES COMPLEMENT SCALED AT PI RADIANS AND
019338,000208: 26,2172           57555                           XCH      DPDIFF     +1                 	# USE S.P. RESULT ABOVE AS HIGH ORDER WORD
019339,000209: 
019340,000210: 26,2173           00006                           EXTEND                                 	# RESCALE DPDIFF TO PI
019341,000211: 26,2174           31555                           DCA      DPDIFF                        	#
019342,000212: 26,2175           20001                           DDOUBL                                 	#

019344,000214: 26,2177           00006                           EXTEND                                 	#
019345,000215: 26,2200           71557                           MP       W0                            	# CDU = CDU + DPDIFF (D.P.) * W0 (S.P.)
019346,000216: 26,2201           20077                           DAS      CDU                           	#
019347,000217: 26,2202           30072                           CAE      ITEMP5                        	# W0 IS SCALED AT 2
019348,000218: 26,2203           00006                           EXTEND                                 	# DPDIFF IS RESCALED TO PI
019349,000219: 26,2204           71557                           MP       W0                            	# W0*DPDIFF IS SCALED AT 2PI (AS CDU)
019350,000220: 26,2205           26077                           ADS      CDU        +          1       	#
019351,000221: 26,2206           54001                           TS       L                             	#
019352,000222: 26,2207           12211                           TCF      +2                            	#
019353,000223: 26,2210           26076                           ADS      CDU                           	#
019354,000224: 
019355,000225: 26,2211           31554                           CAE      DPDIFF                        	# RESCALE DPDIFF TO PI/128
019356,000226: 26,2212           00006                           EXTEND                                 	#
019357,000227: 26,2213           77647                           MP       BIT9                          	# DPDIFF (D.P.) * 256
019358,000228: 26,2214           22072                           LXCH     ITEMP5                        	#

019504,000374: 
019505,000375:                                                                                          	# THE KALMAN FILTER WEIGHTINF VECTORS ARE LISTED IN THE FOLLOWING TABLE ALONG WITH THE TIME FROM THE LAST FILTER
019506,000376:                                                                                          	# INITIALIZATION FOR WHICH THEY ARE TO BE USED. (THE VECTORS ARE STORED IN ORDERED TRIPLETS (W0,W1,W2) IN
019507,000377:                                                                                          	# DESCENDING ORDER IN TIME WITH THE STEADY STATE VALUES AT THE TOP.)
019508,000378: 
019509,000379:                                                                                          	# THE COMPONENTS ARE SCALED AS FOLLOWS:
019510,000380:                                                                                          	#            W0 : SCALED AT  2
019511,000381:                                                                                          	#            W1 : SCALED AT 32
019512,000382:                                                                                          	#            W2 : SCALED AT  8
019513,000383: 
019514,000384: 26,2403           05751        WVECTOR            DEC      0.18608                       	# W0 FROM RELATIVE TIME 1.5 SECS OR MORE
019515,000385: 26,2404           00672                           DEC      0.02696                       	# W1 FROM RELATIVE TIME 1.5 SECS OR MORE
019516,000386: 26,2405           05362                           DEC      0.17105                       	# W2 FROM RELATIVE TIME 1.5 SECS OR MORE
019517,000387: 26,2406           04460                           DEC      0.14358                       	# W0 AT RELATIVE TIME = 1.45 SECONDS
019518,000388: 26,2407           00731                           DEC      0.02890                       	# W1 AT RELATIVE TIME = 1.45 SECONDS
019519,000389: 26,2410           05530                           DEC      0.17727                       	# W2 AT RELATIVE TIME = 1.45 SECONDS

019645,000060: 
019646,000061: $TRIM_GIMBAL_CONTROL_SYSTEM.agc			# 615
019648,000002:                                                                                          	# Copyright:    Public domain.
019649,000003:                                                                                          	# Filename:     TRIM_GIMBAL_CONTROL_SYSTEM.agc
019650,000004:                                                                                          	# Purpose:      Part of the source code for Aurora (revision 12).
019651,000005:                                                                                          	# Assembler:    yaYUL
019652,000006:                                                                                          	# Contact:      Ron Burkey <info@sandroid.org>.
019653,000007:                                                                                          	# Website:      https://www.ibiblio.org/apollo.
019654,000008:                                                                                          	# Pages:        615-629
019655,000009:                                                                                          	# Mod history:  2016-09-20 JL   Created.
019656,000010:                                                                                          	#               2016-10-02 MAS  Transcribed.
019657,000011:                                                                                          	#               2016-10-04 HG   Change 'code' to comments. Looks like code in the scans
019658,000012:                                                                                          	#                               but is actually documentation
019659,000013: 
019660,000014:                                                                                          	# This source code has been transcribed or otherwise adapted from
019661,000015:                                                                                          	# digitized images of a hardcopy from the private collection of 
019662,000016:                                                                                          	# Don Eyles.  The digitization was performed by archive.org.
019663,000017: 
019664,000018:                                                                                          	# Notations on the hardcopy document read, in part:
019665,000019: 
019666,000020:                                                                                          	#       473423A YUL SYSTEM FOR BLK2: REVISION 12 of PROGRAM AURORA BY DAP GROUP
019667,000021:                                                                                          	#       NOV 10, 1966
019668,000022: 
019669,000023:                                                                                          	#       [Note that this is the date the hardcopy was made, not the
019670,000024:                                                                                          	#       date of the program revision or the assembly.]
019671,000025: 
019672,000026:                                                                                          	# The scan images (with suitable reduction in storage size and consequent 
019673,000027:                                                                                          	# reduction in image quality) are available online at 
019674,000028:                                                                                          	#       https://www.ibiblio.org/apollo.  
019675,000029:                                                                                          	# The original high-quality digital images are available at archive.org:
019676,000030:                                                                                          	#       https://archive.org/details/aurora00dapg
019677,000031: 
019679,000033:                                                                                          	# CONTROL REACHES THIS POINT UNDER EITHER OF THE FOLLOWING TWO CONDITIONS ONCE THE DESCENT ENGINE AND THE DIGITAL
019680,000034:                                                                                          	# AUTOPILOT ARE BOTH ON:
019681,000035:                                                                                          	#          A) THE TRIM GIMBAL CONTROL LAW WAS ON DURING THE PREVIOUS Q,R-AXIS TIME5 INTERRUPT (OR THE DAPIDLER
019682,000036:                                                                                          	#             INITIALIZATION WAS SET FOR TRIM GIMBAL CONTROL AND THIS IS THE FIRST PASS), OR
019683,000037:                                                                                          	#          B) THE Q,R-AXES RCS JET CONTROL LAW ATTITUDE STEERING MODE REDUCED THE ATTITUDE ERROR TO LESS THAN
019684,000038:                                                                                          	# 1DEGREE ON EACH AXIS ON ITS LAST TIME5 INTERRUPT.
019685,000039: 
019686,000040:                                                                                          	# THE FOLLOWING T5RUPT ENTRY BEGINS THE TRIM GIMBAL CONTROL LAW.  SINCE IT IS ASSUMED THAT THE LEM WILL REMAIN
019687,000041:                                                                                          	# UNDER TRIM GIMBAL CONTROL, A KALMAN FILTER RUPT IS SET UP TO BEGIN 30 MS FROM THE TRIM GIMBAL RUPT.
019688,000042: 
019689,000043: 26,2564           32373        GTS                CAF      MS30F                         	# RESET TIMER IMMEDIATELY: DT = 30 MS
019690,000044: 26,2565           54030                           TS       TIME5                         	#
019691,000045: 
019692,000046: 26,2566           22016                           LXCH     BANKRUPT                      	# INTERRUPT LEAD IN (CONTINUED)
019693,000047: 26,2567           00006                           EXTEND                                 	#
019694,000048: 26,2570           22012                           QXCH     QRUPT                         	#
019695,000049: 
019696,000050: 26,2571           00006                           EXTEND                                 	#
019697,000051: 26,2572           32402                           DCA      POSTPFIL                      	#
019698,000052: 26,2573           52346                           DXCH     T5ADR                         	#
019699,000053:
