019991,000345: 26,3130           52077                           DXCH     A2CNTRAL                      	#
019992,000346: 
019993,000347: 26,3131           30071                           CAE      ACENTRAL                      	# GET SGN(ALPHA)
019994,000348: 26,3132           00006                           EXTEND                                 	#
019995,000349: 26,3133           63137                           BZMF     +4                            	#
019996,000350: 26,3134           00006                           EXTEND                                 	#
019997,000351: 26,3135           30077                           DCA      A2CNTRAL                      	#
019998,000352: 26,3136           13141                           TCF      +3                            	#
019999,000353: 26,3137           00006                           EXTEND                                 	#
020000,000354: 26,3140           40077                           DCS      A2CNTRAL                      	#
020001,000355: 26,3141           53531                           DXCH     FUNCTION                      	# SAVE AS SGN(ALPHA)ALPHA(2)
020002,000356: 26,3142           00006                           EXTEND                                 	#
020003,000357: 26,3143           30066                           DCA      OMEGA.K                       	#
020004,000358: 26,3144           21531                           DAS      FUNCTION                      	# FORM FUNCT1
020005,000359: 
020006,000360: 26,3145           11530                           CCS      FUNCTION                      	# DEL = SGN(FUNCT1)
020007,000361: 26,3146           13152                           TCF      POSFNCT1                      	#
020008,000362: 26,3147           13151                           TCF      +2                            	#
020009,000363: 26,3150           13154                           TCF      NEGFNCT1                      	#
020010,000364: 
020011,000365: 26,3151           11531                           CCS      FUNCTION   +1                 	# USE LOW ORDER WORD SINCE HIGH IS ZERO
020012,000366: 26,3152           37656        POSFNCT1           CAF      TWO                           	#
020013,000367: 26,3153           13155                           TCF      +2                            	#
020014,000368: 26,3154           37665        NEGFNCT1           CAF      ZERO                          	#
020015,000369: 26,3155           67667                           AD       NEG1                          	#
020017,000371: 26,3156           54072                           TS       DEL                           	#
020018,000372: 
020019,000373: 26,3157           10072                           CCS      DEL                           	# MAKE OMEGA*K REALLY DEL*OMEGA*K
020020,000374: 26,3160           13165                           TCF      FUNCT2                        	# (NOTHING NEED BE DONE)
020021,000375: 26,3161           25253        .66667             DEC      .66667                        	#
020022,000376: 26,3162           00006                           EXTEND                                 	#
020023,000377: 26,3163           40066                           DCS      OMEGA.K                       	#
020024,000378: 26,3164           52066                           DXCH     OMEGA.K                       	# CHANGE SIGN OF OMEGA*K
020025,000379: 
020026,000380: 26,3165           00006        FUNCT2             EXTEND                                 	#
020027,000381: 26,3166           30066                           DCA      OMEGA.K                       	#
020028,000382: 26,3167           53531                           DXCH     FUNCTION                      	# DEL*OMEGA*K
020029,000383: 26,3170           00006                           EXTEND                                 	#
020030,000384: 26,3171           30077                           DCA      A2CNTRAL                      	#
020031,000385: 26,3172           21531                           DAS      FUNCTION                      	# DEL*OMEGA*K + SGN(ALPHA)ALPHA(2)
020032,000386: 
020033,000387: 26,3173           30076        FUNCT3             CAE      A2CNTRAL                      	# CALCULATE (2/3)SGN(ALPHA)ALPHA(2)
020034,000388: 26,3174           00006                           EXTEND                                 	#
020035,000389: 26,3175           73161                           MP       .66667                        	#
020036,000390: 26,3176           52077                           DXCH     A2CNTRAL                      	#
020037,000391: 26,3177           56001                           XCH      L                             	#
020038,000392: 26,3200           00006                           EXTEND                                 	#
020039,000393: 26,3201           73161                           MP       .66667                        	#
020040,000394: 26,3202           26077                           ADS      A2CNTRAL   +1                 	#
020041,000395: 26,3203           54001                           TS       L                             	#
020042,000396: 26,3204           13206                           TCF      +2                            	#
020043,000397: 26,3205           60076                           AD       A2CNTRAL                      	#
020044,000398: 
020045,000399: 26,3206           52066                           DXCH     OMEGA.K                       	# DEL*OMEGA*K+
020046,000400: 26,3207           20077                           DAS      A2CNTRAL                      	# (2/3)SGN(ALPHA)ALPHA(2)=G
020047,000401: 
020048,000402: 26,3210           30076                           CAE      A2CNTRAL                      	# G*ALPHA IN D.P.
020049,000403: 26,3211           00006                           EXTEND                                 	#
020050,000404: 26,3212           70071                           MP       ACENTRAL                      	#
020051,000405: 26,3213           52077                           DXCH     A2CNTRAL                      	#
020052,000406: 26,3214           56001                           XCH      L                             	#
020053,000407: 26,3215           00006                           EXTEND                                 	#
020054,000408: 26,3216           70071                           MP       ACENTRAL                      	#
020055,000409: 26,3217           26077                           ADS      A2CNTRAL   +1                 	#
020056,000410: 26,3220           54001                           TS       L                             	#
020057,000411: 26,3221           13223                           TCF      +2                            	#
020058,000412: 26,3222           26076                           ADS      A2CNTRAL                      	#
020059,000413: 
020060,000414: 26,3223           52077                           DXCH     A2CNTRAL                      	# FIRST AND THIRD TERMS
020061,000415: 26,3224           20075                           DAS      K2THETA                       	# SUMMED IN D.P.
020062,000416: 
020063,000417:                                                                                          	# THE FOLLOWING SECTION CALCULATES .707*DEL*FUNCTION(3/2) AND ADDS IT TO THE OTHER TWO TERMS OF NEGUSUM.
020064,000418: 
020065,000419: 26,3225           11530                           CCS      FUNCTION                      	# TEST FOR HIGH ORDER WORD NON-ZERO
020066,000420: 26,3226           13273                           TCF      FMAGTEST                      	# YES, SEE IF RESCALING IS NECESSARY
020068,000422: 26,3227           13231                           TCF      +2                            	# NO, USE LOW ORDER WORD ONLY
020069,000423: 26,3230           26501        .707GTS            DEC      .70711                        	# (CCS HOLE USED FOR DATA)
020070,000424: 26,3231           04177                           TC       T6JOBCHK                      	#
020071,000425: 
020072,000426: 26,3232           31531                           CAE      FUNCTION   +1                 	# USE LOW ORDER WORD ONLY
020073,000427: 26,3233           04275                           TC       SPROOT                        	# SQUARE ROOT SUBROUTINE CALL
020074,000428: 26,3234           00006                           EXTEND                                 	#         3/2
020075,000429: 26,3235           71531                           MP       FUNCTION   +1                 	# FUNCTION
020076,000430: 26,3236           00006                           EXTEND                                 	# (needs to be shifted right 21 places)
020077,000431: 26,3237           77650                           MP       BIT8                          	#
020078,000432: 26,3240           56001                           XCH      L                             	#
020079,000433: 26,3241           37665                           CAF      ZERO                          	#              3/2
020080,000434: 26,3242           53531                           DXCH     FUNCTION                      	# SAVE FUNCTION    IN FUNCTION LOCATION
020081,000435: 26,3243           13260                           TCF      DELTEST                       	#
020082,000436: 
020083,000437: 26,3244           31530        SQRESCAL           CAE      FUNCTION                      	# HIGH ORDER WORD OF FUNCTION NEEDS TO BE
020084,000438: 26,3245           00006                           EXTEND                                 	# RESCALED FOR ACCURACY, SO MULTIPLY D.P.
020085,000439: 26,3246           77651                           MP       BIT7                          	# VALUE BY 2(6)
020086,000440: 26,3247           23530                           LXCH     FUNCTION                      	#
020087,000441: 26,3250           37665                           CAF      ZERO                          	#
020088,000442: 26,3251           57531                           XCH      FUNCTION   +1                 	#
020089,000443: 26,3252           00006                           EXTEND                                 	#
020090,000444: 26,3253           77651                           MP       BIT7                          	#
020091,000445: 26,3254           21531                           DAS      FUNCTION                      	#
020092,000446: 
020093,000447: 26,3255           37665                           CAF      ZERO                          	# SET FLAG TO GO TO RESCALE, AND GO TO DO
020094,000448: 26,3256           55527                           TS       MULTFLAG                      	# SQUARE ROOT AND FUNCTION(3/2)
020095,000449: 26,3257           13300                           TCF      DOSPROOT                      	# CALCULATION
020096,000450: 
020097,000451: 26,3260           47637        DELTEST            CS       POSMAX                        	# SET FLAG TO GO TO NEGUSUM
020098,000452: 26,3261           55527                           TS       MULTFLAG                      	#
020099,000453: 26,3262           10072                           CCS      DEL                           	# GET DEL*.707
020100,000454: 26,3263           33230                           CAF      .707GTS                       	#
020101,000455: 26,3264           13266                           TCF      +2                            	#
020102,000456: 26,3265           43230                           CS       .707GTS                       	#
020103,000457: 26,3266           13302                           TCF      SPDPMULT                      	# GO TO MULTIPLY ROUTINE
020104,000458: 
020105,000459: 26,3267           37637        RESHIFT            CAF      POSMAX                        	# SET FLAG TO GO TO DELTEST
020106,000460: 26,3270           55527                           TS       MULTFLAG                      	#
020107,000461: 26,3271           37652                           CAF      BIT6                          	#
020108,000462: 26,3272           13302                           TCF      SPDPMULT                      	# GO TO MULTIPLY ROUTINE
020109,000463: 
020110,000464: 26,3273           64362        FMAGTEST           AD       63/64+1                       	# IF MAGNITUDE OF HIGH ORDER WORD IS LESS
020111,000465: 26,3274           54000                           OVSK                                   	# THAN 1/64 RESCALE WHOLE D.P. WORD
020112,000466: 26,3275           13244                           TCF      SQRESCAL                      	#
020113,000467: 
020114,000468: 26,3276           37637                           CAF      POSMAX                        	#
020115,000469: 26,3277           55527                           TS       MULTFLAG                      	#
020116,000470: 
020117,000471: 26,3300           31530        DOSPROOT           CAE      FUNCTION                      	# USE HIGH ORDER WORD ONLY
020119,000473: 26,3301           04275                           TC       SPROOT                        	# SQUARE ROOT SUBROUTINE CALL
020120,000474: 
020121,000475: 26,3302           57530        SPDPMULT           XCH      FUNCTION                      	# THIS IS AN OPEN SUBROUTINE WHICH USES
020122,000476: 26,3303           00006                           EXTEND                                 	# MULTFLAG AS A RETURN SWITCH.
020123,000477: 26,3304           71530                           MP       FUNCTION                      	# IT MULTIPLIES FUNCTION (D.P.) BY C(A)
020124,000478: 26,3305           53531                           DXCH     FUNCTION                      	# AND LEAVES THE RESULT IN FUNCTION (D.P.)
020125,000479: 26,3306           00006                           EXTEND                                 	# IT IS USED FOR-
020126,000480: 26,3307           70001                           MP       L                             	# 1) F(1/2)*F
020127,000481: 26,3310           27531                           ADS      FUNCTION   +1                 	# 2) (.707*DEL)*F
020128,000482: 26,3311           54001                           TS       L                             	# 3) 2(-9)*F
020129,000483: 26,3312           13314                           TCF      +2                            	#
020130,000484: 26,3313           27530                           ADS      FUNCTION                      	#
020131,000485: 
020132,000486: 26,3314           11527                           CCS      MULTFLAG                      	# POSMAX MEANS GO TO DELTEST
020133,000487: 26,3315           13260                           TCF      DELTEST                       	# ZERO   MEANS GO TO RESHIFT
020134,000488: 26,3316           13267                           TCF      RESHIFT                       	# NEGMAX MEANS GO TO NEGUSUM
020135,000489: 
020136,000490: 26,3317           00006        NEGUSUM            EXTEND                                 	# FORM FINAL SUM FOR NEGUSUM
020137,000491: 26,3320           31531                           DCA      FUNCTION                      	#
020138,000492: 26,3321           20075                           DAS      K2THETA                       	#
020139,000493: 
020140,000494: 26,3322           10074                           CCS      K2THETA                       	# TEST FOR ZERO HIGH ORDER PART
020141,000495: 26,3323           13327                           TCF      NEGDRIVE                      	#
020142,000496: 26,3324           13326                           TCF      +2                            	#
020143,000497: 26,3325           13331                           TCF      POSDRIVE                      	#
020144,000498: 
020145,000499: 26,3326           10075                           CCS      K2THETA    +1                 	# SIGN TEST ON LOW ORDER PART
020146,000500: 26,3327           37656        NEGDRIVE           CAF      TWO                           	#
020147,000501: 26,3330           13332                           TCF      +2                            	#
020148,000502: 26,3331           37665        POSDRIVE           CAF      ZERO                          	#
020149,000503: 26,3332           67667                           AD       NEG1                          	#
020150,000504: 26,3333           50073                           INDEX    ITEMP6                        	# SET NEGUQ,R TO NEG DRIVE
020151,000505: 26,3334           55532                           TS       NEGUQ                         	#
020152,000506: 
020153,000507: 26,3335           40000                           COM                                    	#
020154,000508: 26,3336           00006                           EXTEND                                 	# SEND BACK JERK TERM
020155,000509: 26,3337           50073                           INDEX    ITEMP6                        	#
020156,000510: 26,3340           71541                           MP       ACCDOTQ                       	#
020157,000511: 26,3341           50073                           INDEX    ITEMP6                        	#
020158,000512: 26,3342           23542                           LXCH     QACCDOT                       	#
020159,000513: 
020160,000514: 26,3343           10073                           CCS      QRCNTR                        	# LOOP COUNTER
020161,000515: 26,3344           12771                           TCF      GOQTRIMG                      	#
020162,000516: 
020163,000517:                                                                                          	# TRANSFORM JERKS BACK TO GIMBAL AXES.
020164,000518: 
020165,000519: 26,3345           31542                           CAE      QACCDOT                       	# SCALED AT PI/2(7)
020166,000520: 26,3346           00006                           EXTEND                                 	#
020167,000521: 26,3347           71400                           MP       MR12                          	# SCALED AT 2
020168,000522: 26,3350           55576                           TS       Y3DOT                         	#
020170,000524: 26,3351           31544                           CAE      RACCDOT                       	# SCALED AT PI/2(7)
020171,000525: 26,3352           00006                           EXTEND                                 	#
020172,000526: 26,3353           71402                           MP       MR13                          	# SCALED AT 2
020173,000527: 26,3354           27576                           ADS      Y3DOT                         	#
020174,000528: 26,3355           27576                           ADS      Y3DOT                         	# SCALED AT PI/2(7)
020175,000529: 
020176,000530: 26,3356           31542                           CAE      QACCDOT                       	# SCALED AT PI/2(7)
020177,000531: 26,3357           00006                           EXTEND                                 	#
020178,000532: 26,3360           71401                           MP       MR22                          	# SCALED AT 1
020179,000533: 26,3361           55600                           TS       Z3DOT                         	#
020180,000534: 26,3362           31544                           CAE      RACCDOT                       	# SCALED AT PI/2(7)
020181,000535: 26,3363           00006                           EXTEND                                 	#
020182,000536: 26,3364           71403                           MP       MR23                          	# SCALED AT 1
020183,000537: 26,3365           27600                           ADS      Z3DOT                         	# SCALED AT PI/2(7)
020184,000538: 
020185,000539: 26,3366           03400                           TC       WRCHN12                       	# SEND GIMBAL DRIVES TO SERVOS
020186,000540: 26,3367           14606                           TCF      RESUME                        	# WAIT UNTIL NEXT TRIM GIMBAL RUPT
020187,000541: 
020188,000542:                                                                                          	# WAITLIST TASKS TO SET TRIM GIMBAL TURN OFF BITS.
020189,000543: 
020190,000544: 26,3370           37665        OFFGIMQ            CAF      ZERO                          	# SET Q-AXIS FLAG TO ZERO
020191,000545: 26,3371           55532                           TS       NEGUQ                         	#
020192,000546: 26,3372           13375                           TCF      +3                            	#
020193,000547: 26,3373           37665        OFFGIMR            CAF      ZERO                          	# SET R-AXIS FLAG TO ZERO
020194,000548: 26,3374           55534                           TS       NEGUR                         	#
020195,000549: 26,3375           03400                           TC       WRCHN12                       	# FLAGS TO CHANNEL BITS
020196,000550: 26,3376           14602                           TCF      TASKOVER                      	#
020197,000551: 
020198,000552:                                                                                          	# THE WRCHN12 SUBROUTINE SETS BITS 9,10,11,12 OF CHANNEL 12 ON THE BASIS OF THE CONTENTS OF NEGUQ,NEGUR WHICH ARE
020199,000553:                                                                                          	# THE NEGATIVES OF THE TRIM GIMBAL DESIRED DRIVES.
020200,000554: 
020201,000555: 26,3377           07400        BGIM               OCTAL    07400                         	#
020202,000556: 26,3400     0073               CHNL12             EQUALS   ITEMP6                        	#
020203,000557: 
020204,000558: 26,3400           43377        WRCHN12            CS       BGIM                          	# SAVE THE REST OF CHANNEL 12 DURING TESTS
020205,000559: 26,3401           00006                           EXTEND                                 	#
020206,000560: 26,3402           02012                           RAND     12                            	#
020207,000561: 26,3403           54073                           TS       CHNL12                        	# (TEMPORARY STORAGE)
020208,000562: 
020209,000563: 26,3404           11532                           CCS      NEGUQ                         	#
020210,000564: 26,3405           37647                           CAF      BIT9                          	#
020211,000565: 26,3406           13410                           TCF      +2                            	#
020212,000566: 26,3407           37646                           CAF      BIT10                         	#
020213,000567: 26,3410           26073                           ADS      CHNL12                        	#
020214,000568: 
020215,000569: 26,3411           11534                           CCS      NEGUR                         	#
020216,000570: 26,3412           37645                           CAF      BIT11                         	#
020217,000571: 26,3413           13415                           TCF      +2                            	#
020218,000572: 26,3414           37644                           CAF      BIT12                         	#
020219,000573: 26,3415           26073                           ADS      CHNL12                        	# (STORED RESULT NOT USED AT PRESENT)
020221,000575: 26,3416           00006                           EXTEND                                 	#
020222,000576: 26,3417           01012                           WRITE    12                            	#
020223,000577: 
020224,000578: 26,3420           00002                           TC       Q                             	# SIMPLE RETURN ALWAYS
020225,000579: 
020226,000580:                                                                                          	# Q,R-TRANSF TRANSFORMS A Y,Z GIMBAL COORDINATE VARIABLE PAIR (IN A,L) TO PILOT COORDINATES (Q/R), RETURNED IN A.
020227,000581:                                                                                          	# (THE MATRIX M FROM GIMBAL TO PILOT AXES IS ASSUMED TO BE DONE BY T4RUPT AND SCALED AT +1.)
020228,000582: 
020229,000583: 26,3421     0073               QRERAS             EQUALS   ITEMP6                        	#
020230,000584: 
020231,000585: 26,3421           22073        QTRANSF            LXCH     QRERAS                        	# SAVE Z-AXIS VARIABLE
020232,000586: 26,3422           00006                           EXTEND                                 	#
020233,000587: 26,3423           71405                           MP       M21                           	# (Y-AXIS)*M21
020234,000588: 26,3424           56073                           XCH      QRERAS                        	# SAVE, GET Z-AXIS VARIABLE
020235,000589: 26,3425           00006                           EXTEND                                 	#
020236,000590: 26,3426           71401                           MP       M22                           	# (Z-AXIS)*M22
020237,000591: 26,3427           60073                           AD       QRERAS                        	# SUM = (Y-AXIS)*M21 + (Z-AXIS)*M22
020238,000592: 26,3430           00002                           TC       Q                             	# RETURN WITH SUM IN A
020239,000593: 
020240,000594: 26,3431           22073        RTRANSF            LXCH     QRERAS                        	# SAVE Z-AXIS VARIABLE
020241,000595: 26,3432           00006                           EXTEND                                 	#
020242,000596: 26,3433           71406                           MP       M31                           	# (Y-AXIS)*M31
020243,000597: 26,3434           56073                           XCH      QRERAS                        	# SAVE, GET Z-AXIS VARIABLE
020244,000598: 26,3435           00006                           EXTEND                                 	#
020245,000599: 26,3436           71403                           MP       M32                           	# (Z-AXIS)*M32
020246,000600: 26,3437           60073                           AD       QRERAS                        	# SUM = (Y-AXIS)*M31 + (Z-AXIS)*M32
020247,000601: 26,3440           00002                           TC       Q                             	# RETURN WITH SUM IN A
020248,000602: 
020249,000603: 26,3441           25253        (2/3)              DEC      0.66667                       	#
020250,000604: 
020252,000606:                                                                                          	# SUBROUTINE: TGOFFCAL            MOD. NO. 1  DATE: AUGUST 22, 1966
020253,000607: 
020254,000608:                                                                                          	# PROGRAM DESIGN BY: RICHARD D. GOSS (MIT/IL)
020255,000609: 
020256,000610:                                                                                          	# PROGRAM IMPLEMENTATION BY: JONATHAN D. ADDELSTON (ADAMS ASSOCIATES)
020257,000611: 
020258,000612:                                                                                          	# THIS SUBROUTINE CALCULATES THE TRIM GIMBAL SHUTDOWN TIME FOR EITHER THE Q OR THE R AXIS (DEPENDING ON THE
020259,000613:                                                                                          	# CALLING SEQUENCE).  THIS TIME IS SCALED FOR IMMEDIATE USE BY A WAITLIST CALL AS SHOWN IN THE CALLING SEQUENCES.
020260,000614:                                                                                          	# IF THE TIME-TO-GO IS MORE THAN TWO MINUTES, IT IS LIMITED TO TWO MINUTES DUE TO THE WAITLIST SPECIFICATION.  IF
020261,000615:                                                                                          	# THE TIME-TO-GO IS LESS THAN TEN MILLISECONDS, THE SHUTDOWN IS PERFORMED IMMEDIATELY AND THE WAITLIST CALL IS
020262,000616:                                                                                          	# BY-PASSED.  FINALLY, IF THE TRIM GIMBAL SHOULD HAPPEN TO BE MOVING IN A DIRECTION WHICH INCREASES THE ANGULAR
020263,000617:                                                                                          	# ACCELERATION ABOUT THE GIVEN AXIS, THEN THE NEGATIVE GIMBAL DRIVE FLAG IS IMMEDIATELY COMPLEMENTED AND THE
020264,000618:                                                                                          	# NORMAL CALCULATIONS ARE RESUMED.
020265,000619: 
020266,000620:                                                                                          	# THESE TIME-TO-GO CALCULATIONS ARE DESIGNED TO DRIVE THE TRIM GIMBAL TO A POSITION WHERE THE DESCENT ENGINE WILL
020267,000621:                                                                                          	# CAUSE NO ANGULAR ACCELERATION.  THIS SUBROUTINE IS CALLED ONLY FROM THE WAITLIST TASK CHEKDRIV WHICH IS
020268,000622:                                                                                          	# INITIATED ONLY WHEN THE TRIM GIMBAL CONTROL LAW HAS LOST CONTROL OF THE LEM VEHICLE ATTITUDE AND MUST RETURN TO
020269,000623:                                                                                          	# THE USE OF REACTION CONTROL SYSTEM JETS.
020270,000624: 
020271,000625:                                                                                          	# CALLING SEQUENCES:
020272,000626: 
020273,000627:                                                                                          	#                     26,1000  3 7657 1            CAF    ZERO           Q-AXIS INDEXER
020274,000628:                                                                                          	#                     26,1001  0 $$$$ $            TC     TGOFFCAL       CALL TGOFFCAL (*** REPLACE $S ***)
020275,000629:                                                                                          	#                     26,1002  0 4511 0            TC     WAITLIST       CALL WAITLIST WITH CALCULATED TIME
020276,000630:                                                                                          	#                     26,1003   0$$$$ $            2CADR  OFFGIMQ        2CADR OF Q-AXIS SHUTDOWN PROGRAM
020277,000631:                                                                                          	#                     26,1004   54006 1
020278,000632: 
020279,000633:                                                                                          	#                     26,1005  3 7657 1            CAF    TWO            R-AXIS INDEXER
020280,000634:                                                                                          	#                     26,1006  0 $$$$ $            TC     TGOFFCAL       CALL TGOFFCAL (*** REPLACE $S ***)
020281,000635:                                                                                          	#                     26,1007  0 4511 0            TC     WAITLIST       CALL WAITLIST WITH CALCULATED TIME
020282,000636:                                                                                          	#                     26,1010   0$$$$ $            2CADR  OFFGIMR        2CADR OF R-AXIS SHUTDOWN PROGRAM
020283,000637:                                                                                          	#                     26,1011   54006 1
020284,000638: 
020285,000639:                                                                                          	# SUBROUTINES CALLED: NONE, BUT WRCHNL12 IS CALLED AFTER BOTH TGOFFCALL CALLS.
020286,000640: 
020287,000641:                                                                                          	# NORMAL EXITS: TO WAITLIST CALL OR BEYOND 2CADR IN CALLING SEQUENCE AS SPECIFIED ABOVE.
020288,000642: 
020289,000643:                                                                                          	# ALARM OR ABORT EXIT MODES: NONE
020290,000644: 
020291,000645:                                                                                          	# INPUT: 1. THE AXIS INDEXER: 0 FOR Q, 2 FOR R (SEE CALLING SEQUENCES)
020292,000646:                                                                                          	#        2. THE SIGNED TIME DERIVATIVE OF ACCELERATION (QACCDOT OR RACCDOT) SCALED AT PI/2(7) RAD/SEC(3).
020293,000647:                                                                                          	#        3. THE ACCELERATION APPROXIMATION FROM THE DESCENT KALMAN FILTER TRANSFORMED TO PILOT AXES (ALPHAQ OR
020294,000648:                                                                                          	# ALPHAR) SCALED AT PI/8 RAD/SEC(2).
020295,000649:                                                                                          	#        4. THE NEGATIVE GIMBAL DRIVE FLAG (NEGUQ AND NEGUR) WHERE +1 BIT INDICATES A GIMBAL DRIVE DIRECTION WHICH
020296,000650:                                                                                          	# DECREASES THE SIGNED GIMBAL ANGLE, WHERE -1 BIT INDICATES A GIMBAL DRIVE DIRECTION WHICH INCREASES THE SIGNED
020297,000651:                                                                                          	# GIMBAL ANGLE, AND WHERE ZERO INDICATES NO DRIVE.
020298,000652:                                                                                          	#        5. CHANNEL 12 CONTAINS THE TRIM GIMBAL DRIVES AND OTHER BITS.
020299,000653: 
020300,000654:                                                                                          	# ERASEABLE STORAGE CONFIGURATION (NEEDED BY THE INDEXING METHODS):
020302,000656:                                                                                          	#               NEGUQ           ERASE           +2                              # NEGATIVE OF Q-AXIS GIMBAL DRIVE
020303,000657:                                                                                          	#               (SPWORD)        EQUALS          NEGUQ           +1              # ANY S.P. ERASABLE NUMBER, NOW THRSTCMD
020304,000658:                                                                                          	#               NEGUR           EQUALS          NEGUQ           +2              # NEGATIVE OF R-AXIS GIMBAL DRIVE
020305,000659: 
020306,000660:                                                                                          	#               QACCDOT         ERASE           +2                              # Q-JERK SCALED AT PI/2(7) RAD/SEC(3) +SGN
020307,000661:                                                                                          	#               (SPWORD)        EQUALS          QACCDOT         +1              # ANY S.P. ERASABLE NUMBER, NOW ACCDOTR
020308,000662:                                                                                          	#               RACCDOT         EQUALS          QACCDOT         +2              # R-JERK SCALED AT PI/2(7) RAD/SEC(3) +SGN
020309,000663:                                                                                          	# NOTE: NOW ACCDOTQ MUST PRECEDE QACCDOT
020310,000664: 
020311,000665:                                                                                          	#               ALPHAQ          ERASE           +2                              # Q-AXIS ACCELERATION SCALED AT PI/8 R/S2
020312,000666:                                                                                          	#               (SPWORD)        EQUALS          ALPHAQ          +1              # ANY S.P. ERASABLE NUMBER, NOW OMEGAR
020313,000667:                                                                                          	#               ALPHAR          EQUALS          ALPHAQ          +2              # R-AXIS ACCELERATION SCALED AT PI/8 R/S2
020314,000668:                                                                                          	# NOTE: NOW OMEGAP,OMEGAQ PRECEDE ALPHAQ
020315,000669: 
020316,000670:                                                                                          	# DEBRIS: L, Q, ITEMP1, ITEMP2, ITEMP6
020317,000671: 
020318,000672: 
020319,000673: 26,3442           54065        TGOFFCAL           TS       QRNDXER                       	# Q OR R AXIS INDEXER
020320,000674: 26,3443           50065                           INDEX    QRNDXER                       	# GET SIGNED JERK TERM SCALED AT PI/2(7)
020321,000675: 26,3444           31542                           CAE      QACCDOT                       	# IN RADIANS/SECOND(3)
020322,000676: 26,3445           00006                           EXTEND                                 	# IF THETA TRIPLE-DOT IS ZERO, THEN RESET
020323,000677: 26,3446           13511                           BZF      TGOFFNOW                      	# DRIVE TO ZERO (SHOULD BE REDUNDANT)
020324,000678: 26,3447           54066                           TS       NZACCDOT                      	# SAVE NON-ZERO JERK FOR DENOMINATOR
020325,000679: 26,3450           00006                           EXTEND                                 	# TEST FOR REDUCING ACCELERATION IS SAME
020326,000680: 26,3451           50065                           INDEX    QRNDXER                       	# AS TEST FOR SAME SIGN IN -ACC AND ACCDOT
020327,000681: 26,3452           71420                           MP       ALPHAQ                        	# IF POSITIVE PRODUCT, THEN GIMBAL DRIVE
020328,000682: 26,3453           10000                           CCS      A                             	# SHOULD BE REVERSED: NOTE THAT A SIMPLE
020329,000683: 26,3454           13460                           TCF      NEGTIME                       	# BZMF TEST WILL NOT WORK WHEN THE MP
020330,000684: 26,3455           13460                           TCF      NEGTIME                       	# INSTRUCTION RESULTS IN ZERO IN A
020331,000685: 26,3456           13466                           TCF      POSTIME                       	# AT POSTIME IT IS INSURED THAT A POSITIVE
020332,000686: 26,3457           13466                           TCF      POSTIME                       	# TIME WILL RESULT AND ACC WILL GO TO ZERO
020333,000687: 
020334,000688: 26,3460           50065        NEGTIME            INDEX    QRNDXER                       	# COMPLEMENT THE DRIVE DIRECTION FLAG
020335,000689: 26,3461           41532                           CS       NEGUQ                         	#
020336,000690: 26,3462           50065                           INDEX    QRNDXER                       	#
020337,000691: 26,3463           55532                           TS       NEGUQ                         	#
020338,000692: 26,3464           40066                           CS       NZACCDOT                      	# COMPLEMENT ACCDOT TO GET A GUARANTEED
020339,000693: 26,3465           54066                           TS       NZACCDOT                      	# POSITIVE TIME FROM QUOTIENT
020340,000694: 
020341,000695: 26,3466           50065        POSTIME            INDEX    QRNDXER                       	# TIME = -ACC/ACCDOT (POSITIVE VALUE)
020342,000696: 26,3467           41420                           CS       ALPHAQ                        	# SCALED AT PI/8 RADIANS/SECOND(2)
020343,000697: 26,3470           00006                           EXTEND                                 	# MULTIPLY 1/16
020344,000698: 26,3471           77645                           MP       BIT11                         	# TO CHANGE SCALING TO 2PI RAD/SEC(2)
020345,000699: 26,3472           00006                           EXTEND                                 	# ACCDOT SCALED AT PI/2(7) IN DENOMINATOR
020346,000700: 26,3473           10066                           DV       NZACCDOT                      	# YIELDS TIME SCALED AT 256 SECONDS
020347,000701: 26,3474           63517                           AD       -2MIN256                      	# COMPARE WITH MAXIMUM 2 MINUTE DELAY OF
020348,000702: 26,3475           10000                           CCS      A                             	# WAITLIST ACTION (TIMES AT 256 SECONDS)
020349,000703: 26,3476           43516                           CS       -2MINWL                       	# MORE THAN TWO MINUTES, USE 2 MINUTES
020350,000704: 26,3477           00002                           TC       Q                             	# RETURN WL CALL WITH 2 MIN AT 1BIT=10MS
020352,000706: 26,3500           67657                           AD       ONE                           	# (CORRECT FOR CCS BIT)
020353,000707: 26,3501           00006                           EXTEND                                 	# CALCULATE DT = ABS(T-2MIN)
020354,000708: 26,3502           73520                           MP       128/164                       	# AND RESCALE DT TO WAITLIST SCALING
020355,000709: 26,3503           20001                           DDOUBL                                 	#
020356,000710: 26,3504           63516                           AD       -2MINWL                       	# -T = DT + 2MIN (IN WAITLIST SCALING)
020357,000711: 26,3505           40000                           COM                                    	# MAKE T POSITIVE FOR WAITLIST
020358,000712: 26,3506           00006                           EXTEND                                 	# MAKE FINAL CHECK TO INSURE T .G. 10MS
020359,000713: 26,3507           63511                           BZMF     TGOFFNOW                      	# DO SHUTDOWN NOW (COULD USE BZF)
020360,000714: 26,3510           00002                           TC       Q                             	# RETURN TO WAITLIST CALL WITH WL TIME
020361,000715: 
020362,000716: 26,3511           37665        TGOFFNOW           CAF      ZERO                          	# MAKE SURE PLUS ZERO FOR DRIVE FLAG
020363,000717: 26,3512           50065                           INDEX    QRNDXER                       	# TURN OFF DRIVE FLAG NOW
020364,000718: 26,3513           55532                           TS       NEGUQ                         	#
020365,000719: 26,3514           50002                           INDEX    Q                             	#
020366,000720: 26,3515           00003                           TC       3                             	# SKIP WAITLIST CALL AND 2CADR
020367,000721: 
020368,000722: 
020369,000723: 26,3516     0065               QRNDXER            EQUALS   ITEMP1                        	# INDEXER FOR Q OR R AXIS
020370,000724: 26,3516     0066               NZACCDOT           EQUALS   ITEMP2                        	# TEMPORARY STORAGE FOR NON-ZERO ACCDOT
020371,000725: 26,3516           50437        -2MINWL            DEC      -12000     B-14               	# - 2 MINUTES SCALED FOR WAITLIST
020372,000726: 26,3517           60777        -2MIN256           DEC      -.46875                       	# - 2 MINUTES SCALED AT 256
020373,000727: 26,3520           31000        128/164            OCTAL    31000                         	# 128/163.84 CONVERTING 256 TO WAITLIST/2
020374,000728: 26,3521                        ENDDAP26           EQUALS                                 	#
(End of include-file TRIM_GIMBAL_CONTROL_SYSTEM.agc, resuming main.agc)
020374,000061:

020407,000032: 
020409,000034: 25,3064                                           BANK     25                            	#
020410,000035: 25,3064  E6,1634                                  EBANK=   AOSQ                          	#
020411,000036: 
020412,000037: 25,3064           37650        AOSTASK            CAF      BIT8                          	# TEST POWERED ASCENT FLAG (BIT8/DPBOOLS)
020413,000038: 25,3065           70765                           MASK     DAPBOOLS                      	# 0- NOT POWERED ASCENT
020414,000039: 25,3066           00006                           EXTEND                                 	# 1- POWERED ASCENT
020415,000040: 25,3067           13325                           BZF      COASTASC                      	# END CYCLE OF TASKS DURING ASCENT COAST
020416,000041: 
020417,000042: 25,3070           31671                           CAE      KCOEFCTR                      	# TEST KCOEFCTR FOR INITIAL PASS
020418,000043: 25,3071           00006                           EXTEND                                 	#
020419,000044: 25,3072           13275                           BZF      ZEROCOEF                      	# DISCONTINUITY SECTION FOR COEFFA
020420,000045: 
020421,000046: 25,3073           63367                           AD       DEC-399                       	# TEST KCOEFCTR FOR CONSTANT RANGE
020422,000047: 25,3074           00006                           EXTEND                                 	# ON BOTH K AND COEFFA
020423,000048: 25,3075           63077                           BZMF     +2                            	#
020424,000049: 25,3076           13301                           TCF      KONENOW                       	#
020425,000050: 
020426,000051: 25,3077           33410                           CAF      0.00125                       	# COEFFA = 0.00125(T) + 0.25
020427,000052: 25,3100           00006                           EXTEND                                 	#
020428,000053: 25,3101           71671                           MP       KCOEFCTR                      	#
020429,000054: 25,3102           37643                           CAF      BIT13                         	#
020430,000055: 25,3103           60001                           AD       L                             	#
020431,000056: 25,3104           54066        COEFFA             TS       ITEMP2                        	#
020432,000057: 
020433,000058: 25,3105           33411                           CAF      0.0014                        	# K = 0.0014(T) + 0.44
020434,000059: 25,3106           00006                           EXTEND                                 	#
020435,000060: 25,3107           71671                           MP       KCOEFCTR                      	#
020436,000061: 25,3110           33412                           CAF      0.44                          	#
020437,000062: 25,3111           60001                           AD       L                             	#
020438,000063: 25,3112           54065                           TS       ITEMP1                        	#
020439,000064: 25,3113           40000                           COM                                    	# (1-K),QR SCALED AT 1
020440,000065: 25,3114           67637                           AD       POSMAX                        	# (1 BIT ERROR DOES NOT COMPOUND)
020441,000066: 25,3115           55657                           TS       (1-K)QR                       	#
020442,000067: 
020443,000068: 25,3116           00006                           EXTEND                                 	# (1-K)/8 IS (1-K) SCALED AT 8
020444,000069: 25,3117           77644                           MP       BIT12                         	#
020445,000070: 25,3120           55660                           TS       (1-K)/8                       	#
020446,000071: 
020447,000072: 25,3121           30065                           CAE      ITEMP1                        	# WFORQR = K/DT SCALED AT 16
020448,000073: 25,3122           00006                           EXTEND                                 	#
020449,000074: 25,3123           73403                           MP       10AT16WL                      	# DT = .1 SECS
020450,000075: 25,3124           55656                           TS       WFORQR                        	#
020451,000076: 
020452,000077: 25,3125           40065                           CS       ITEMP1                        	# FORM (.1-.05K) FROM K SCALED AT 1
020453,000078: 25,3126           00006                           EXTEND                                 	# WHICH IS USED AS IS BUT SINCE THESUM
020454,000079: 25,3127           73375                           MP       .05AT.5                       	# IS TO BE SCALED AT 1/2, THE TWO
020455,000080: 25,3130           63376                           AD       .1AT.5                        	# CONSTANTS REFLECT THAT SCALE FACTOR
020456,000081: 25,3131           54065                           TS       ITEMP1                        	#
020457,000082: 
020458,000083: 25,3132           30066        COEFFA1            CAE      ITEMP2                        	# FORM COEFFA(AOSQ)
020459,000084: 25,3133           00006                           EXTEND                                 	#
020460,000085: 
020462,000087: 
020463,000088: 25,3134           71634                           MP       AOSQ                          	#
020464,000089: 25,3135           55634                           TS       AOSQ                          	# FIRST TERM OF NEW AOSQ, ,SCALED AT PI/2
020465,000090: 
020466,000091: 25,3136           30066                           CAE      ITEMP2                        	# FORM COEFFA(AOSR)
020467,000092: 25,3137           00006                           EXTEND                                 	#
020468,000093: 25,3140           71635                           MP       AOSR                          	#
020469,000094: 25,3141           55635                           TS       AOSR                          	# FIRST TERM OF NEW AOSR, SCALED AT PI/2
020470,000095: 
020472,000097: 25,3142           40066                           CS       ITEMP2                        	# FORM .5(1-COEFFA) SCALED AT 2
020473,000098: 25,3143           00006                           EXTEND                                 	# FORM COEFFA SCALED AT 1 WHICH IS THE
020474,000099: 25,3144           77643                           MP       BIT13                         	# SAME AS 2(COEFFA) SCALED AT 2
020475,000100: 25,3145           67643                           AD       BIT13                         	# SO MULTIPLY BY 1/4 TO GET .5(COEFFA)
020476,000101: 25,3146           54066                           TS       ITEMP2                        	# AND 1/4 IS 1/2 WHEN SCALED AT 2
020478,000103: 
020479,000104: 25,3147           41417                           CS       OMEGAQ                        	# SAVE PRESENT OMEGAQ FOR NEXT PASS
020480,000105: 25,3150           57644                           XCH      OLDWFORQ                      	# GET -(LAST OMEGAQ)
020481,000106: 25,3151           00006                           EXTEND                                 	#
020482,000107: 25,3152           61640                           SU       SUMRATEQ                      	# FORM- W - W(OLD) - SUMRATE = SUM
020483,000108: 25,3153           61417                           AD       OMEGAQ                        	# SCALED AT PI/4 RADIANS/SECOND
020484,000109: 25,3154           00006                           EXTEND                                 	#
020485,000110: 25,3155           70066                           MP       ITEMP2                        	# AOSQ = COEFFA(AOSQ)+.5(1-COEFFA)(SUM)
020486,000111: 25,3156           27634                           ADS      AOSQ                          	# SCALED AT PI/2 RADIANS/SECOND(2)
020487,000112: 
020488,000113: 25,3157           41421                           CS       OMEGAR                        	# SAVE PRESENT OMEGAQ FOR NEXT PASS
020489,000114: 25,3160           57645                           XCH      OLDWFORR                      	# GET -(LAST OMEGAR)
020490,000115: 25,3161           00006                           EXTEND                                 	#
020491,000116: 25,3162           61641                           SU       SUMRATER                      	# FORM- W - W(OLD) - SUMRATE = SUM
020492,000117: 25,3163           61421                           AD       OMEGAR                        	# SCALED AT PI/4 RADIANS/SECOND
020493,000118: 25,3164           00006                           EXTEND                                 	#
020494,000119: 25,3165           70066                           MP       ITEMP2                        	# AOSR = COEFFA(AOSR)+.5(1-COEFFA)(SUM)
020495,000120: 25,3166           27635                           ADS      AOSR                          	# SCALED AT PI/2 RADIANS/SECOND(2)
020496,000121: 
020497,000122: 25,3167           30065                           CAE      ITEMP1                        	#
020498,000123: 25,3170           00006                           EXTEND                                 	# FORM TERM FR RATE DERIVATION
020499,000124: 25,3171           71634                           MP       AOSQ                          	# (.1-.05K)AOSQ
020500,000125: 25,3172           55642                           TS       AOSQTERM                      	# SCALED AT PI/4 RADIANS/SECOND
020501,000126: 
020502,000127: 25,3173           30065                           CAE      ITEMP1                        	#
020503,000128: 25,3174           00006                           EXTEND                                 	# FORM TERM FOR RATE DERIVATION
020504,000129: 25,3175           71635                           MP       AOSR                          	# (.1-.05K)AOSR
020505,000130: 25,3176           55643                           TS       AOSRTERM                      	# SCALED AT PI/4 RADIANS/SECOND
020506,000131: 
020507,000132: 25,3177           31634                           CAE      AOSQ                          	# FORM AOS FOR U-AXIS
020508,000133: 25,3200           61635                           AD       AOSR                          	#
020509,000134: 25,3201           00006                           EXTEND                                 	#
020510,000135: 25,3202           73377                           MP       .707WL                        	#
020511,000136: 25,3203           55636                           TS       AOSU                          	# SCALED AT PI/2 RADIANS/SECOND(2)
020512,000137: 
020513,000138: 25,3204           41634                           CS       AOSQ                          	# FORM AOS FOR V-AXIS
020514,000139: 25,3205           61635                           AD       AOSR                          	#
020515,000140: 
020517,000142: 25,3206           00006                           EXTEND                                 	#
020518,000143: 25,3207           73377                           MP       .707WL                        	#
020519,000144: 25,3210           55637                           TS       AOSV                          	# SCALED AT PI/2 RADIANS/SECOND(2)
020520,000145: 
020521,000146: 25,3211           36165                           CAF      THREE                         	# SET UP LOOP FOR Q,R,U,V-AXES
020522,000147: 25,3212           54065                           TS       AXISCNTR                      	#
020523,000148: 
020524,000149: 25,3213           50065        ALLAXES            INDEX    AXISCNTR                      	#
020525,000150: 25,3214           11634                           CCS      AOSQ                          	# FORM ABSOLUTE VALUE OF AOS
020526,000151: 25,3215           67657                           AD       ONE                           	#
020527,000152: 25,3216           13220                           TCF      +2                            	#
020528,000153: 25,3217           67657                           AD       ONE                           	#
020529,000154: 25,3220           50065                           INDEX    AXISCNTR                      	# SAVE IN ITEMP REGISTER (3-6)
020530,000155: 25,3221           54070                           TS       ABVLAOSQ                      	# SCALED AT PI/2 RADIANS/SECOND(2)
020531,000156: 25,3222           63400                           AD       -.02R/S2                      	# -.02 RADIANS/SECOND(2) SCALED AT PI/2
020532,000157: 25,3223           00006                           EXTEND                                 	#
020533,000158: 25,3224           63263                           BZMF     CONSTMIN                      	# USE 1/(.02) SEC(2)/RAD AS 1/AMIN
020534,000159: 25,3225           63413                           AD       +.02R/S2                      	#
020535,000160: 25,3226           54066                           TS       ITEMP2                        	#
020536,000161: 25,3227           37651                           CAF      BIT7                          	#
020537,000162: 25,3230           22007                           ZL                                     	# SCALE FACTOR FOR .5ACCMIN.
020538,000163: 25,3231           00006                           EXTEND                                 	#
020539,000164: 25,3232           10066                           DV       ITEMP2                        	#
020540,000165: 25,3233           50065        ACCMINVL           INDEX    AXISCNTR                      	#
020541,000166: 25,3234           55651                           TS       .5ACCMNQ                      	# SCALED AT 2(+8)/PI
020542,000167: 
020543,000168: 25,3235           33400                           CAF      -.02R/S2                      	# CALCULATE ONE OF THE FOLLOWING (4) SUMS:
020544,000169: 25,3236           00006                           EXTEND                                 	# 2JETAC(Q,R)-ABAOS(Q,R)-.02RAD/SEC(2) OR
020545,000170: 25,3237           50065                           INDEX    AXISCNTR                      	# 1JETAC(U,V)-ABAOS(1,V)-.02RAD/SEC(2)
020546,000171: 25,3240           60070                           SU       ABVLAOSQ                      	# EACH SUM HAS EACH TERM SCALED AT PI/2
020547,000172: 25,3241           50065                           INDEX    AXISCNTR                      	# THE "OUTER LOOP" IS DEFINED TO CALCULATE
020548,000173: 25,3242           61630                           AD       1JACCQ                        	# THE VALUES 1JACCV, 1JACCR SCALED AT PI/4
020549,000174: 25,3243           00006                           EXTEND                                 	# AND 1JACCU, 1JACCV SCALED AT PI/2 WHERE
020550,000175: 25,3244           63265                           BZMF     DEMANDAC                      	# 1JACCU = 2(.707)(1JACCQ+1JACCR) AND
020551,000176: 25,3245           37665                           CAF      ZERO                          	# 1JACCV = 2(.707)(1JACCQ+1JACCR)
020552,000177: 25,3246           50065                           INDEX    AXISCNTR                      	# WHERE THE CALCULATIONS USE THE FACT THAT
020553,000178: 25,3247           55665                           TS       QMANDACC                      	# 1JACC(Q,R) AT PI/4 = 2JACC(Q,R) AT PI/2
020554,000179: 25,3250           50065                           INDEX    AXISCNTR                      	# MANDACC(Q,R)=1 MEANS USE 4 JETS, 0 FOR 2
020555,000180: 25,3251           31445                           CAE      1/2JTSQ                       	# MANDACC(U,V)=1 MEANS USE 2 JETS, 0 FOR 1
020556,000181: 25,3252           00006                           EXTEND                                 	#
020557,000182: 25,3253           77642                           MP       BIT14                         	#
020558,000183: 25,3254           50065        AXISLOOP           INDEX    AXISCNTR                      	# SET UP 1/NJTSX TO 1/2JTSX FOR URGENCY
020559,000184: 25,3255           55661                           TS       1/NJTSQ                       	# (DOES NOT COUNT FOR U,V-AXES)
020560,000185: 
020561,000186: 25,3256           10065                           CCS      AXISCNTR                      	# DECREMENT LOOP COUNTER AND TEST FOR END
020562,000187: 25,3257           13261                           TCF      +2                            	#
020563,000188: 25,3260           13313                           TCF      NEXTCALL                      	# FINISHED LOOP
020564,000189: 
020565,000190: 25,3261           54065                           TS       AXISCNTR                      	#
